%% Text:śivadharmaśāstram
%% Based on the edition of NN and NN with occasional pieces of commentary in Nepali by Naraharinath: paśupatimatam śivadharmamahāśāstram paśupatināthadarśanam
%% bṛhadādhyātmikapariṣada, kāṣṭhamaṇḍapa, Nepal, saṃvat 2055 (1998) and
%% compared with transcript T0032 (T32) of IFP, Pondicherry.
%% Prepared by: Anil kumar Acharya (French Institute of Pondicherry).
%% NOTE that, although this work is very widely transmitted, 
%% the base edition is little more than a sloppy transcription of one Nepalese manuscript.
%% To go some way to compensate, I have collated just one South Indian source (IFP, T32).
%% But this text is still in a poor state and this electronic version does *not* claim to be 
%% a finished edition.  Furthermore, it is unfinished not simply because many editorial choices remain to be taken,
%% but also because the variants of many, many sources remain to be gathered.
%% The numbering of verses is not in accordance with the irregular numeration of the printed text
%% from which it has been prepared; rather, it is original to this electronic version.

%% A couple of general observations:
%% 1. In the South Indian transcription very often the word "rudra" replaces the word "śiva",
%% which occurs very often in Nepalese transcripiton.
%% 2. Both transcription seems influnced by their respective regions;
%% viz. In the list of the holy rivers tha name Tāmraparṇī is missing
%% in the Nepalese transcription but occurs in the south Indian transcription,
%% because of its South Indian origin.
%% Not proof-read

%% Chapter 1

%% p.1

atha paśupatimate śivadharmaśāstre śivabhaktirnāma prathamo.adhyāyaḥ|
śrī gaṇeśāya namaḥ| oṃ namaḥ śivāya|
%% The ascription, found at the beginning of each chapter, of the works of the Śivadharma-corpus to a Paśupatimata appears to be the invention of the editor.

devadeva mahādeva śāntaṅkamalalocana|
jagadārtiharaṃ devaṃ śūlapāṇinnamostute|| 1.1||

namas tuṅgaśiraścumbivandracāmaracārabhe|
trailokyanagarārambhe mūlastambhāya śambhave|| 1.2||

%% Above two verses are missing in T32
sarvakāraṇaśeṣasya jagataḥ sarvadā śivam|
% sarvakāramaśeṣasya \T32
gobrāhmaṇanṛpāṇāñca śivaṃ bhavatu sarvataḥ|| 1.3||

śivamādau śivaṃ madhye śivamante ca sarvadā|
sarveṣāṃ śivabhaktānāṃ manujānāñca naḥ śivam|| 1.4||

% anugānāṃ ca \T32
merupṛṣṭhe sukhāsinamṛṣisaṃghaiḥ samāvṛtam|
% merupṛṣṭhasamāsīnaṃ tryambakaṃ sa samāvṛtam| \T32
lokānugrahakartāraṃ sarvajñaṃ nandikeśvaram|| 1.5||

% lokānugrahakaṃ śāntaṃ \T32
teṣāṃ madhye samutthāya munibrahmasutottamaḥ|
sanatkumāraḥ sutapāḥ pṛcchati sma yathāvidhiḥ|| 1.6||

sanatkumāra uvāca
bhagavan sarvadharmajña śivadharmaparāyaṇaḥ|
% sarvadharmaparāyaṇa! \T32
śrotukāmāḥ paraṃ dharmamimaṃ sarve samāgatāḥ|| 1.7||

% ime sarve samāgatāḥ \T32
agniṣṭomādayo yajñā bahuvittakṛyānvitāḥ|
% bahuvittakriyānvitāḥ \T32
nātyantaphalabhūyiṣṭhā bahvāyāsasamanvitāḥ|| 1.8||

% nātyantaphala . . ṣṭhā \T32
na śakyante yataḥ kartum alpavittairdvijātibhiḥ|
% na śakyaṃ tairyataḥ \T32
sukhopāyamato brūhi sarvakāmārthasādhakam|| 1.9||

tasyopāyamato \T32
hitāya sarvasatvānāṃ śivadharmaṃ sanātanam|
% sarvamartyānāṃ \T32
% yena siddhāḥ surā daityā gandharvoragarākṣasāḥ| \T32
% ṛṣayaḥ kiṃnarā yakṣāstathā kiṃpuruṣādayaḥ| \T32
% vividhā"cānye śivadharmaparāyaṇāḥ| \T32
% sampūjyāḥ sasurāḥ sarve tadbhaktāḥ śivadhārmikāḥ| \T32
%% The above lines are missing in the printed edition from Nepal.
nandikeśvara uvāca
śrūyatāmabhidhāsyāmi sukhopāyamahatphalam|| 1.10||

% mahat tatphalam \T32
paramasarvadharmāṇāṃ śivadharmaṃ śivātmakam|
% paramaṃ sarvadharmāṇāṃ śivadharmaṃ śivo kam| \T32
śivena kathitaṃ pūrvaṃ pārvatyāḥ ṣaṇmukhasya ca|| 1.11||

gaṇānāṃ devamukhyānāmasmākañca viśeṣataḥ|
ajñānārṇavamagnānāṃ sarveṣāṃ prāṇināmayam|| 1.12||
śivadharmāntu yaḥ śrīmān uddhārārthamudāhṛtam|
% śivadharmoḍupaḥ śrīmān uttarārtha° \T32
%% p.2
yena yaṃ śāntacetaskaiḥ śivabhaktaiḥ śivārthibhi|| 1.13||

% ............... śivabhaktaiḥ śivādibhiḥ| \T32
saṃsevyate paro dharmaste rudro nātra saṃśayaḥ|
% rudrā \T32
ekakālaṃ dvikālaṃ vā trikālaṃ nityameva vā|| 1.14||
%% Above line is missing in T32;
% grāme vā yadi vāruṇye jale vāpi sthale.api vā|
% yatra dṛśyate liṃgaṃ sarvatīrthāni tatra vai| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in printed edition.

ye smaranti virūpākṣaṃ vijñeyāste gaṇeśvarāḥ|
kīrtayiṣyanti ye rudraṃ sakṛd apy aśubhair narāḥ|| 1.15||
% sakṛdapyāśutena vā \T32

sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyante saptajanmakṛtair api|
ye.arcayanti sadā rudraṃ na te prakṛti mānuṣāḥ|| 1.16||
% arcayanti \T32

rudralokāt paribhraṣṭāste rudrāste rudrā nātra saṃśayaḥ|
jātenātmadruhā yena nārcito bhagavan śivaḥ|| 1.17||
suciraṃ saṃsaratyasmin asāre duḥkhasāgare|
% saṃsāre duḥkhasāgare \T32
sahānistatmahacchidraṃ samohaḥ sāndhamūkatā|| 1.18||
% tasya cittaṃ mahaccitraṃ \T32
yaḥ kṣaṇaṃ vā muhūrtaṃ vā śarvameko nu cintayet|
% śivamekaṃ na cintayet \T32
durlabhaṃ prāpya mānuṣyaṃ ye.arcayanti sadā śivam|| 1.19||
% sadāśivam \T32
teṣāṃ hi saphalaṃ janma kṛtārthāste narottamāḥ|
śivabhaktiparā ye tu bhavapraṇatamānasaḥ|| 1.20||
% bhavapraṇatacetasaḥ \T32
bhavasaṃsmaraṇe yukta na te duḥkhasya bhāginaḥ|
% °saṃsmaraṇodyuktā te na duḥkhasya bhājanam| \T32
bhuvanāni manojñāni vicitrā.abharaṇāstriyaḥ|| 1.21||
% bhavanāni manojñāni bibhramabharaṇastriyaḥ| \T32
dhanaṃ vā tuṣṭiparyantaṃ śivapūjāvidherphalam|
% dhanaṃ cādṛṣṭaparyantaṃ \T32
ye vāñchanti mahābhogān rājyañca tridaśātmake|| 1.22||
% tridaśālaye \T32
te.arcayanti sadākālaṃ harasya caraṇāmbujam|
saubhāgyakāntimadrūpaṃ satyaṃ tyāgaprabhāvatām|| 1.23||
% saubhāgyaṃ kāntimadrūpaṃ satyaṃ tyāgaḥ prabhāvatā| \T32
śauryaṃśca jagataḥ khyātiṃ śivamarcayato bhavet|
% śauryaṃ ca jagati khayātiḥ śivamarcayato bhavet| \T32
nārudraḥ saṃsmaredrudraṃ nārudro rudramarcayet|| 1.24||
nārudraḥ kīrtayedrudraṃ nārudro rudramāpnuyāt|
śivadharmasya sāro.ayaṃ śive bhaktiḥ suniścalā|| 1.25||
sā cāṣṭāṅgī śivenoktā kāryā nityaṃ prayatnataḥ|

%% 

śrībhagavan uvāca
% śrībhagavan \T32
madbhaktajanavātsalyaṃ pūjāyāś cānumodanam|| 1.26||
% pūjāyāmanumodanam \T32
svayaṃ me.abhyarcanaṃ kuryāt mamārthe cāṅgaceṣṭitam|
% svayamabhyarcanaṃ bhaktyā \T32
matkathāśravaṇe bhaktiḥ svaranetrāṅgavikriya|| 1.27||
% °vikriyā \T32
mamānusaṃsmaren nityaṃ yaś ca mām upajīvati|
% mamānusmaraṇaṃ nityaṃ yaśca māṃ copajīvati| \T32
bhaktir aṣṭavidhā hy eṣā yasmin mleccho.api vartate|| 1.28||


sa viprendro muniḥ śrīmān sa yatiḥ sa ca paṇḍitaḥ|
%% p.3
na me priyaścaturvedo madbhaktaḥ śvapavo.api yaḥ|| 1.29||
% na me priyaścarvedī madbhaktaḥ śvapaco.api yaḥ| \T32
tasmai deyantato grāhyaṃ sa ca pūjyo yathāhyaham|
śivabhaktāya yaddānaṃ bhaktyā kiñcit pradīyate|| 1.30||
tadahantatra gṛhṇāmi tenānanta taducyate|
% tadahantatra \ conj; tadahantrattrigṛhṇāmi \ed
%% Above two lines 30cd - 31ab are missing in T32
patraṃ puṣpaṃ phalaṃ toyaṃ yo me bhaktyā prayacchati|| 1.31||
tasyāhaṃ na praṇasyāmi sa ca me na praṇasyati|
yo māṃ na sarvagamyaścennaraḥ sarva mayi sthitam|| 1.32||
% nārcayedyaḥ sadātmasthaṃ yo māṃ samayamāsthitaḥ| \T32
sa māṃ parvatadurgeṣu mārgamāṇo vipadyate|
yo māṃ sarvagataṃ paśyet sarvaśca mayi saṃsthitaḥ|| 1.33||
% sarvatragaṃ \T32
tasyāhaṃ nityamātmasthaḥ sa ca nityaṃ mayisthitaḥ|
nandikeśvaraḥ uvāca
% nandikeśvaraḥ \T32
sudurlabhā śive bhaktiḥ durlabhañca śivārcanam|| 1.34||
durlabhañca śive dānaṃ śivahomaśca durlabhaḥ|
% sudurlabhaṃ śive dānaṃ \T32
sudurlabhaṃ śivajñānaṃ tadabhyāso.api durlabhaḥ|| 1.35||
sudurlabhataraṃ yajñaṃ japadhyānaṃ śivātmakam|
sudurlabhā tapaḥprāptistadabhyāso.api durlabhaḥ|| 1.36||
%% Above verse 36 is missing in T32
sudurlabhamidaṃ jñātvā śavabhaktiṃ samāśrayet|
% śive bhaktiṃ \T32
ityeṣa vaḥ samāsena śivadharmo.akhilakramāt|| 1.37||
nirdiṣṭaḥ prathame.adhyāye śeṣo.asau ca pravistaraḥ|
%% The above two lines 37cd - 38ab are after line 40ab in T32
namastebhyo manuṣyebhyo ye śivaṃ śaraṇaṅgatāḥ|| 1.38||
% lābhasteṣāṃ manuṣyāṇāṃ ye śivaṃ śaraṇāgatāḥ| \T32
yeṣāṃ divā ca rātrau ca nityaṃ śivagatasmṛtiḥ|
% teṣāṃ \T32
namaskārādisaṃyuktaṃ śiva ityakṣaradvayam|| 1.39||
% śivāyetya . . . trayam| \T32
jihvāgre vartate yasya saphalantasya jīvitam|
imaṃ yaḥ paṭhate nityaṃ śṛuṇuyādvāpi bhaktitaḥ|| 1.40||
% ya idaṃ paṭhate nityaṃ śṛuṇuyādvā samāhitaḥ| \T32
sa muktaḥ sarvapāpaistu śivaloke mahīyate|
% vimuktaḥ sarvapāpebhyaḥ \T32
ḍākinyo vividhākārā rākṣasā pretanāyakāḥ|| 1.41||
na tasya pīḍāṅkurvanti tathānyepi hi hiṃsakāḥ|
% na tathānyepi hiṃsakāḥ| \T32
śatravo nāśamāyānti saṅgrāme jayamāpnuyāt|| 1.42||
sarvarogairnabādhyate āpado na spṛśanti tam|
% sa na rogeṇa bādhyeta na spṛśantyāpado.api tam| \T32
dhanamāyuryaśavidyāṃ prabhāvamatulaṃ labhet|| 1.43||
śubhenopacayaṃ yāti nityaṃ pūrṇamanorathaḥ|

\Colo
iti śivadharmaśāstre śivabhaktirnāma prathamo.adhyāyaḥ|
% iti śivadharmaśāstre prahtamo.adhyāyaḥ| \T32

%% p.4

%% Chapter 2

atha paśupatimate śivadharme mahāśāstre
śivadharmapraśnādhyāyo nāma dvitīyo.adhyāyaḥ|
namaḥ śivāya
sanatkumāra uvāca
% Missing in T32
liṅgārcanavidhiṃ puṇyaṃ śrotumicchāmi tattvataḥ|
tvatprasādādviśeṣeṇa bhagavannandikeśvara|| 2.1||
yat puṇyaṃ sthāpite liṅge kṛte yacca śivālaye|
sammārjane ca yatpuṇyaṃ yatpuṇyamupalepane|| 2.2||
nīrājanauṣadhī bīja snāne maṅgalavādane|
% bījāsnānamaṃgalavādane| \T32
puṇyaṃ yaccārghyadānena toyasnānena yadbhavet|| 2.3||
% toyasnānena ca yatphalam| \T32
pañcagavyapayasnāne dadhisnāne ca yadbhavet|
ghṛtasnāne ca yatpuṇyaṃ ghṛtābhyaṅge ca yatphalam|| 2.4||
% ghṛtābhyaṃge ca yatproktaṃ ghṛtasnāne ca yadbhavet| \T32
madhusnāne ca yat puṇyaṃ puṇyamikṣurasena ca|
% madhusnānena yatproktaṃ \T32
udvartanāntarasnāne kuśapuṣpodakena ca|| 2.5||
% udbartanāntarāsnānaṃ \T32
suvarṇaratnatoyaiśca gandhacandanavāribhiḥ|
% suvarṇaratnatoyaistu \T32
karpūrāgurutoyena svacchatoyena yatphalam|| 2.6||
% karpūrāgurutoyaiśca \T32
vilepanaiśca gandhādyairvilipte yatphalaṃ labhet|
% viliptena ca yatphalam| \T32
tālavṛntapradānena pradāne cāmarasya ca|| 2.7||
muktapuṣpārcane yacca mālayā liṅgapūraṇe|
% muktāpuṣpārcane yacca mālābhirliṃgapūraṇe| \T32
puṣpamaṇḍapakāryaśca puṣpamālāvalambane|| 2.8||
% puṣpamaṇḍapikāyāṃ ca \T32
pūjābhaktiviśeṣaiśca vedyāṃ mālāvaveṣṭane|
% pūjanoktaviśeṣaiśca vedyāmālāvalmbane| \T32
puṣpajātiviśeṣeṣu dhūpeṣvapi ca yatphalam|| 2.9||
% dhūpadīpe ca yat phalam| \T32
vastrālaṅkāradāne ca dīpadarpaṇadarśane|
bhakṣyabhojyānnapānādi phalakandanivedane|| 2.10||
pradakṣiṇe namaskāre praṇāmastotrajaṃ phalam|
% pradakṣiṇanamaskārapraṇāma° \T32
pratākādhvajachatrāṇāṃ ghaṃṭāvāditraśaṃkhayā|| 2.11||
% chatradhvajapatākānāṃ ghaṇṭāvāditraśaṃkhayoḥ| \T32
vitānavastrapūjāyāṃ balihome kriyāsu ca|
% balihomakriyāsu ca| \T32
gavāṃśca bhṛtyanāgānāṃ bhūmidāne ca yatphalam|| 2.12||
% gavagandhabhṛtyanāgānāṃ \T32
grāmakheṭapurāṇāśca daśadāne ca yatphalam|
% strīṇāṃ saṃgītadānena nāṭyenaiva viśeṣataḥ|| \T32
% svayaṃ mālyopahāreṇa puṃsāṃ puṇyaṃ tu yadbhavet| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
tatpālānāpahāre ca puṇyāpuṇyantu yadbhavet|| 2.13||
yatināmannadānāni pātropakaraṇāni ca|
% . . . . . nādi mātropakaraṇāni ca| \T32
datvā kiṃ labhate puṇyaṃ datvā cāpi pratiśrayam|| 2.14||
% kṛtvā vā tatpratiśrayam| \T32
% namaskāre tathā teṣāṃ pratyutthānābhivādane| \T32
% khaṭvā prāvaraṇādīni datvā yatphalabhāgbhavet|| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
yadapyanyadbhavet sūkṣmamajñānānna pracoditam|
tatsarvaṃ kathayāsmākaṃ bhaktānāmanukampayā|| 2.15||

\Colo
iti śivadharmapraśnādhyāyo dvitīyaḥ|
% iti śivadharmaśāstre dvitīyo.adhyāyaḥ| \T32

%% p.5

%% Chapter 3
%% 1694:2:26, A3

%%atha paśupatimate śivadharmaśāstre nandikeśvarapoktāyāṃ
%%saṃhitāyāṃ liṅgotpattirnāma tṛtīyo.adhyāyaḥ|
% liṅgātpattirnāma \ed
oṃ namaḥ śivāya
nandikeśvara uvāca
tvamatīva śive bhaktaḥ padmayonisutottama|
tena te nikhilaṃ vakṣye śṛṇuṣvekāgramānasaḥ|| 3.1||
pūrvamekārṇave ghore naṣṭe sthāvarajaṅgame|
vivādaḥ sumahānāsīd brahmāviṣṇoḥ parasparam|| 3.2||
% vivādastu \T32
ahaṃ kartā tvahaṃ kartā na madanojagatpatiḥ|
% ahaṃ kartā hyahaṃ kartā na matto.anyo jagatprabhuḥ| \T32
evamāha hariṃ brahmā brahmāṇaṃśca haristathā|| 3.3||
tayordarpāpahārāya prabodhārthaśca vetayoḥ|
% tayordarpāpahārārthaṃ prabodhārthaṃ ca devayoḥ| \T32
madhye samutthitaṃ liṅgamaiśvaryantejasaḥ param|| 3.4||
% madhye samabhavalliṅgaṃ aiśvaraṃ taijasaṃ param| \T32
jvālāmālāvṛtandivyam aprameyaguṇoditam|
% aprameyamanūpamam| \T32
yojanāyutavistīrṇaḥ sthitantadvimalenyapi|| 3.5||
% sthitaṃ tadvimalembhasi| \T32
jvālābhirmohitau tasya liṅgasya surasattamau|
% jvālābhirmohito tasya \T32
tadā vismayamāpannau paśyantāvamarādhipam|| 3.6||
% tato \T32
gatāvūrdhamadhastasya saṃpradhārya parasparam|
% śatādūrdhvamadhastasya \T32
adhovalambaye viṣṇoragādūrdhaṃ pitāmahaḥ|| 3.7||
% adho draṣṭuṃ gato viṣṇurūdhvaṃ caiva pitāmahaḥ| \T32
adṛṣṭvā tadadhaścordhvaṃ tau sametya parasparam|
% adṛṣṭvāntamadhaścordhvaṃ \T32
kṛtāñjalipuṭau bhūtvā liṅgantuṣṭavatustathā|| 3.8||
% tuṣṭuvatustadā| \T32
% anādi devadeveśa viśveśvara maheśvara| \T32
% sarvajña jñānavijñānapradāyaka namo.astu te|| \T32
% anantakānti  . . anantāsanasaṃsthita| \T32
% anantaśaktisambhoga parameśa namo.astu te|| \T32
% parāvaraparātīta utpattisthitikāraṇa| \T32
% sarvārthasādhanopāya viśeśvara namo.astu te|| \T32
% bahūrūpa mahārūpa sarvarūpa namo.astu te| \T32
% paśupāśārṇavātīta varaprada namo.astu te|| \T32
% svabhāvanirmalābhoga sarvavyāpin sadāśiva| \T32
% yogayogin mahāyogin yogeśvara namo.astu te|| \T32
% niraṃjana nirādhāra svādhāra niripaplava| \T32
% prasannaparameśāna yogeśvara namo.astu te|| \T32
% jvihvā capalabhāvena veditaṃ yo.asmi yanmayā| \T32
% tatkṣantavyamanaupamya kaste stauti guṇārṇavam|| \T32
% liṃgotpattistavaṃ puṇyaṃ yaḥ śṛṇoti narassadā| \T32
% notpadyate sa saṃsāre sthānaṃ prāpnoti śāśvatam|| \T32
% tasmātsarvaprayatnena śṛṇuyādvācayettathā| \T32
% pāpakaṃcukamutsṛjya prāpnoti paramaṃ padam|| \T32
%% Above verses of T32 occurs twice, once here and again at the end;
%% but in printed edition, from Nepal, these vereses occurs only at the end.
liṅgamadhye paraṃ liṅgaṃ sthitaṃ dvādaśasammitam|
% prādeśasaṃmitam| \T32
samādhistotrasampannau dṛṣṭavantau śivātmakam|| 3.9||
% dṛṣṭayantau śivātmakau| \T32
naiva tatkāñcanaṃ raupyaṃ tāmraṃ sphaṭikamauktikam|
% sphāṭikamauktikam| \T32
lakṣamātraṃ sthitaṃ śāntaṃ kevalavtacchivātmakam|| 3.10||
tayostuṣṭo mahādevaḥ provāca varamuttamam|
% tayostuṣṭau mahādevo pradadau \T32
kāraṇatvamanujñāya tatraivāntaradhīyata|| 3.11||
% kāraṇatvamanuktvā ca \T32
prāñjaliḥ praṇato viṣṇurbrahmāpi vedatatparaḥ|
% kṛtāñjalipuṭo viṣṇuḥ brahmā ca brahmatatparaḥ| \T32
pūrvaṃ liṅgaṃ samabhyarcya tadā kāryāṇi cakratuḥ|| 3.12||
% paścāt kāryāṇi cakratuḥ| \T32
