dambhamātsaryanirmuktā yathātathyaprabhāṣiṇaḥ|| 4.5||
% dambhamātmaryanirmuktāḥ yathātathyābhibhāṣiṇaḥ| \T32
samvibhāgaparaḥ prajñā aśaṭhāñcāpyakutsitāḥ|
% prājñāḥ aśaṭhāścāpyakutsitāḥ| \T32
viṣayeṣvapi nirlepāḥ padmapatramivāmbhasā|| 4.6||
na dīnā nāpi malinā na ca rogavaśānugāḥ|
% na ca roṣavaśaṃvadāḥ| \T32
bhavanti bhavitātmānaḥ śraddhāḥ sādhuniṣevitāḥ|| 4.7||
% bhavanti bhāvitātmānaḥ susnigdhāḥ sādhusevitāḥ| \T32
na pādapāṇivākcakṣuḥ śrotu śiśnodare budhā|
% śrotraśiśnavaśaṃgatāḥ| \T32
capalyaṃ naiva kurvanti sarvavyasanavarjitāḥ|| 4.8||
% cāpalāni na kurvanti sarvavyāsaṅgavarjitāḥ| \T32
rudrātmāno rudaparā rudrāṃśā rudrabhāvanāḥ|
% rudrāśā \ ed
% rudrāṃśā rudrabhāvitāḥ| \T32
ityācārasamāyuktāḥ bhavanti bhuvi mānavāḥ|| 4.9||
% evaṃvidhasamācārā \T32
ekāntabhaktimāsthāya guṇeṣveteṣu vartatāḥ|
% vartata| \T32
pūjanīyaḥ śivo nityaṃ parāparavibhūtaye|| 4.10||
kiñcidvedamayaṃ pātraṃ kiñcitpātraṃ tapomayam|
āgamiṣyati tatpātraṃ yatpātraṃ tārayiṣyati|| 4.11||
nandikeśvara uvāca
%% Missing in T32
sarveṣāmevapātrāṇāmatipātraṃ maheśvaram|
% maheśvaraḥ| \T32
yajanāt trāyate yasmādatīva narakārṇavāt|| 4.12||
% patanāt trāyate \T32
tasya pātrasya mahātmyāddānaṃ bhavati cākṣayam|
% dānamaṇvapi cākṣayam| \T32
tasmāttasmai sadā deyaṃ  aprameyaphalārthibhiḥ|| 4.13||
śive dattaṃ hutaṃ taptaṃ pūjāvalinivedanam|
ekasyānantaphaladaṃ tadbhavennātra saṃśayaḥ|| 4.14||
% ekaṃ vānantaphaladaṃ \T32
bhaktyā vittānusāreṇa kuryāt prasādasañcayam|
alpaṃ mahati vā puṇyaṃ tulyamāḍhyadaridrayoḥ|| 4.15||
% alpe mahati vā puṇyaṃ phalamāḍhyadaridyayoḥ| \T32
vittaśāṭhyena yaḥ kuryāddharmamāḍhyopi sa naraḥ|
% sannaraḥ\ ed
% yo naraḥ| \T32
na tatphalamavāpnoti pralobhākrāntamānasaḥ|| 4.16||
% na sa tatphalamavāpnoti \T32
tasmāttribhāgaṃ vittasya jīvanāya prakalpayat|
% prakalpayet \T32
bhāgadvayañca dharmārthamanityaṃ jīvitaṃ yataḥ|| 4.17||
bhaktyā pracoditaḥ kuryādalpavitto.api yo naraḥ|
% alpavitto.api mānavaḥ| \T32
mahāvibhavasāro.api na kuryādktivarjitaḥ|| 4.18||
% na kuryādbhaktivarjitaḥ| \T32
sarvasvamapi yo dadyācchive bhaktivivarjitaḥ|
nāsau dharmamavāpnoti bhaktirevātra kāraṇam|| 4.19||
% na tena bharmabhāk sa syāt \T32
na ca tapobhiratyugrairna ca sarvamahāmakhaiḥ|
gacchecchivaṃ puraṃ divyaṃ yuktabhaktirbhavātmakaḥ|| 4.20||
% muktvā bhaktiṃ śivātmikām| \T32
%% p.12
mṛṇmayaiṣṭaka śailaṃ vā yaśca kuryācchivālaye|
% mṛddā?rviṣṭakaśailaṃ vā yaḥ kuryādvai śivālayam| \T32
trisaptakulasaṃyukto rudraloke mahīyate|| 4.21||
% trissaptakulamuddhṛtya \T32
mṛṇmayātkoṭiguṇitaṃ puṇyaṃ syādārubhiḥ kṛte|
koṭikoṭiguṇaṃ puṇyaṃ dāravodiṣṭakāmaye|| 4.22||
% mṛtkāṣṭhādiṣṭakāmaye| \T32
aiṣṭakādviguṇaṃ puṇyaṃ śailaje syācchivālaye|
% iṣṭakādviguṇaṃ puṇyaṃ śailake \T32
mṛcchailayoḥ samaṃ jñyeyaṃ puṇyamāḍhyadaridrayoḥ|| 4.23||
yatra tatra yataḥ kuryāt kartuḥ puṇyaṃ śileṣṭayoḥ|
% yatra kvāpi gataḥ puṇyaṃ kṛtaṃ śaileṣṭakādibhiḥ| \T32
navaṃ purāṇe rahitaṃ tasmāt kuryācchivālayam|| 4.24||
aṣṭoṣṭakālamāyuktaṃ yaḥ prakuryācchivālayam|
% aṣṭeṣṭakāsamāyuktaṃ \T32
vidhūya pāpasaṃghātaṃ so.api gacchechivālayam|| 4.25||
% krīḍamāno.api yaḥ kuryādbālabhāve śivālayam| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
rudraloke labhetso.api vimānaṃ sarvakāmikam|
puṣpamālāparikṣiptaṃ divyagandhopaśobhitam|| 4.26||
dolāvikṣepasaṃyuktaṃ ghaṇṭācāmarabhūṣitam|
% ḍolāvikṣepasaṃyuktaṃ \T32
muktādāmavitānena śobhitaṃ sūryasamprabham|| 4.27||
apsarogaṇasaṅkīrṇaṃ sarvakāmasukhapradam|
% sukhaprabham| \T32
tatroṣitvā mahābhogaiḥ koṭikoṭyayutaṃ sukhī|| 4.28||
% mahābhoge \T32
kramādāgatya loke.asmin rājā bhavati dhārmikaḥ|
% dūrataḥ śikharaṃ dṛṣṭvā namaskuryācchivālayam| \T32
% saptajanmakṛtaṃ pāpaṃ kṣiprameva vinaśyati|| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
dṛṣṭvā pariharejjantun mārjanyā mṛdusūkṣmayā|| 4.29||
% paśyanpariharañjantra mārjanyātyatisūkṣmayā| \T32
śanaiḥ savmārjanaṃ kurvan cāndrāyaṇaphalaṃ labhet|
nāhārapratijīrṇāyā vandhyāyāḥ kṣīṇavatsayoḥ|| 4.30||
% nāhāravaśajīrṇāyā vandhyāyāḥ kṣīṇavatsayā| \T32
rogārtāyāḥ prasūtāyā gośca gomayamāharet|
% rogārā navasūtā yā bhogbhyo gomayamāharet| \T32
khasaṃsthaṅgomayaṃ grāhyaṃ sthāne vā patitaṃ śubhe|| 4.31||
uparyadhastāt saṃtyajya pratyagraṃ jantuvarjitam|
% uparyadhaśca \T32
vastrapūtena toyena yaḥ kuryādupalepanam|| 4.32||
paśyan pariharan jantūn cāndrāyaṇaphalaṃ labhet|
yaḥ kuryāt sarvakāryāṇi vastrapūtena vāriṇā|| 4.33||
sa muniḥ sa mahāsādhuḥ sa yogī sa śivaṃ vrajet|
kṣaranti sarvadānāni yajñahomavalikriyāḥ|| 4.34||
na kṣarante mahādānamabhayaṃ sarvado hi mām|
% na tu kṣarenmahādānaṃ abhayaṃ sarvadehinām| \T32
nairantaryeṇa yaḥ kuryāt pakṣaṃ sammārjanārcanam|| 4.35||
% pakṣasammārjanāṃ janam| \T32
yugakoṭiśtaṃ divyaṃ śivaloke mahīyate|
tasyānte sa caturvedaḥ surūpaḥ priyadarśanaḥ|| 4.36||
% tadante sa caturvedaḥ svarūpaḥ \T32
ādyaḥ sarvaguṇopeto rajā bhavati dhārmikaḥ|
% āḍhyaḥ \T32
%% p.13
samparkeṇāpi yaḥ kuryānnaraḥ kumbhaṃ śivālaye|| 4.37||
so.api dehakṣaye jñānaṃ prāpya śāntimavāpnuyāt|
rudradevanikāyeṣu kaścijjñānamavāpnuyāt|| 4.38||
% rudradevanikāryeṣu \T32
kaścidevātra midinyālbdhvā jñānaṃ vimucyate|
% kaścideva tu medinyāṃ labdhvā jñānaṃ vimuṃcate| \T32
tāvadbhramanti saṃsāre duḥkhaśokapariplutāḥ|| 4.39||
na bhavanti śive bhaktā yāvatsarvepi dehinaḥ|
samāsaktaṃ yathācittaṃ jantorviṣayagocare|| 4.40||
% bhavedviṣayagocarāḥ| \T32
yadi nāma śivepyevaṃ ko na mucyeta bandhanāt|
ya kuryat kuṭṭimāṃ bhūmiṃ darpaṇodarasannibhām|| 4.41||
% yaḥ kuryātkuṭṭimaṃ bhūmiṃ darpaṇodarasannibham| \T32
nānāvarṇavicitrāṃ vā vicitrakusumākulām|
% ca vicitrakuṣumojvalam| \T32
kvacitkalaśavinyāsāṃ paṅkajairupaśobhitām|| 4.42||
% kvacitkalaśavinyastāṃ paṃkajādyupaśobhitām| \T32
manobhiramyā saumyāśca śivāyatanasaṃsadi|
% (mano)ramāṃ ca kusumāṃ \T32
yāvaddaṇḍā bhavebhūmiḥ samantācca suśobhanā|| 4.43||
% yāvaddhastā bhavedbhūmiḥ samantādupaśobhitā| \T32
tāvadyugasahasrāṇi rudraloke mahīyate|
sudhāpraliptaṃ yaḥ kuryāt sarvayatnaiḥ śivālayam|| 4.44||
% sudhāviliptaṃ \T32
tāvatpuṇyaṃ labhetso.api yāvadāyatane kṛte|
pratyantaṃ yaḥ prakurvīta śambhorāyatanaṃ budhaḥ|| 4.45||
% pratyabdaṃ \T32
dhavalaṃ kṣīrasudhayā yathāśobhiśca varṇakaiḥ|
% dhavalaṃ sūta sudhayā yathāśobhaṃ ca varṇakaiḥ| \T32
yāvatyahāni kurute dhavalaṃ cacchivālayaṃ|| 4.46||
% yāvantyabdāni kurute dhvalaṃ tacchivālayaṃ \T32
tāvadyugasahasrāṇi rudraloke mahīyate|
kārayeccitraśāstrajñaiḥ yatnāccitraṃ śivālaye|| 4.47||
rudrāvatārakrīḍādyaiḥ prayogairāgamoditaiḥ|
yāvatsa rudrarūpāṇi surūpāṇi tu lepayat|| 4.48||
% yāvanti rudrarūpāṇi svarūpāṇyapi lekhayet| \T32
tāvadyugasahasrāṇi rudraloke mahīyate|
%% In T32 the above verses 47cd - 49ab occurs after verse 44ab (of this edition).
khaṇḍasphaṭitasaṃskāraṃ yaḥ kuryāttu śivālaye|| 4.49||
% khaṇḍasphuṭitasaṃskāraṃ yaḥ kurvīta śivālaye| \T32
ārāmāvasathādyeṣu labhate maulikaṃ phalam|
% ārāmāvasathe vāpi \T32
nāsti rudrasamo devo nāsti rudrasamo guruḥ|| 4.50||
nāsti rudrasamaḥ jñānaṃ nāsti rudrasamantapaḥ|
% evaṃ śivāśramārāmaṃ kṛtvā saṃskārapūrvakam| \T32
% kṛtvālpamapi vā bhaktyā idaṃ stotramudīrayan|| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
nirdhautamalapaṅkāya svabhāva malamūrtaye|| 4.51||
% nirddhūtamaladehāya svabhāvāmalamūrtaye| \T32
sitabhasmāṅgarāgāya deveśāya namostute|
nīlakaṇṭhāya śarvāya ajāyāmitamūrtaye|| 4.52||
bahūrūpāya śāntāya śāśvatāya namostu te|
mahābhogīndrahārāya piṅgalocanacārave|| 4.53||
% mahābhogīndrabhūṣāya piṃgalocanarocaye| \T32
vicitraracitāṅgāya anantāya namostu te|
% vicitracaritāḍhyāya \T32
%% p.14
parātparapareśāya sarvagāya mahātmane|| 4.54||
% parāya parameśāya sarvajñāya namostu te| \T32
atītaguṇasaṃghāya viśveśāya namostu te|
%% In T32 the above two lines 54cd & 55ab occurs after verse 53ab (of this edition).
sarvapraṇatadevāya svayamapraṇatātmane|| 4.55||
% sarvapraṇatadehāya \T32
pūjyānāmapi pūjyāya anāthāya namostu te|
% pūjyāya namastryakṣāya śūline| \T32
brahmendraviṣṇuvandyāya utpattisthitihetave|| 4.56||
bhuktimuktipradānāya samstutāya namostu te|
vāmāya vāmarūpāya vāmacārāya bhāvine|| 4.57||
% vāmacārāya gāmine| \T32
vāmakāntārdhadehāya anantāya namostu te|
% īśānāya namostute| \T32
ya idaṃ kīrtayennityaṃ prāsādādhyāyamuttamam|| 4.58||
sarvapāpavinirmukto sa gopatyamavāpnuyāt|
% śivasāyujyamavāpnuyāt| \T32

\Colo
iti śivadharmaśāstre nandikeśvaraproktāyāṃ saṃhitāyām
āyatanādhyāyaścaturthaḥ|
% iti śivadharmaśāstre prāsādādhyāyo nāma caturtho.adhyāyaḥ| \T32

%% Chapter 5

atha paśupatimate śivadharmaśāstre śivārcanadravyavidhirnāma pañcamo.adhyāyaḥ|
oṃ namaḥ śivāya
nandikeśvara uvāca
% śrīnandikeśvaraḥ \T32
liṅgamūrtamaheśasya śivasya parameṣṭhinaḥ|
% liṅgamūrtermaheśasya \T32
snānakāle prakurvīta jayaśabdābhimaṅgalam|| 5.1||
triśūlavajraśaṃkhā.ava śrīvatsasvastikādibhiḥ|
% triśūlavajraśaṃkhābja \T32
hemaraupyādipātreṣu kalpitairgomayādibhiḥ|| 5.2||
% hemarūpyādipātreṣu \T32
nānāvarṇakasaṃyuktai rakṣitaistilatuṇḍalaiḥ|
% nānāvarṇai(śca ku)sumairakṣataistilataṇḍulaiḥ| \T32
bhaktaiśca dadhisaṃyuktai yathāśobhaṃ prapūritaiḥ|| 5.3||
% siddhārthadadhisammiśraiḥ yathāśobhaṃ ca pūritaiḥ| \T32
dravyaiḥ piṣṭapradīpādyaiścūtāśvatthādipallavaiḥ|
% uccairyaṣṭipradīpādyaiḥ cūtāśvatthādipallavaiḥ| \T32
oṣadhībhiśca medhyābhiḥ sarvabījairyavādibhiḥ|| 5.4||
% sarvabījairyavāṃkuraiḥ| \T32
divaseṣūttameṣu ca parvakāleṣu sarveṣu|
aṣṭamyādiṣu sarveṣu puṣpapūrṇābhiparvaṇi|| 5.5||
% aṣṭamyādiṣu sarveṣu divaseṣūtsaveṣu ca| \T32
% parvakāleṣu sarveṣu puṇyapauṇādiparvaṇi|| \T32
śaṃkhabheryādinirghoṣairmahāgeyasvarairyutaiḥ|
% mahadbhirgeyasaṃyutaiḥ| \T32
kuryānnīrājanī liṅgaṃ śivamuddiśya maṅgalaiḥ|| 5.6||
% kuryānnirājanaṃ liṅge \T32
yāvatparvāṇi vidhinā kuryānnīrājanaṃ śive|
% vidhivat \T32
tāvadyugasahasrāṇi rudraloke mahīyate|| 5.7||
snānakāle trisandhyāśca yaḥ kuryād geyavādinaḥ|
% snānakāle trisandhyaṃ ca yaḥ kuryād geyavādanam| \T32
nṛtyaṃ vā mukhavādyaṃ vā tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu|| 5.8||
% nṛttaṃ vā \T32
%% p.15
yāvantyahāni kurute geyanṛtyādivāditam|
% geyanṛtyādivādanam| \T32
tāvadvarṣasahasrāṇi rudraloke mahīyate|| 5.9||
% śivaloke mahīyate| \T32
kapilāpañcagavyena kuśavāriplutena ca|
% kuśavāriyutena ca| \T32
snāpayenmantrapūtena brahmasnānaṃ hi tatsmṛtam|| 5.10||
ekāhamapi pyoliṅge brahmasnānaṃ samācaret|
% ekāhamapi yo liṅge \T32
vidhūya sarvapāpāni śivaloke mahīyate|| 5.11||
% savidhūyāśu pāpāni rudraloke mahīyate| \T32
kapilā pañcagavena dadhikṣīraplutena ca|
% dadhikṣīraghṛtena ca| \T32
snānaṃ śataguṇaṃ jñeyaṃ tarusnānānna saṃśayaḥ|| 5.12||
% itarasmānna saṃśayaḥ| \T32
devāgnikāryamuddiśya dehaśuddhiṃśca śāśvatīm|
% devadāryaṃ samuddiśya dehaśudhyarthameva ca| \T32
kapilāmāharettasmānmunidevādinirmitām|| 5.13||
% munidevādivandhitām| \T32
kāpilyaṃ yaḥ pivecchūdraḥ śivasaṃskāravarjitaḥ|
% kāpilāṃ yaḥ pivecchūdraḥ śivakāryārthanirmitām| \T32
pacyate sa mahāghore suciraṃ narakārṇave|| 5.14||
% sa pacyate mahāghore suciraṃ narakārṇave| \T32
varṣakoṭisahasreṣu yatpāpaṃ samupārjitam|
ghṛtābhyaṅgena liṅgasya dahetsarvanna saṃśayaḥ|| 5.15||
kalpakoṭisahasreṇa yatpāpaṃ samupārjitam|
% kalpakoṭisahasreṣu \T32
ghṛtasnānena tatsarvaṃ dahatyagnirivendhanam|| 5.16||
% ghṛtābhyaṅgena liṅgasya \T32
kṛṣṇāṣṭamyāṃ ghṛtasnānaṃ kṛtvā liṅge sakṛnnaraḥ|
kulaikaviṃśamuddhṛtya śivaloke mahīyate|| 5.17||
ayutaṃ yo gavāndadyāddogdhrīṇaṃ vedapārage|
vastrahomādiyuktānāṃ kṣīrasnānena tatphalam|| 5.18||
% vastrādihemayuktānāṃ gṛtasnānena tatphalam| \T32
sakṛdāḍakena payasā yo liṅgaṃ snāpayennaraḥ|
% sadāḍhakena payasā \T32
rājatena vimānena somalokaṃ sa gacchati|| 5.19||
% somaloke mahīyate| \T32
dadhnā tu snāpayelliṅgaṃ sakṛdbhaktyāpi yo naraḥ|
sarvapāpavinirmukto viṣṇuloke mahīyate|| 5.20||
% snāpya dadhnā sakṛlliṅgaṃ viṣṇuloke mahīyate| \T32
madhunā snāpayelliṅgaṃ sakṛdbhaktyāpi yo naraḥ|
sarvapāpavinirmukto vahniloke mahīyate|| 5.21||
% madhunā snāpayitvā tu vahnilokaṃ  sa gacchati| \T32
snāpayettilatailena hastayastrodbhavena ca|
% hastayantrodbhavena ca| \T32
śvetapītakapuṣpairvā vāyuloke mahīyate|| 5.22||
% śvetapītakapiṣṭairvā \T32
snānamikṣurasenāpi yo liṅgaṃ sakṛdācaret|
labhedvaidyādharaṃ lokaṃ sarvakāmasamanvitam|| 5.23||
phalodakena yo liṅgaṃ sakṛtsnāpayate naraḥ|
% bhaktyā snāpayate naraḥ| \T32
utsṛjya pāpakalitaṃ pitṛloke mahīyate|| 5.24||
sitena bhasmanāsnāpya sakṛlliṅgaṃ pramodate|
candrāṃśunirmalaḥ śuddhaḥ śivavatsomamaṇḍalam|| 5.25||
% candrāṃśunirmalaḥ śrīmān śivavatsomamaṇḍale| \T32
%% p.16
vastrapūtena toyena yo liṅgaṃ snāpayennaraḥ|
sarvakāmasu tṛptātmā vāruṇaṃ lokamāpnuyāt|| 5.26||
kuśodakena yo liṅgaṃ sakṛtsnāpayate naraḥ|
% bhaktyā snāpayate sakṛt| \T32
kāñcanena vimānena brahmaloke mahīyate|| 5.27||
gandhacandanatoyena snāpayetsakṛdīśvaram|
gāndharvalokamāpnoti gandharvaiśca sa pūjyate|| 5.28||
puṣpodakena sāvitraṃ kaiveraṃ hemavāriṇā|
ratnodakena cāpyaindraṃ lokaṃ prāpya sa modate|| 5.29||
% ratnodakena māhendraṃ \T32
pāṭalotpalakhaṇḍāni karavīrāṇi sarvadā|
% pāṭalotpalapadmāni \T32
snānakāleṣu yojyāni sthirāṇi surabhīṇi ca|| 5.30||
% snānatoyeṣu \T32
eṣāmekatamaṃ snānaṃ kṛtvā tu bhaktitaḥ śive|
% yaḥ kuryādbhaktitaḥ śive| \T32
vibhūya pāpakalilaṃ śivaloke mahīyate|| 5.31||
karpūrāgarutoyena yo liṅgaṃ snāpayennaraḥ|
% yo liṅgaṃ snāpayet sukṛt| \T32
sarvapāpavinirmuktaḥ śivaloke mahīyate|| 5.32||
mantrāṣṭaśatajaptena vimalenāmbhasā śivam|
snāpayitvā sakṛdbhaktyā śivalokamapāpnuyāt|| 5.33||
% śivaloke mahīyate| \T32
snāpya liṅgaṃ sakṛddadhnā kṛṣṇāṣṭamyāmupoṣitaḥ|
kulasaptakamuddhṛtya śivaloke mahīyate|| 5.34||
%% Above verse 34 is missing in T32
pitṝnuddiśya lo liṅgaṃ snāpayecchītavāriṇā|
tṛptāḥ svargaṃ gamiṣyanti pataro narakādapi|| 5.35||
% prayāsyanti \T32
liṅgaṃ śītāmbunā snāpya dhāroṣṇapayasā tataḥ|
snāpya paścāt ghṛtasnānaṃ tata eva viśiṣyate|| 5.36||
% ghṛtenāpi kṛtamekaṃ viśiṣyate| \T32
evaṃ snānatrayaṃ kṛtvā pūjayitvā tu bhaktitaḥ|
% etatsnānatrayaṃ \T32
aśvamedhasahasrasya phalamāpnoti mānavaḥ|| 5.37||
mṛtkumbhāttāmrajaiḥ kumbhaiḥ snānaṃ śatagoṇottaram|
raupyairlakṣottraṃ puṇyaṃ haimyaiḥ koṭyadhikaṃ bhavet|| 5.38||
% raupyaṃ \T32
liṅgasya darśanaṃ puṇyaṃ darśanātsparśanaṃ śubham|
sparśanādarcanaṃ śreṣṭhaṃ ghṛtasnānamataḥ param|| 5.39||
ihāmutra kṛtaṃ pāpaṃ ghṛtasnānena dehinām|
kṣamate śaṃkaro yasmāttasmātsnānaṃ samācaret|| 5.40||
ekaviṃśaḥ kulopetaḥ krīḍate divi rudravat|
snānaṃ palaśataṃ jñeyamabhyaṅgaṃ pañcaviṃśatiḥ|| 5.41||
% jalasnānaṃ palaśataṃ(jñeyaṃ) abhyaṃgaḥ pañcaviṃśatiḥ| \T32
%% p.17
phalānāṃ dvisahasrāṇāṃ mahāsnānaṃ prakīrtitam|
% phalānāṃ dve sahasre tu mahāsnānaṃ ... bhaktitaḥ| \T32
ghṛtābhyaṅge ghṛtasnāne yatnālliṅgaṃ virukṣayet|| 5.42||
% virūkṣayet| \T32
ye na godhūmajaiścūrṇaiḥ kaṣāyairgandhayojitaiḥ|
% yavagodhūmajaiścūrṇaiḥ toṣayadgandhayojitaiḥ| \T32
sukhoṣṇenāmbhasā vāpi snāpayettadanantaram|| 5.43||
gharṣayedvilvapatraiśca tatpīṭhañca viśodhayet|
% tava pīṭhaṃ ca śodhayet| \T32
daśadhenusahasrāṇi yaddatvā labhate phalam|| 5.44||
% daśakoṭisahasrāṇi \T32
tatphalaṃ labhate sarvaṃ liṅgasyodvartane kṛte|
% labhate martyo \T32
arghyaṃ puṣpajalopetaṃ yaḥ śivāya nivedayet|| 5.45||
sa pūjyate sarvalokaiḥ śivavanmodate ciram|
% sapūjya sarvalokeṣu \T32
gandhodakena sanmiśramudakārghaṃ śatottaram|| 5.46||
% daśottaram| \T32
pañcagayasamāyuktamarghaṃ lakṣaguṇottaram|
% arghyaṃ śataguṇaṃ bhavet| \T32
yoṣṭāṅgamarghaṃ sampūrṇaṃ śivamūrdhni nivedayet|| 5.47||
% arghyamaṣṭāṃgamāpūrya liṅgamūdhni nivedayet| \T32
daśavarṣasahasrāṇi rudraloke mahīyate|
āpaḥ kṣīrakuśāgrāṇi dadhisarpissataṇḍulam|| 5.48||
% āpaḥ kṣīraṃ kuśagrāṇi dadhyājyaṃ ca sataṇḍulam| \T32
tilāḥ siddhārthakāścaiva aṣṭāṅgorghaḥ prakīrtitaḥ|
% tilasiddhārthakaiścaivaṃ ardhyo.aṣtāṃgāḥ prakīrtitaḥ| \T32
dāraveṇārghapātreṇa datvārghyaṃ yatphalaṃ bhavet|| 5.49||
% dāruveṇvarghyapātreṇa yaddatvā labhate pahalam| \T32
tasmāddaśaguṇaṃ puṇyaṃ mṛtpātreṇa prakīrtitam|
% tasmācchataguṇapuṇyaṃ \T32
tāmrapātrārghadānena puṇyaṃ śataguṇottaram|| 5.50||
% tāmrapātre \T32
palāśatāmrapātrābhyāṃ tāmrapātrasamaṃ bhavet|
% palāśapadmapatrāṇāṃ tāmrapātre \T32
rūpyapātreṇa vijñeyamarghaṃ śataguṇottaram|| 5.51||
% ropyapātreṇa vijñeyamarghyaṃ lakṣaguṇottaram| \T32
suvarṇapātravinyastamarghaṃ koṭiguṇottaram|
% arghyaṃ \T32
evaṃ snānārghanaivedyabalidhūpādiṣu kramāt|| 5.52||
pātrāntaraviśeṣeṇa tatphalañcottarottaram|
%% The above two lines 52cd & 53ab are missing in T32.
raupyapātrapradānena yatpuṇyaṃ vedapārage|| 5.53||
% yatphalaṃ \T32
tasmācchataguṇaṃ puṇyaṃ śive mṛtpātradānataḥ|
% śivamṛtpātradānataḥ| \T32
hemapātrāṇi yaddatvā puṇyaṃ sādvedapārage|| 5.54||
tāmrapātrapradānena tasmācchataguṇaṃ bhavet|
% tasmācchataguṇaṃ śive| \T32
palakoṭisuvarṇasya yo dadyādvedapārage|| 5.55||
śivāya raupyapātreṇa tasya puṇyaṃ tatodhikam|
hemapātrāṇi yo bhaktyā śivāya vinivedayet|| 5.56||
% hemapātraṃ tu yo bhaktyā \T32
na śakyaṃ tatphalaṃ vaktuṃ puṇyānantyādaśeṣataḥ|
% na tasya śakyate vaktuṃ puṇyānantyaṃ viśeṣataḥ| \T32
tulyameva phalaṃ proktaṃ śivenāḍhyadaridrayoḥ|| 5.57||
% śive cāḍhyadaridrayoḥ| \T32
