% vaivatatphalamāpnoti \T32
tasmāt patraiḥ phalaiḥ puṣpairnaivedyādyaistu yatphalam|| 5.59||
% tāvatpatraiḥ phalaiḥ puṣpaiḥ toyādyaiścaiva yatkṛtam| \T32
tadanantaphalaṃ jñeyaṃ bhaktirevātra kāraṇam|
liṅgasya lepanaṃ kuryāddvivyagandhaiḥ sugandhibhiḥ|| 5.60||
% liṅgasyālepanaṃ kuryāt \T32
varṣakoṭiśataṃ divyaṃ śivaloke mahīyate|
gandhānulepanātpuṇyaṃ  dviguṇaścandanasya tu|| 5.61||
% dviguṇaṃ candanasya tu| \T32
