% candanāgarukarpūraiḥ kṛṣṇapiṣṭaiḥ \T32
liṅgaṃ paryāptamālipya kalpakoṭiśataṃ divi|
% kalpakoṭiṃ vaseddivi| \T32
saṃvījya tālavṛntena liṅgamebhiḥ pralepitam|| 5.64||
daśavarṣasahasrāṇi vāyuloke mahīyate|
% varṣakoṭisahasrāṇi \T32
bhaktyā nivedya rudrāya tālavṛntaṃ suśobhanam|| 5.65||
% suśobhanam(bhitam)| \T32
daśavarṣasahasrāṇi labhate paramaṃ padam|
% rudraloke mahīyate| \T32
māyūravyajanandatvā śivāyātīvaśobhanam|| 5.66||
% mayūravajanam \T32
varṣakoṭiśataṃ divyaṃ śivaloke mahīyate|
% varṣakoṭiśataṃ puṇyaṃ \T32
datvā śivāya cāmaraṃ maṇidaṇḍavibhūṣitam|| 5.67||
% śivāya cāmaraṃ datvā \T32
