daśadatvā suvarṇāni yatphalantadavāpnuyāt|
% śvetarkasya viśeṣeṇa dviguṇaṃ phalamiṣyate| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
evaṃ puṣpaviśeṣeṇa phalaṃ tadadhikaṃ bhavet|| 5.73||
