yāvattatpatrakusumaṃ bījamūlaphalāni ca|| 5.115||
tāvadvarṣasahasrāṇi rudraloke mahīyate|
lakṣā prāṇyaṅganirmuktaṃ dhūpaṃ datvā sakṛcchive|| 5.116||
% lakṣāṃ prāmāṇyanirmuktasūpaṃ dadyāt sakṛcchive| \T32
caturvedagṛhe janma prāpnoti satataṃ sukhī|
% caturvedīgṛhe janma \T32
kṛṣṇāguruśca karpūraṃ dhūpaṃ dadyānmaheśvarī|| 5.117||
% kṛṣṇāgarusakarpūraṃ dhūpaṃ dadyānmaheśvare| \T32
tairantaryeṇa māsārdhaṃ tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu|
kalpakoṭisahasrāṇi kalpakoṭiśatāni ca|| 5.118||
bhuktvā śivapure bhogān tasyānte tu mahīpatiḥ|
% tasyāpyante mahīpatiḥ| \T32
guggulaṃ ghṛtasaṃyuktaṃ sākṣādgṛhṇāti śaṅkaraḥ|| 5.119||
māsārdhaṃ mātra dānena śivaloke mahīyate|
% māsārdhamātra \T32
śive kṛṣṇacaturdaśyāṃ yāmārdhaṃ guggulaṃ dahet|| 5.120||
% yaḥ sājyaṃ gugguluṃ dahet| \T32
aparādhasahasraikamihāmutrakṛtaṃ kṣayet|
% aparādhasahasraṃ tat \T32
devadārunnameruśca sarjaśrīvāsakundaram|| 5.121||
śrīphalaṃ cājya saṃyuktaṃ dagdhvāpnoti parāṃgatim|
% śrīphalaṃ cājyasaṃmiśraṃ datvāpnoti parāṃ śriyam| \T32
ebhyaḥ sugandhikaṃ dhūpaṃ ṣaṭsahasraguṇottaram|| 5.122||
% sugandhikarpūraṃ \T32
agurordaśasāhasraṃ saghṛtaṃ dviguṇaṃ bhavet|
% agaruṃ daśasāhasraṃ dviguṇaṃ cāsitāgarum| \T32
gugguloḥ śatasāhasraṃ saghṛtaṃ dviguṇaṃ bhavet|| 5.123||
% gugguluṃ \T32
priyaśca guggulordhūpa ājyayukto viśeṣataḥ|
% guggulurnityaṃ \T32
palānāntu mahiṣākṣasyaddhigugguloḥ|| 5.124||
% dve sāhasre phalānāṃ tu mahiṣākṣasya gugguloḥ| \T32
dagdhatvenājyamiśrasya śivatulyaḥ prajāyate|
% dagdhvājyena tu saṃmiśraṃ \T32
%% p.22
na meruṃ ghṛtasaṃyuktaṃ dagdhvā bilvamathāpi vā|| 5.125||
% agaruṃ ghṛtasaṃyuktaṃ  . . . . . phalāni ca| \T32
agniṣṭomasya yāgasya phalaṃ prāpnoti mānavaḥ|
śodhayet pāpasaṃyuktaṃ puruṣannātra saṃśayaḥ|| 5.126||
kṛṣṇāgurostu yo dhūpaistuṣāgniriva kāñcanam|
% kṛṣṇāgarudbhavo bhūpaḥ \T32
yo.antaḥ śivagṛhaṃ gandhaiḥ sugandhaiśca pralepayet|| 5.127||
% bhaktyā sugandhena pralepayet| \T32
kapāṭadvāramudghāṭya tiryagūrdhvaṃ savedikam|
% kavāṭadvārakuḍyāntaṃ \T32
vāsayetpuṣpamālābhiḥ dhūpaiścāpi sugandhibhiḥ|| 5.128||
% śvāsayetpuṣpamālābhiḥ \T32
yaḥ kuryāt sakṛdapyevaṃ puṇyantasyāvadhārayaḥ|
sarvakāmasusampūrṇairmahāyānaiḥ sahasraśaḥ|| 5.129||
% sarvakāmaiśca sampūrṇo \T32
āpūrayandiśaḥ sarvā āmodaiśca sugandhibhiḥ|
% āpurāyaṃ diśaḥ sarvāḥ \T32
kalpakoṭiśatandivyaṃ śivaloke mahīyate|| 5.130||
% rudraloke mahīyate| \T32
tasyānte dharmaśeṣeṇa trailokyā.adhipatirbhavet|
vātāvṛttau tu yaḥ kuryādevaṃ gandhaiḥ śivālayam|| 5.131||
% ṛtāvṛtau ca yaḥ kuryād \T32
sa samastakulopetaḥ śivatulyabalo bhavet|
% śivaloke mahīyate| \T32
trivṛcchuklaṃ supītaṃ vā padmasūtrādinirmitam|| 5.132||
% padṛsūtrādinirmitam| \T32
gandhopavītaṃ rudrāya datvā vedāntago bhavet|
% datvopavītaṃ rudrāya bhavedvedāntagocaraḥ| \T32
vāsāṃsi suvicitrāṇi surabhīṇi mṛduni ca|| 5.133||
% sāravanti mṛdūni ca| \T32
dhūpitāni śive dadyādakleśyāni navāni ca|
vikeśāni navāni ca| \T32
yāvantadvastratantūnāṃ parimāṇaṃ vidhīyate|| 5.134||
% yāvattatvastratantūnāṃ parimāṇaṃ samantataḥ| \T32
tāvadvarṣasahasrāṇi śivaloke mahīyate|
% tāvadyugasahasrāṇi rudraloke mahīyate| \T32
truṭimātrantu yo dadyāddhemaṃ liṅgasya mūrdhani|| 5.135||
indrasyārdhāsane tiṣṭhed yāvadindrāścaturdaśa|
% indrasyārdhāsane tāvad \T32
evamevānusāreṇa phalaṃ jñeyaṃ samāsataḥ|| 5.136||
% evaṃ vittānusāreṇa phalaṃ jñeyaṃ samāsataḥ| \T32
sarveṣāmeva hemānāṃ mukuṭānāñca sarvaśaḥ|
% sarveṣāṃ maṇipaṭṭānāṃ mukuṭāderviśeṣataḥ| \T32
yorkaparṇapuṭaṃ pūrṇāṃ ghṛtena madhunā saha|| 5.137||
% yorkapatrapuṭaṃ pūrṇaṃ madhuparkaṃ sumantritam| \T32
nivedayīta śarvāya sośvamedhaphalaṃ labhet|
% nivedayeta \T32
śālitaṇḍulaprasthena śūrvādinā susaṃskṛtam|| 5.138||
% śālināṃ taṇḍulaṃ prasthaṃ kuryādannaṃ susaṃskṛtam| \T32
śivāya taccaru dadyāta caturdaśyāṃ viśeṣataḥ|
haridrāṃ kṛsarāṃ śuklāṃ pāyasaṃ yāvasaṃ tathā|| 5.139||
% hāridraṃ kṛsaraṃ śuklaṃ pāyasṃ vā caruṃstathā| \T32
guḍakhāṇḍājyasammiśram evamannaṃ prakalpayet|
% °sammiśraṃ naivedyaṃ parikalpayet| \T32
yāvantastaṇḍulā tasminnaivedye parisaṃkhyayo|| 5.140||
% parisaṃkhyayā| \T32
tāvadvarṣasahasrāṇi rudraloke mahīyate|
guḍakhaṇḍakṛtānāñca bhakṣyāṇāṃ vinivedane|| 5.141||
% bhakṣyāṇāṃ ca nivedane| \T32
ghṛtena pācitānāṃ yaddatvā daśaguṇaṃ phalam|
% ghṛtena pacitānāṃ tu puṇyaṃ śataguṇaṃ bhavet| \T32
%% p.23
bharjitāyānnakādīnāṃ bhakṣyārdhaṃ phalamiṣyate|| 5.142||
% majjikāpānakānāṃ tu \T32
tadardhaṃ salilasyāpi vāsitasya nivedane|
mātuluṅgaphalādīni supakvāni nivedayet|| 5.143||
% pakvāni ca nivedayet| \T32
śivāya tatphalaṃ tasya bhakṣāṇāṃ vinivedayet|
% bhakṣyāṇāṃ yannivedane| \T32
% pañcasaugandhikopetaṃ tāmbūlaṃ ca nivedayet| \T32
% śivāya gurave caiva tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu| \T32
% sugandhadehastejasvī sarvāvayavasundaraḥ| \T32
% varṣakoṭiśataṃ divyaṃ śivaloke mahīyate| \T32
%% Above four lines are not in the printed edition, from Nepal.
ghṛtapradīpadānena śivāya śatayojanam|| 5.144||
alaṃghitvātamogacchedvimānaiḥ sūryasaprabhaiḥ|
% laṃghayitvā tato yāti vimānaiḥ sūryasaprabhaiḥ| \T32
% gacchecchivapuraṃ divyaṃ yāvadābhūtaviplavam| \T32
% tasyānte sa mahīpālo brāhmaṇo vā.abhijāyate| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
yaḥ kuryātkārtike māsi śobhanāndīpamālikām|| 5.145||
ghṛtena ca caturdaśyām amāvāsyām athāpi vā|
% ghṛtenaiva \T32
sūryāyutapratikāśastejasā bhāsayandiśaḥ|| 5.146||
% °pratikāśaiḥ tejobhir \T32
tejorāśivimānasthaḥ kulamudyotya sarvaśaḥ|
% kulamuddhṛtya \T32
yāvatpradīpasaṃkhyānaṃ ghṛtenāpūrya bodhitam|| 5.147||
tāvadyugasahasrāṇi rudraloke mahīyate|
dīpavṛkṣaṃ susamṛddhaṃ śarvasyāyatanaṃ śubham|| 5.148||
% lohamuccaṃ śivālaye| \T32
pūrvasmādviguṇaṃ puṇyaṃ labhate nātra saṃśayaḥ|
dīpavṛkṣaṃ susamṛddhaṃ śobhayucca śivālaye|| 5.149||
datvā kalpāyutaṃ sāgraṃ śivaloke mahīyate|
%% Above two lines 149cd & 150ab are missing in T32
% kāpilena ghṛtenaiva sūkṣmatantukṛtena ca| \T32
% sakṛddipaṃ śive dadyāt tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu| \T32
% sūryakoṭipratīkāśaiḥ vimānaiḥ sārvakāmikaiḥ| \T32
% gacchetso.api śivaṃ lokaṃ yāvadābhūtasamplavam| \T32
% tasyā .............................. dehasamanvitaḥ| \T32
% jñānayogaṃ samādāya tatraiva sa vimucyate| \T32
%% The above lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
śirasā dhārayeddīpaṃ sarvarātraṃ śivālaye|| 5.150||
lalāṭe vāpi hastābhyāmudyuktaśca tathorasi|
% vātha \T32
sūryakoṭipratīkāśairvimānaiḥ sarvakāmikaiḥ|| 5.151||
% sūryāyutapratīkāśaiḥ \T32
kalpāyutasahasrāṇi śivaloke mahīyate|
% kalpāyuta śataṃ divyaṃ rudraloke mahīyate| \T32
śivasya puroto dadyāddarpaṇañcāpinirmalam|| 5.152||
% darpaṇaṃ cāru nirmalam| \T32
paryantaśobhitaṃ kṛtvā śvetamālyaiḥ sacandanaiḥ|
candrāṃsunirmalaḥ śrīmatsubhagaḥ kāmarūpadhṛk|| 5.153||
kalpāyutasahasrāṇi śivaloke mahīyate|
% rudraloke \T32
kṛtvā pradakṣiṇā bhaktyā śivasyaivaṃ yathāvidhi|| 5.154||
% śivasyobhayathā naraḥ| \T32
sarvayajñopavāseṣu sarvayajñeṣu yatphalam|
%% The above line is missing in T32
aśvamedhasahasrasya sukhena labhate phalam|| 5.155||
% labhate phalamuttamam| \T32
namaskāraḥ smṛto yajñaḥ sarvayajñottamottamaḥ|
% sarvayajñottamaḥ śive| \T32
namaskṛtvā mahādevamaśvamedhaphalaṃ labhet|| 5.156||
praṇamya daṇḍavadbhūmau namaskāreṇa yo.arcayet|
sa yāṅgatimavāpnoti na tāṃ yajñaśatairapi|| 5.157||
sarvayajñopavāseṣu sarvatīrthes.u yatphalam|
stutijapyopahāreṇa sarvantatphalamāpnuyāt|| 5.158||
% śive tatphalamāpnuyāt| \T32
śvetaṃ mahādhvajaṃ datvā kṛtvā vāsaśca raṅgikam|
% kṛtvā vai ṣaṃcaraṃgikam| \T32
%% p.24
kiṅkiṇīrutasampanna mayūrachatrabhūṣitam|| 5.159||
% kiṃkiṇīravakopetaṃ \T32
etenaiva vimānena sarvadevopari shtitam|
% sa sitena vimānena sarveṣāṃ copari sthitaḥ| \T32
saṃvatsarasahasraikaṃ modate divi rudravat|| 5.160||
% manvantarasahasraṃ tu \T32
dhvajamālākulaṃ kuryāt yathāproktaṃ śivālayam|
% prākārālayamadhyataḥ| \T32
mahādhvajāṣṭakaṃ vāpi digvidikṣu nivedayet|| 5.161||
sa vimānasahasreṇa divyadhvajasuśobhinā|
% divyāśvapariśobhinā| \T32
kalpāyutasahasrāgraṃ modate divi rudravat|| 5.162||
śaraccandrāṃśuvimalaṃ muktādāmopaśobhitam|
% muktāmālopaśobhitam| \T32
maṇidaṇḍamayaṃ chatraṃ dadyādvā kāñcanānvitam|| 5.163||
% maṇidaṇḍamavacchatraṃ dadyāt kāñcananirmitam| \T32
sa chatreṇa vimānena dhāryamāṇena śobhinā|
% sachatraiśca vimānaiśca dhāryamāṇaiśca śobhitam| \T32
vimānaśatasambhogaiściraṃ śivapure vaset|| 5.164||
% vimānaiḥ sarvasaṃbhogaiḥ ciraṃ śivapuraṃ vrajet| \T32
yadi vā rājyamākāṃkṣetsadeho kālaparyayāt|
% yadi cedrājyamākāṃkṣed dehī kālaviparyayāt| \T32
bhuṃkte samudraparyantāmekachatrāvasundharām|| 5.165||
śṛṅkhalābhiḥ samāyuktāṃ mahāghaṇṭāṃ mahāsvanām|
% yaḥ śṛṅkhalā samāyuktāṃ \T32
kāṃsyalohamayī vāpi nivadhnīyācchivālaye|| 5.166||
% bandhayedyo śivālaye| \T32
ghaṇṭākarṇagaṇaḥ śrīmān śivasyātīvavallabhaḥ|
śivatulyabalobhūtvā śivaloke vasecciram|| 5.167||
% śivaloke mahīyate| \T32
bherīmṛdaṅgamurujantimilaṃ paṭahādikam|
% bherīmṛdaṅgamuravatimilo \T32
vaṃśakāṃśyādivāditraṃ śivāya vinivedayet|| 5.168||
% yaḥ śivāya vinivedayet| \T32
savimānairmahābhogairvaṃśavīṇākṛtasvanaiḥ|
yugāyutaśataṃ divyaṃ śivaloke mahīyate|| 5.169||
strīsaṅgītakadānena sanāṭyena viśeṣataḥ|
% strīṇāṃ saṅgītadānena \T32
yatheṣṭamaiśvare loke modate kālamakṣayam|| 5.170||
mahanmahāsvanaṃ dadyācchaṅkhayugma śivālaye|
% mahāsvanaṃ tu yo dadyācchaṃkhayugmaṃ śivāya tu| \T32
yugakoṭimahābhogaiḥ śivaloke mahīyate|| 5.171||
% yugakoṭiśataṃ divyaṃ rudraloke mahīyate| \T32
vimānaṃ sitapadmābhaṃ madhye padmavibhūṣitam|
% vitānaṃ sitapadmābhaṃ madhye kamalabhūṣitam| \T32
vicitramekavarṇaṃ vā navavastropaśobhitam|| 5.172||
% nānāvarṇopaśobhitam| \T32
kiṅkiṇīravakopetaṃ candrakaiścopaśobhitam|
% kandukaiścopaśobhitam| \T32
lambakaiḥ sūtradāmaiśca ghaṇṭārutavibhūṣitam|| 5.173||
% lambakairmuktādāmaiśca ghaṇṭācāmarabhūṣitam| \T32
śivasyopari yo dadyātpurato vāpi kalpayet|
rudravat sarvalokeṣu yugakoṭi sa modate|| 5.174||
śivasyopari yo dadyāt sarvaratnopaśobhitam|| 174||
maṇḍapaṃ mauktikaṃ śrīmān tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu|
% maṇḍanaṃ \T32
koṭikoṭivimānaistu sarvakāmasamanvitaḥ|| 5.175||
%% p.25
ābhūtasampravaṃ yāvadāste śivapure sukhī|
% yāvat tāvacchivapure vaset| \T32
śarvasyāyatane kuryādvastrapūtāṃ suśobhanām|| 5.176||
% vastrapūjāṃ suśobhanam| \T32
dukūlapaṭṭadevāṅgaiḥ suvastraiḥ varṇakānvitaiḥ|
% varṇakāñcitaiḥ \ed
% vatrairanyaiśca śobhanaiḥ| \T32
paṭṭāvivastratantūnāṃ parisaṃkhyā tu yāvatī|| 5.177||
% vastrādipaṭṭatantūnāṃ (bhavet)saṃkhyā tu yāvati| \T32
tāvadyugasahasrāṇi rudraloke mahīyate|
śivabhaktyā jagatkṛtsnaṃ dṛṣṭidvāreṇa dhāryate|| 5.178||
% vṛṣṭisāreṇa sāryate| \T32
yatsaṃdhāryaṃ jagatpuṇyamagnikāryeṇa tadbhavet|
ya kuryādiṣṭakāgāraṃ rudrāgneratiśobhanam|| 5.179||
tatra kṛtvāgnikāryañca śivaloke mahīyate|
% sakṛttatrāgnikāryeṇa rudrasāyujyamāpnuyāt| \T32
śivāgnikāryaṃ yaḥ kuryādāyuṣaścāpi cātmanaḥ|| 5.180||
% yaḥ kṛtvā kuryāttryāyuṣamātmanaḥ| \T32
mucyate daśabhirpāpaiḥ sitena śivabhasmanā|
% daśabhirmucyate pāpaiḥ sitena śivabhāvanā| \T32
kṛtvā śivālayaṃ prānte daśamaṇḍalakāni tu|| 5.181||
% śivālayaprānte \T32
sarvāgrapākasaṃyuktaṃ tatra nityaṃ baliṃ haret|
% sarvapākāgrasaṃyuktaṃ teṣu nityaṃ baliṃ haret| \T32
puṣpadhūpajalopetaṃ tāmrapātre prakalpayet|| 5.182||
% arghyaṃ puṣpajalopetaṃ \T32
rudramātṛgaṇādīnāṃ divyatīnāñca sarvataḥ|
% devatānāṃ ca sarvataḥ| \T32
yaḥ kuryātsakṛdapyevaṃ daśadikṣu balikriyām|| 5.183||
daśavarṣasahasrāṇi rudraloke mahīyate|
rudrasandhyābalindatvā nityaśarvāśrame niśi|| 5.184||
% raudraṃ sandhyābaliṃ kṛtvā nityaṃ parvasu vā niśi| \T32
kalpāyutasahasrāṇi śivaloke mahīyate|
% kalpāyutaśataṃ sāgraṃ śivaloke mahīyate| \T32
dadhibhaktamayaṃ liṅgaṃ hemapātrādiṣu sthitam|| 5.185||
% hemapātrādisaṃsthitam| \T32
puṣpadhūpārcitaṃ kṛtvā divyamālyopaśobhitam|
% vimānopari śobhitam| \T32
śirasā dhārayetpātraṃ śanaiḥ kuryātpradakṣiṇam|| 5.186||
% śanairgacchetpradakṣiṇam| \T32
śivāyatanaparyantaṃ śaṅkabheryādinisvanaiḥ|
darpaṇadhvajamālābhi sarvaṃ kuryāt suśobhanam|| 5.187||
% darpaṇairdhvajamālābhiḥ geyanṛttādibhiḥ saha| \T32
chatracāmaradhūpādyairyaṣṭidīpādibhistathā|
% citracāmaradhūpādyaiḥ \T32
taccheṣa dadhibhaktena liṅgasya purataḥ sthitaḥ|| 5.188||
% taccheṣaṃ dadhibhaktena liṅgasya purataḥ sthitam| \T32
puṣpākṣatādisammiśraṃ sarvadikṣu baliṃ kṣipet|
% puṣākṣatavimiśreṇa pīṭhe tadupasaṃharet| \T32
etena mātaro raudrā śivomāṣaṇmukhādayaḥ|| 5.189||
% rudro śivo vā ṣaṇmukhādayaḥ| \T32
śāntiṃ kurvanti suprītā raudreṇa balinā tadā|
% śāntiṃ juṣanti \T32
śivamālyopanayanaṃ pūjānteṣu pramārjanam|| 5.190||
% śivamāhyāpanayanaṃ pūjānte bhūpramārjanam| \T32
ekaikameva tulyaṃ syāccāndrāyaṇaphalena tu|
śivamaṇḍalakaṃ vṛttaṃ hastamātraṃ śivāgrataḥ|| 5.191||
% śivamaṇḍalakaṃ kṛtvā \T32
avakīryākṣataiḥ puṣpaiḥ patrairvāpyatha komalaiḥ|
% yaḥ kuryādakṣataiḥ puṣpaiḥ patrairvāpyatha kevalaiḥ| \T32
surupaḥ subhagaḥ śrīmān tejasvī vedavitsukhī|| 5.192||
%% p.26
caturvedagṛhe janma sa kṛtvā labhate naraḥ|
% caturvedīgṛhe janma sakṛtkṛtvā labhennaraḥ| \T32
evaṃ svastikapadmādyairbhūriśobhāṃ śivālaye|| 5.193||
% bhūmiśobhā śivālaye| \T32
kṛtvā varṇakapiṣṭādyaiḥ tasmācchataguṇaṃ labhet|
% °cchataguṇaṃ bhavet| \T32
śivayajñopakaraṇaṃ kṛtvālpaṃ yadi vā bahuḥ|| 5.194||
% datvālpaṃ \T32
bhāvaṃ vittānusāreṇa śivaloke mahīyate|
% sa ca vittānusāreṇa \T32
śivamuddhiśya yaddattaṃ tatsarvaṃ muktikāraṇam|| 5.195||
% sarvakāraṇakāraṇam| \T32
tadanantaphalṃ dātuṃ bhatīti kimadbhutam|
% dāturbhavatīti \T32
yadiṣṭañca viśiṣṭañca nyāyena ca yadātam|| 5.196||
% yadyadiṣṭaṃ viśiṣṭaṃ ca nyāyena samupārjitam| \T32
tacchivāya nivedyaṃ syādbhaktyānantaphalārthibhiḥ|
karma śāṭhyena yaḥ kuryānmūlenāpi śivālaye|| 5.197||
% mūlyenāpi śivālaye| \T32
tepi śaṭhā divaṃ yānti karmaṇā pāpavarjitāḥ|
% so.api śāṭhyāddivaṃ yāti pāpavarjitakarmaṇā| \T32
kūpārāmādivāpyādyaiḥ śivāyatanakarmaṇi|| 5.198||
% kṛtvārāmānnapānādi śivāyatanakarmasu| \T32
upayuktāni bhūtāni khananotpāṭanādiṣu|
akāmato.api sarvāṇi carāṇi sthāvarāṇi ca|| 5.199||
divaṃ yānti na sandehaḥ prabhāvātharameṣṭhinaḥ|
liṅgāddhastaśatasāgraṃ śivakṣetraṃ samantataḥ|| 5.200||
% liṅga hastaśataṃ sāgraṃ \T32
dehināṃ tatra pañcatvaṃ śivasāyujyakāraṇam|
% dehināṃ tatra maraṇaṃ \T32
manujaiḥ sthāpite liṅge kṣatramānamidaṃ bhavet|| 5.201||
% idaṃ smṛtam| \T32
svāyambhuvasahasraṃ syādārṣe caivaṃ tadardhikam|
% svyaṃ bhūte sahasraṃ syāt ārṣe caiva tadardhakam| \T32
pāpācāro.api yastasminnāyācchivapuraṃ smṛtam|| 5.202||
% pa . . . naro.api yastasmin nivaseta śivālaye| \T32
% sa yāti paramaṃ sthānaṃ tasmācchivapuraṃ mahat| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
tasmādāvasathaṃ kuryācchivakṣetrasamīpataḥ|
śivakṣetrasamīpasthaṃ yattoyaṃ purataḥ sthitam|| 5.203||
% purataḥ śubham| \T32
śivagaṅgeti vijñeyaṃ tatra snātvā śivaṃ vrajet|
% śivagaṅgetitajjñeyaṃ \T32
grāme vā yadaraṇye vā yatra devo maheśvaraḥ|| 5.204||
tatra tatra kurukṣetraṃ naimiṣaṃ vāpi puṣkaram|
%% The above two lines are missing in T32
yaḥ kuryāddīrghikāṃ vāpi kūpaṃ cāpi śivālaye|| 5.205||
trisaptakulasaṃyuktaḥ śivaloke mahīyate|
% trisaptakulamuddhṛtya \T32
sarvamanyatparityajya śivaikāhitamānasaḥ|| 5.206||
śivapūjāvidhiṃ kuryādyadicchecchubhamātmanaḥ|
tvaritaṃ jīvitaṃ yāti tvaritaṃ yāti yauvanam|| 5.207||
tvaritaṃ vyādhirabhyeti sampūjyo bhagavan śivaḥ|
% tasmātpūjyaḥ sadā śivaḥ| \T32
yāvannāyāti maraṇaṃ yāvannākramate jarā|| 5.208||
yāvannendriyavaikalyaṃ tāvatpūjaya śaṅkaram|
na śivārcanatulyosti dharmo.atra bhuvanatraye|| 5.209||
% na śivārcanato hyasti dharmo.anyo \T32
%% p.27
iti vijñāya yatnena pūjanīyaḥ sadāśivaḥ|
ye bhaktyā devadeveśe śive śānte aje vibhau|| 5.210||
% ye bhaktyā devadevasya śivasya parameṣṭhinaḥ| \T32
nyāyārjitāni dravyāṇi arpayanti svaśaktitaḥ|
%% The above line is missing in T32
ihaloke sukhaṃ prāpya te yānti paramaṃ padam|| 5.211||
% vidanti varamaṃ padam| \T32
sampūjyo paśubhartāraṃ prahṛṣṭenāntarātmanā|
% viśuddhenāntarātmanā| \T32
kṛtāñjalipuṭo bhūtvā bhaktyāstotramudīrayet|| 5.212||
% idaṃ stotramudīrayet| \T32
śivaṃ śivakaraṃ śāntaṃ śivātmānaṃ śivottamam|
% śivottamaḥ| \T32
śivamārgapraṇetāraṃ praṇamāmi sadā śivam|| 5.213||
% sadāśivam| \T32
śāśvataṃ śobhanaṃ śuddhaṃ śāsakaṃ doṣaśoṣakam|
% smaraddoṣapramokṣakam| \T32
viśvaṃ viśveśvaraṃ devaṃ śaṅkaraṃ praṇamāmyaham|| 5.214||
sarvapāpaharannāthaṃ sarvadoṣaharaṃ param|
% sarvapāpaharaṃ nāthaṃ sarvarogaharaṃ śubham| \T32
sarvavyādhiharaṃ nityaṃ namāmyārtiharaṃ param|| 5.215||
% sarvabādhaharaṃ nityaṃ \T32
asthānaṃ sthānasatsthānaṃ saṃsthitaṃ sthitibhāvanam|
% saṃsthitasthitibhāsakam| \T32
sthiramātmathayogasthaṃ sthāṇvīśaṃ praṇamāmyaham|| 5.216||
% śirasthānasthayogasthaṃ \T32
īśānaṃ varadaṃ devamiśānaṃ mantranāyakam|
% īśānamantanāyakam| \T32
%% In T32 the above line 217ab occurs after verse 217 (of this edition).
% īśānaṃ puruṣaṃ ghoraṃ vāmaṃ sadyaṃ maheśvaram| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
īśānaṃ sarvabhūtānāmīśānaṃ praṇamāmyaham|| 5.217||
% īśvaraṃ praṇamāmyaham| \T32
iyaṃ pūjāvidhiṃ puṇyaṃ yaḥ śṛṇoti sakṛnnaraḥ|
% iti pūjāvidhiṃ \ t32
sa muktaḥ sarvapāpaistu śivalokamavāpnuyāt|| 5.218||
% sarvapāpebhyaḥ śivaloke mahīyate| \T32

\Colo
iti śivadharme śivārcanadravyavidhiḥ pañcamo.adhyāyaḥ|
% iti śivadharmaśāstre śivārcanadravyapuṇyaṃ nāma pañcamo.adhyāyaḥ| \T32

%% Chapter 6
atha paśupatimate śivadharmaśāstre
nandikeśvarapraṇīte śāntyādhyāyo nāma ṣaṣṭho.adhyāyaḥ|
oṃ namaḥ śivāya|
nandikeśvara uvāca|
% śrīnandikeśvaraḥ \T32
ataḥ paramidaṃ guhyaṃ rudrādgītaṃ mahodayam|
% śivodgīṇaṃ \T32
mahāvighnapraśamanaṃ mahāśāntikaraṃ śubham|| 6.1||
akālamṛtyuśamanaṃ sarvavyādhinivāraṇam|
% akālamṛtyumathanaṃ \T32
paracakraprathamanaṃ sarvadā jayavardhanam|| 6.2||
% sadā vijayavardhanam| \T32
% stambhanaṃ parasainyasya ripusādakaraṃ sadā| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
sarvadevagrahānīkaṃ samabhīṣṭaphalapradam|
% sarvābhīṣṭāvabhāsakam| \T32
sarvaśāntyādhikārākhyaṃ dharmaṃ vakṣyāmi śāśvatam|| 6.3||
%% p.28
śaśāṅkārdhadharastryakṣo nāgayajñopavītakaḥ|
% nāgayajñopavītavān| \T32
caturmukhaścaturbāhuḥ sitabhasmāvaguṇṭhitaḥ|| 6.4||
varo vareṇyo varado devadevo maheśvaraḥ|
trailokye namitaḥ śrīmān śāntimāsśu karotu me|| 6.5||
% trailokyanamitaḥ \T32
sarvāvayavapūrṇena gātreṇa tanumadhyamā|
% sarvāvayavamukhyena \T32
pītaśyāmātisaumyena snigdhavarṇena śobhanā|| 6.6||
% śivarūpeṇa sevitaḥ| \T32
lalāṭe tilakopetā candrarekhārdhadhāriṇī|
% lalāṭatilakopetā candralekhārdhadhāriṇī| \T32
citrāmbaradharā devī sarvābharaṇabhūṣitā|| 6.7||
% divyāmbaradharā devī \T32
varastrīmayarūpeṇa śobhāguṇamahāspadā|
% varastrī sarvanārīṇāṃ śobhāguṇamahāspadam| \T32
bhāvanāmātrasantuṣṭā umādevi varapradā|| 6.8||
sākṣādāgatya rūpeṇa śāntenāmitatejasā|
% sākṣādāgamya rūpeṇa \T32
śāntiṃ karotu me prītā bhaktānāṃ bhaktavatsalā|| 6.9||
padmarāgadyutiḥ saumye raktamālyānulepanaḥ|
abālo bālarūpeṇa ṣaḍvaktraḥ śikhivāhana|| 6.10||
% ṣaṇmukhaḥ \T32
pūrṇenduvadanaḥ saumyastriśikhaḥ śaktisaṃyutaḥ|
% triśikhā \T32
kṛttikomāgnirudrāṃśasamudbhūtaḥ surārcakaḥ|| 6.11||
% kṛttikomāgnirudrāṃga gaṃgodbhūtaḥ surārcitaḥ| \T32
kārtikeyo mahātejo varadānaikatatparaḥ|
% mahātejā \T32
śāntiṃ karotu me nityaṃ balaṃ saukhyañca me sadā|| 6.12||
% saukhyañca sarvadā| \T32
śvetavastraparīdhānastryakṣaḥ kanakasuprabhaḥ|
% kanakasaprabhaḥ| \T32
śūlapāṇi mahāprājño nandīśaḥ śivabhāvitaḥ|| 6.13||
% śūlapāṇirmahāprājño \T32
śivārcanaparonityaṃ śivadhyānaikatatparaḥ|
% śivadhyānaikaparamaḥ śivabhaktiparāyaṇaḥ| \T32
śāntiṃ karotu me śānto dharme ca matimuttamam|| 6.14||
mahodaro mahākāyaḥ snigdhāñjanacayacchaviḥ|
ekadaṃṣṭrotkaṭo devo gajavaktro mahābalaḥ|| 6.15||
%% Above verse 15 is missing in T32
nāgayajñopavīti ca nānābharaṇabhūṣitaḥ|
% nāgābharaṇa° \T32
sarvārthasampadādhāro gaṇādhyakṣo varapradaḥ|| 6.16||
rudrasya tanayo devo nāyako.atha vināyakaḥ|
karotu me mahāśāntiṃ karmasiddhiñca sarvadā|| 6.17||
indranīlanibhastryakṣo dīptaśūlāyudhodyataḥ|
raktāmbaradharaḥ śrīmān kṛṣṇāṅgo nāgabhūṣaṇaḥ|| 6.18||
pāpāpanodanamalam alakṣmīmalanāśanam|
% pāpāpanodamatulaṃ alakṣmīmalanāśanaḥ| \T32
karotu me mahāśāntiṃ mahākālo mahābalaḥ|| 6.19||
% karotu me mahākālaḥ prītiṃ prītena cetasā| \T32
pītavastraparīdhānā kanyārūpāsvalaṅkṛtā|
gaṇamātāmbikāstryakṣā puṇyā gaurīśvareśvarī|| 6.20||
% °mbikā tryakṣā puṇyā gaurī sureśvarī| \T32
%% p.29
sarvasiddhikarī devī prasādaparamāparā|
% sarvasiddhipradā devī prasādaparamā śivā| \T32
śāntiṃ karotu me mātā siddhaścānu prayacchatu|| 6.21||
% °me prītā siddhimāśu prayacchatu| \T32
snigdhaśyāmena varṇena mahāmahiṣamardanam|
% mahāmahiṣamardanī| \T32
dhanuścakrapraharaṇā khaḍgapaṭṭisadhāriṇī|| 6.22||
% śaṃkhayaṣṭyasidhāriṇī| \T32
ātarjanyudyatakarā sarvopadravanāśanī|
% ātarjanyodyatakarā \T32
sarvamaṅgala mātā me śivamācaratu dhruvam|| 6.23||
niemāṃsena śarīreṇa snāyvasthisunibandhanaḥ|
%% The above two lines 23cd & 24ab are missing in T32.
atisūkṣmo.ativikāntastryakṣo bhṛṅgiritirmahān|| 6.24||
% bhṛṃgiriṭirmahān| \T32
rudrātmajo mahāvīro rudraikāhitamānasaḥ|
% rudrātmajo rudrabhakto rudraikagatamānasaḥ| \T32
sopi me śāntabhāvena śāntimāśu prayacchatu|| 6.25||
% sopi śāntātmabhāvena \T32
pracaṇḍagaṇasainyeśo mahāṭaṃkākṣadhārakaḥ|
% pracaṇḍagaṇasaivyastho \T32
akṣamālārpitakara tryakṣaścaṇḍeśvaro varaḥ|| 6.26||
% caṇḍeśvaraḥ prabhuḥ| \T32
caṇḍapāpāpaharaṇo brahmahatyādiśodhanaḥ|
karotu me mahāyogī kalyāṇānāmparamparām|| 6.27||
% nityaṃ kalyāṇavardhanam| \T32
śaṅkhakundendutulyābhaḥ kaṇṭhe marakataprabhaḥ|
akṣamālī śivāgrasthaḥ svayaṃ jñānavyavasthitaḥ|| 6.28||
% akṣamālāśirograstu svayaṃ jñāne vyavasthitaḥ| \T32
caturmukhaścatuḥpādastrinetraḥ sarvadojjvalaḥ|
% °catuṣpādaḥ \T32
kṣitipatirvṛṣo devo dharmo dharmatamottamaḥ|| 6.29||
% kṣiteḥ patirvarayo devaḥ sarvadharmottamottamaḥ| \T32
īśaṃ vahati pṛṣṭhena tasmāddharmo jagatprabhuḥ|
vṛṣo vṛṣavaraḥ śrīmān karotu mama śāntikam|| 6.30||
% vṛṣo vṛṣapatiḥ śrīmān \T32
padmāsanaḥ padmanibhaḥ caturvadanapaṅkajaḥ|
kamaṇḍaludharaḥ śrīmān devagandharvapūjitaḥ|| 6.31||
śive dhyānaikaparamaḥ śivasadbhāvabhāvitaḥ|
% śivadhyānaikanirataḥ \T32
brahmaśabdena divyena brahmaśāntiṃ karotu me|| 6.32||
% brahmāśāntiṃ \T32
tārkṣāsanaścaturbāhuḥ śaṅkacakragadādharaḥ|
% tārkṣyāsana° \T32
śyāmaḥ pītāmbaradharo mahābalaparākramaḥ|| 6.33||
% vanamālāvibhūṣitaḥ| \T32
yajñadehottamo devo mādhavo madhusūdanaḥ|
% yajñadevottamo devo \T32
śivaprasādasampannaḥ śivadhyānaparāyaṇaḥ|| 6.34||
% śivapraṇāmaparamaḥ śivadhyānaikatatparaḥ| \T32
sarvapāpapraśamakaḥ sarvāsuranikṛntakaḥ|
%% The above line 35ab is missing in T32.
sarvadā śāntabhāvena viṣṇuḥ śāntiṃ karotu me|| 6.35||
% śivārcanaparo nityaṃ \T32
ārhantaḥ śāntacetaṣka viśvātman viśvayātitaḥ|
digvāsāmalapaṅkaśca saumyacittasamāhitaḥ|| 6.36||
saṃvartalocanaḥ śāntaḥ śivajñānaikacintakaḥ|
śāntiṃ karotu me śāntaḥ śivayogena bhāvitaḥ|| 6.37||
%% p.30
jitendriyaḥ samādhisthaḥ pātracīvarabheṣitaḥ|
varadābhayapāṇiśca jñānadhyānarataḥ sadā|| 6.38||
yogadṛṣṭiḥ sadāyuktaḥ śivajñānena bhāvitaḥ|
śāntiṃ karotu me deva sarvasatvahite rataḥ|| 6.39||
pītavarṇena dehena hāreṇa suvicitriṇā|
sarvāṅgasundarī devi vijayā jayakāriṇī|| 6.40||
śivārcanaratā nityaṃ śivajāpyaparāyaṇā|
dharitrī lokamātā ca nityaṃ rakṣāṃ karotu me|| 6.41||
kṣīrodādutthito gāvo lokānāṃ hitakāmyayā|
prīṇayanti sadā devān viprāṃścaiva viśeṣataḥ|| 6.42||
nityaṃ tu devatātmānaḥ kurvantu mama śāntikam|
%% Verses 36-43ab are missing in T32.
padmarāgaprabhā devi caturvadanapaṅkajā|| 6.43||
akṣamālārpitakarā kamaṇḍaludharā śubhā|
brahmāṇi saumyavadanā śivapūjāparāyaṇā|| 6.44||
% brahmāṇī \T32
śāntiṃ karotu me prītā brahmaśabdena sarvadā|
himaśailanibhā devi mahāvṛṣabhavāhanā|| 6.45||
triśūlahastā varadā nāgābharaṇabhūṣitā|
% sarvābharaṇa° \T32
% rudrabhaktā mahāvīryā rudrārcanaparā śivā| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
caturbhujā caturvaktrā trinetrā pāpahāriṇī|| 6.46||
ārtiharatu me prītā rudrāṇī nityamujvalā|
% ārtiṃ haratu me prītā brahmaśabdena sarvadā| \T32
% ................. īśvarī nityamujvalā| \T32
%% Above half line is not in printed edition, from Nepal.
mayūravāhanā devi sindūrārūṇavigrahā|| 6.47||
śaktihastā mahārūpā sarvālaṅkārabhūṣitā|
rudrabhaktā mahāvīryā rudrārcanaratā sadā|| 6.48||
% rudrabhaktā mahāpuṇyā \T32
kaumārī varadā devi śāntimāśu dadātu me|
% śāntimāśu karotu me| \T32
śaṃkhacakragadāhastā śyāmā pitāmbaraprīyā|| 6.49||
caturbhujā tārkṣayānā vaiṣṇavī surapūjitā|
% tārkṣyavāhā \T32
śivārcanaratā nityaṃ śivaikāhitamānasā|| 6.50||
% śivārcanaratābhaktā rudraikagatamānasā| \T32
śāntikarotu me nityaṃ sarvāsuravimardinī|
% śāntiṃ karotu me prītā \T32
airāvatagajārūḍha vajrahastā mahābalā|| 6.51||
netrāṇāntu sahasreṇa bhūṣitā kanakaprabhā|
siddhagandharvanamitā sarvālaṅkārabhūṣitā|| 6.52||
aindrī devī sadākālaṃ śāntimāśu karotu me|
varāhaghoṇā vikaṭā varāhavaravāhanā|| 6.53||
śyāmāvadātāṃ vipulā śaṃkhacakragadāyudhā|
tarjayanī sadā vighān arcayantī sadā śivam|| 6.54||
% sadāśivam| \T32
%% p.31
vārāhī varadā devī kṣamārogyaṃ dadātu me|
%% In T32 verses 53cd - 55ab occurs inbetween 51ab - 51cd (of this edition).
ardhakeśā koṭarākṣā nirmāṃsā snāyubandhanā|| 6.55||
% ūrdhvakeśotkaṭākṣāmā nirmāṃsasnāyubandhanā| \T32
karālavadanā ghorā khaṅgakaṭṭārakodyata|
% kṅgaghaṇṭāyudhodyatā| \T32
kapālamālinī kruddhā khaṭvāṅgavaradhāriṇī|| 6.56||
% kapālamālinī devī krūrā \T32
āraktapiṅganayanā gajacarmāvaguṇṭhitā|
nānānāgopavītāṅgī pretasthānanivāsinī|| 6.57||
% nānānāgaparītāṅgī \T32
śivārūpeṇa ghoreṇa śivārāvabhayaṅkarā|
% °bhayaṅkarī| \T32
cāmuṇḍā caṇḍarūpeṇa mahārakṣāṃ karotu me|| 6.58||
% citrayantrā sano tu me| \T32
% bhūtapretaviśācebhyo mama rakṣāṃ karotviha| \T32
% āyuḥ śriyaṃ balaṃ saukhyaṃ prītā bhūtvā dadātu me|| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
apītena śarīreṇa nānābharaṇabhūṣitā|
ātarjayantī vighnāni jvalatkhaṭvāṅgadhāriṇī|| 6.59||
dhvāṃkṣāsanā mahāvīrā sarvapāpapraṇāśanī|
lambauṣṭhi varadā devī śāntimāśu karotu me|| 6.60||
%% Verses 59 & 60 are missing in T32.
ākāśamātaro divyāstathānyālokamātaraḥ|
% ākāśe mātaro divyāḥ \T32
sarvamātṛmahādevyaḥ sāyudhavyagrapāṇayaḥ|| 6.61||
% sarvamātṛgaṇā devyaḥ \T32
jagadvyāpyāvatiṣṭhante valikāmā mahodayā|
% jagadvyāpyāvatiṣṭhantyo \T32
rudrabhaktyā mahāvīryā rudrārcā hitamānasā|| 6.62||
% rudrabhaktā mahāvīryā rudrārcanaparāyaṇāḥ| \T32
śāntiṃ kurvantu me nityaṃ mātaraḥ surapūjitāḥ|
ye rudrā raudrakarmaṇo rudrasthānanivāsinaḥ|| 6.63||
% raudrasthāna° \T32
saumyāścaiva tu ye kecit sthāṇusthānanivāsinaḥ|
mātaro rudrarūpāśca  gaṇānāmadhipaśca ye|| 6.64||
vighnabhūtāstathā cānye digvidikṣu samāśritāḥ|
% tathā ye ca \T32
sarve suprītamanasaḥ pratigṛhṇantu me balim|| 6.65||
% pratigṛhṇanti māṃ balim| \T32
siddhimāśu prayacchantu bhayebhyaḥ pāntu māṃ sadā|
% siddhiṃ kurvantu me nityaṃ \T32
aindryāṃ diśi gaṇā ye tu vajrahastā mahābalāḥ|| 6.66||
suśvetākṣāḥ śvetanibhāstathā vai śvetalohitāḥ|
