% siddhaḥ sādhyaḥ śubhaḥ śubhro brāhmo māhendra vai dhṛtī| \T32
candrasya bhānoścotpannā yogāścaite mahābalāḥ|| 6.149||
% candrasya bhānorutpannā hyete yogā mahābalāḥ| \T32
śivabhaktiparāḥ sarve śivājñānuvidhāyinaḥ|
% śivabhaktiyutāḥ sarve \T32
śāntiṃ kurvantu me nityaṃ tathā kilviṣanāśanam|| 6.150||
% śivadhyānaparāyaṇāḥ| \T32
kṛttikā paramā devī rohiṇī rucirānanā|
śrīmanmṛgaśirābhadrā ārdrā ca paramojvalā|| 6.151||
% pamojvalā \ ed
% mṛgaśīrṣā śive bhaktā ārdrā ca paramojvalā| \T32
punarvasustathā puṣyā aśleṣā.atha mahābalā|
% āśleṣā ca mahojvalā| \T32
nakṣatramātaro hyetāḥ prabhāmālāvibhūṣitāḥ|| 6.152||
% nakṣatramantaro hyetāḥ prabhāmālāvabhāsitāḥ| \T32
mahādevārcane saktā mahādevānubhāvitāḥ|
% mahādevārcanaratā mahādevātmabhāvanāḥ| \T32
pūrvabhāge sthitā hyetāḥ śāntiṃ kurvantu me sadā|| 6.153||
māghā sarvaguṇopetā pūrvā caiva tu phālguṇī|
uttarā phālguṇī śreṣṭhā hastā citrā tathottamā|| 6.154||
% hastacitrā tathottarā| \T32
svātirviśākhā varadā dakṣiṇasthānasaṃśritā|
% svātī viśākhā \T32
arcayanti mahākālaṃ devaṃ tribhuvaneśvaram|| 6.155||
% arcayantaḥ sadākālaṃ devaṃ triṇayanaṃ param| \T32
nakṣatramātaro hyetāstejasā paribhūṣitāḥ|
%% The above line is missing in T32.
%% p.37
mamāpi śāntikaṃ nityaṃ kurvantu śivacoditāḥ|| 6.156||
% mamāpi śāntikaṃ hyetāḥ \T32
anurādhā tathā jyeṣṭhā mūlaṛddhibalānvitā|
% anūrādhā tathā jyeṣṭhā mūlā vṛścikabalānvitā| \T32
pūrvāṣāḍhā mahāvīryā āṣāḍhā cottarā śubhā|| 6.157||
abhijinnātmana kṣetraṃ śravaṇā paramojvalā|
% abhijinnāma nakṣatraṃ śravaṇaḥ paramojvalaḥ| \T32
etā paścimato dīptā rājante rājamūrtayaḥ|| 6.158||
% etāḥ paścimato dīptā rājante cārumūrtayaḥ| \T32
īśānaṃ pūjayantyetāḥ sarvakālaṃ subhāvitāḥ|
% iśānaṃ \ ed
% īśānaṃ pūjayantyetat \T32
mama śāntiṃ prakurvantu vibhūtibhiḥ samanvitā|| 6.159||
% śāntiṃ kurvantu me nityaṃ vibhūtiṃ ca mahāhitāḥ| \T32
dhaniṣṭhā śatabhiṣā ca pūrvabhādrapadāstathā|
% śraviṣṭhā śatabhiṣak caiva pūrvabhādrapadasthathā| \T32
uttarābhādrarevatyau aśvinī ca mahardhikāḥ|| 6.160||
% uttarābhadrarevatyā hyaśvatī sumaharddhikā| \T32
bharaṇī ca mahāvīryā nityamuttarataḥ sthitāḥ|
% nityamuttarasaṃsthitāḥ| \T32
śivārcanaparā nityaṃ śivadhyānaikamānasāḥ|| 6.161||
% śivārcanaratā nityaṃ \T32
śāntiṃ karotu me nityaṃ sarvakālaśubhodayām|
% śāntiṃ kurvantu me nityaṃ sarvakālaṃ śubhodayāḥ| \T32
meṣo mahāhikaḥ siṃho dhanurdīptimatāṃ varāḥ|| 6.162||
% meṣo mṛgādhipasthaṃ yo dhanurdīptimatāṃ varaḥ| \T32
pūrveṇa bhāṣayantyete śivapūjāparāyaṇāḥ|
% pūrve tu bhāsayantyete śivapūjāparāyaṇaḥ| \T32
śāntiṃ kurvantu me nityaṃ śivaśaktiparāyaṇāḥ|| 6.163||
% harapādābjapūjakāḥ| \T32
kanyā ca vṛṣabhaḥ śrīmān makaraścāpi ṛddhimān|
% vṛṣaśca varadaḥ kanyā makaraśca mahardhikāḥ| \T32
% ṛṣabhaśca mahāvīryāḥ śivabhāvasubhāvitāḥ| \T32
ete dakṣiṇabhāge tu pūjayantaḥ sadāśivam|| 6.164||
% ete dakṣiṇadeśe tu pūjayanti sadāśivam| \T32
bhaktyā paramayā nityaṃ śāntiṃ me kurutāṃ sadā|
% śāntiṃ kurvantu me sadā| \T32
mithunaśca tulā kumbhaḥ paścimena vyavasthitā|| 6.165||
% tulākumbhau paścime tu vyavasthitāḥ| \T32
śivapūjārcanaparāḥ kṣamaṃ kurvantu me sadā|
% śivapūjārcane yuktāḥ śāntiṃ \T32
karkaṭo vṛściko mīna ete hyuttarataḥ sthitāḥ|| 6.166||
% mīno yenta \T32
pūjayanti sadākālaṃ rudraṃ bhuvananāyakam|
% yajante sadākālaṃ rudraṃ tribhuvanādhipam| \T32
śāntiṃ kurvantu me nityaṃ śivajñānānuvidhāyinaḥ|| 6.167||
% rudrajñānuvidhāyinaḥ| \T32
ṛṣayaḥ saptavikhyātā dhruvāntāḥ paramojvalāḥ|
% ṛṣayaḥ saptasaṃkhyātā \T32
śivaprasādasampannāḥ śāntiṃ kurvantu me sadā|| 6.168||
kaśyapo gālavo gārgyo viśvāmitro mahāmuniḥ|
% kāśyapo \T32
manurdakṣo vaśiṣṭho.atha mārkaṇḍaḥ pulahaḥ kratuḥ|| 6.169||
% pulastyaḥ pulahaḥ kratuḥ| \T32
nārado bhṛgurātreyo bharadvājoṅgirāmuni|
vālmīki kaiśikaḥ kaṇvaḥ śākalyo.atha punarvaśu|| 6.170||
% vālmīkiḥ kauśikaḥ kaṇ.vaḥ (śāka)jābālyo.atha punarvasuḥ| \T32
śākalyāyana ityādā ṛṣayo.atha mahāvratāḥ|
% śālaṃkāyana ityādyā ṛṣayo.atha mahābalāḥ| \T32
śivadhyānārcanedyuktāḥ śāntiṃ kurvantu me sadā|| 6.171||
% śivadhyānārcane yuktāḥ \T32
ṛṣipatnyā mahāpuṇyā ṛṣikanyā kumārikāḥ|
% ṛṣipatnyo mahābhāgā \T32
śivārcanaparānnityaṃ śāntiṃ kurvantu me sadā|| 6.172||
% śivārcanaratā nityaṃ \T32
siddhāḥ saṃsiddhatapasā gaṇo vidyādharāgrahāḥ|
% siddhāḥ samṛddhatapaso gandharvāścāpsarogaṇāḥ| \T32
%% p.38
mahātmāno mahotsāha garuḍāśca mahardhikā|| 6.173||
% vidyādharā mahātmāno garuḍāśca maharddhikaḥ| \T32
maheśvaraparā hyete maheśapādapūjakāḥ|
% maheśvaraparā nityaṃ maheśvarapadārcakāḥ| \T32
siddhimāśu prayacchantu āśirvādaparāyaṇāḥ|| 6.174||
% śivadharmaparāyaṇāḥ| \T32
namucirdaityarājendraḥ śaṃkukarṇo mahābalaḥ|
% namucirnāma daityendraḥ \T32
mahādāno.atha vikhyātā daityaḥ paramavīryavān|| 6.175||
% mahānādo.atha vitataḥ \T32
hāṭakeśvaradevasya nityapūjāparāyaṇāḥ|
varaṃ vīryañca me nityaṃ prayacchantu mahardhikāḥ|| 6.176||
% balaṃ vīryañca me kṣipraṃ prayacchatu mahardhikaḥ| \T32
mahājambho hayagrīvaḥ prahlādo vyaktahlādakaḥ|
% prahlādo daityarāt prabhuḥ| \T32
tārako.agnimukho daityaḥ kālanemirmahotkaṭaḥ|| 6.177||
% kālanemirbalistathā| \T32
ete daityāḥ mahātmānaḥ śivasadbhāvabhāvitāḥ|
puṣṭiṃ balantathā vīryaṃ prayacchantu sukhodayam|| 6.178||
vilocano hiraṇyākṣaḥ suparvāśca sulomakaḥ|
% vairocano hiraṇyākṣaḥ suparvā ca sulomajaḥ| \T32
mucukundo sukundaśca daityo revatakastathā|| 6.179||
% raivatakastathā| \T32
bhāveṇa ca pareṇāśu yajante sarvadā śivam|
% bhāvena parameṇāśu yajantaḥ \T32
satataśca śubhātmānaḥ puṣṭiṃ kurvantu me sadā|| 6.180||
% satāṃ ca śivātmānaṃ \T32
daityapatnyā mahābhāgā daityānāṃ kanyakāḥ śubhāḥ|
kumārāścaiva daityānāṃ śāntiṃ kurvantu me sadā|| 6.181||
%% Above verse 181 is missing in T32
āraktena śarīreṇa raktāntāyatalocanaḥ|
mahābhogakṛtāṭopaḥ śaṃkhābjakṛtalāñchanaḥ|| 6.182||
ananto nāgarājendra śivapādārcane rataḥ|
% śivapūjārataḥ sadā| \T32
mahāpāpaviṣaṃ hatvā śāntimāśu karotu me|| 6.183||
% kṣemārogyaṃ karotu me| \T32
suśvetena tu dehena suśvetotpalaśekharā|
cārubhogo kṛtāṭopo hāracāruvibhūṣaṇaḥ|| 6.184||
vāsukirnāma rājendro rudrapūjāparo mahān|
mahāpāpaṃ viṣaṃ hatvā śāntimāśu karotu me|| 6.185||
% sarvapāpaviṣaṃ hatvā kṣemārogyakarotu me| \T32
atipītena dehena visphuradbhogasampadā|
% prasphurad°\T32
tejasā cātidiptena kṛtasvastikalāñchanaḥ|| 6.186||
% tejasā cātisaptena \T32
nāgarāḍrakṣakaḥ śrīmān nāgakoṭyasamanvitāḥ|
% nāgarāṭ takṣakaḥ śrīmān nāgakoṭisamanivtaḥ| \T32
karotu me mahāśāntiṃ sarvadoṣaviṣāpahān|| 6.187||
% sarvadoṣaviṣāpahaḥ| \T32
atikṛṣṇena varṇena sphītavikaṭamastakaḥ|
% sphuradvikaṭamastakaḥ| \T32
kaṇṭhe rekhātrayopetā ghoradaṃṣṭrāyudhādyataḥ|| 6.188||
karkoṭake mahānāgo viṣadarpabalānvitāḥ|
% kālakūṭo mahānāgo viṣadarpasamanvitaḥ| \T32
viṣaśāstrāgnisantāpaṃ hatvā śāntiṃ karotu me|| 6.189||
%% p.39
padmavarṇena dehena cārupadmāyatekṣaṇaḥ|
% pañcabindukṛtābhāso grīvāyāḥ śubhalakṣaṇaḥ| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
khyātaḥ padmo mahānāgo harapādārcane rataḥ|| 6.190||
karotu me mahāśāntimahāpāpaviṣakṣayam|
puṇḍarīkanibhenāpi dehenāmitatejasā|| 6.191||
śaṃkhaṃ śūlābjarucirairbhūṣito mūrdhni sarvadā|
% śaṃkhaśūlābjaruciraiḥ bhūṣito mūrdhni bindhubhiḥ| \T32
mahāpadmo mahānāgo nityaṃ paśupaternataḥ|| 6.192||
% nityaṃ paśupatau rataḥ| \T32
viniṣkṛtya viṣaṃ ghoraṃ śāntim āśu karotu me|
% vinihatya viṣaṃ \T32
śyāmena dehabhāreṇa śrīmatkamalalocanaḥ|| 6.193||
viṣadarpāvalonmatto grīvāyāmekarekhayā|
% viṣadarpabalonmatto \T32
śaṃkhapālaḥ śrīyādīptaḥ śivapādābjapūjakaḥ|| 6.194||
mahāviṣaṃ mahāpāpaṃ hatvā śāntiṃ karotu me|
% mahāghoraviṣaṃ hatvā karotu mama śāntikam| \T32
atighoreṇa dehena candrārdhakṛtamastakaḥ|| 6.195||
% atigaureṇa dehena \T32
dīptabhogakṛtāṭopaḥ śubhalakṣaṇalakṣitaḥ|
kulike nāgarājeśo nityaṃ haraparāyaṇaḥ|| 6.196||
% guliko nāgarājendro \T32
apahṛtya viṣaṃ ghoraṃ karotu mama śāntikam|
antarīkṣe ca ye nāgā ye nāgāḥ svargasaṃsthitāḥ|| 6.197||
girikandaradurgeṣu ye nāgā bhuvisaṃsthitāḥ|
% bhūmisaṃsthitāḥ| \T32
pātāle ye sthitā nāgāḥ sarve.apyatra samāhitāḥ|| 6.198||
rudrapādārcane śaktāḥ kurvantu mama śāntikam|
% rudrapādārcane yuktāḥ śāntiṃ kurvantu me sadā| \T32
nāginyo nāgakanyāśca tathā nāgakumārikāḥ|| 6.199||
śivabhaktāḥ sumanasaḥ śāntiṃ kurvatnu me sadā|
ya idaṃ nāgasaṃsthānaṃ kīrtayecchṛṇuyādapi|| 6.200||
na tasya sarpahiṃsanti na viṣaṃ kramate sadā|
% na tasya nāgā hiṃsanti viṣaṃ nākramate sadā| \T32
% cintitaṃ sidhyate nityaṃ tathā pāpaparikṣayaḥ| \T32
% siddhimāśu prayacchanti sarvavighnavivarjitāḥ| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
