% yamunā narmadā tathā| \T32
gomatī tāpi kāverī varuṇā devikā tathā|
% gomatī cāpi kāverī kauśikā ca sarasvatī| \T32
% tāmraparṇī ca sarayūḥ varuṇā devikā tathā| \T32
sarvabhūtapatiṃ devaṃ parameśaṃ maheśvaram|| 6.202||
pūjayanti mahānadyaḥ śivasadbhāvabhāvitāḥ|
% pūjayanto mahānadyaḥ \T32
śāntiṃ kurvantu me nityaṃ tathā pāpaparikṣayaḥ|| 6.203||
siddhimāśu prayacchantu sarvavighnavivarjitāḥ|
% sarvavighnavināśanam| \T32
candrabhāgā mahāpuṇyā nadī godāvarī śubhā|| 6.204||
śarayū gaṇḍakī śreṣṭhā kauśikī ca sarasvatī|
etā nadyo mahābhāgāḥ śivapādārcane ratāḥ|| 6.205||
% etā nadyo mahāpuṇyāḥ \T32
śāntiṃ kurvantu me prītāḥ śivadhyānaikamānasā|
nairāñjanā nāma nadī śoṇaścāpi mahānadaḥ|| 6.206||
% nairañjanā \T32
%% p.40
mandākinī ca paramā tathā sannihitā śubhā|
etāścānyaśca bahavo bhuvi divyāntarīkṣugāḥ|| 6.207||
% bahyopabhūmidivyantarikṣagāḥ| \T32
rudrārcanaparā nadyaḥ kurvantu mama śāntikam|
% guhyāni yāni tīrthāni āsamudrātsarāṃsi ca| \T32
% kurvantu śāntikaṃ tāni śrīkaṇṭhādhiṣṭhitāni tu| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
mahāvaiśravaṇo devo yakṣarājo maharddhikaḥ|| 6.208||
% mahānvaiśravaṇo devo \T32
