% yakṣāsaṃkhyeyasaṃyuktaḥ| \T32
mahāvibhavasampanno harapādārcane rataḥ|| 6.209||
% ratoḥ \ ed
haradhyānaikaparamo harapādanatottamaḥ|
%% The above line is missing in T32.
śāntiṃ karotu me prītaḥ padmapatrāyatekṣaṇaḥ|| 6.210||
maṇibhadro mahāyakṣo maṇiratnavibhūṣitaḥ|
manohareṇa hāreṇa kaṇṭhalagnena rājate|| 6.211||
% śivadhyānarato nityaṃ śivapādābjapūjakaḥ| \T32
% śāntiṃ karotu me nityaṃ sarvadoṣanivāraṇam| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
yakṣiṇī yakṣakanyābhiḥ parivāritavigrahaḥ|
rudrārcanaparo yuktaḥ karotu mama śāntikam|| 6.212||
% rudrārcanaparo bhaktaḥ \T32
suviromotha yakṣendro maṇikuṇḍalabhūṣitaḥ|
% suvīro nāma yakṣendro maṇikuṇḍalabhūṣaṇaḥ| \T32
lalāṭe hemapaṭṭena śobhanena virājate|| 6.213||
% virājitaḥ| \T32
bahuyakṣāsamākīrṇo yakṣairnamitavigrahaḥ|
