% śivaḥ parāparo nityaṃ \T32
% vaṃciko nāma yakṣendraḥ karṇikākaṭakojvalaḥ| \T32
% makuṭena vicitreṇa keyūrābhyāṃ virājitaḥ| \T32
% yakṣāsaṃkhyeyasaṃyukto yakṣakoṭisamanvitaḥ| \T32
% harārcanarato nityaṃ karotu mama śāntikam| \T32
%% The above lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
śrīmān vibhāṇḍiko yakṣo nānāratnavibhūṣitaḥ|
