%% Chapter 7

atha paśupatimate śivadharmaśāstre nandikeśvaraproktāyāṃ
śivārcanaphalakathanaṃ nāma saptamo.adhyāyaḥ|
oṃ namaḥ śivāya|
nandikeśvara uvāca|
% nandikeśvara| \T32
ye smaranti sadākālamīśānaṃ pūjayanti vā|
% pūjayanti ca| \T32
rudralokaparibhraṣṭā vijñeyāste gaṇeśvaraḥ|| 7.1||
% gaṇeśvarāḥ| \T32
agnihotrāśca vedāśca yajñāśca bahudakṣiṇā|
% bahudakṣiṇāḥ| \T32
śivaliṅgārcanasyaite koṭyaṃśenāpi no samāḥ|| 7.2||
sadā jayanti yajñena sadā dānaṃ prayacchati|
% sadā yajati yajñena sadā dānaṃ prayacchati| \T32
sadā sajjñānadakṣaśca yaḥ sadārcayate śivam|| 7.3||
% sadā sa vāyubhakṣyaḥ syādyassadārcayate śivam| \T32
yaḥ śivaṃ pūjayennityaṃ praṇamedvāpi bhaktitaḥ|
tasya yogañca mokṣañca śivaḥ prītaḥ prayacchati|| 7.4||
yaḥ kuryādarcanaṃ māsam ekāhāro jitendriyaḥ|
sa yatphalamavāpnoti na tatsarvairmahāmakhaiḥ|| 7.5||
paurṇamāsyām amāvāsyāṃ caturdaśyāṣṭamīṣu ca|
snāpayitvāmbhasā liṅgaṃ sarvayajñaphalaṃ labhet|| 7.6||
kṛṣṇapakṣe trayodaśyām upaṣya parameśvaram|
% parameśvare| \T32
prātarmadhyāhna yaḥ pūjāṃ caturdaśyāṃ samācaret|| 7.7||
% prātarmadhyāhnapūjāṃ ca \T32
pañcagavyaṃ sa pītvādau havirbhūñjīta vāgyataḥ|
% pañcagavyaṃ sakṛtpītvā \T32
daśānāṃ sośvamedhānāṃ phalaṃ prāpnoti mānavaḥ|| 7.8||
% daśānāmaśvamedhānāṃ \T32
upoṣya ca kṛṣṇāṣṭamyāṃ arcayitvā tu śaṅkaram|
prāpnoti paramaṃ sthānaṃ yatradevo maheśvaraḥ|| 7.9||
brahmacārī śūcirbhūtvā trisandhyāṃ pūjayecchivam|
kulasaptakamuddhṛtya śivaloke mahīyate|| 7.10||
% trisaptakulamuddhṛtya \T32
%% p.45
dānopavāsaniyamaiḥ pūjā jāgarabhojanaiḥ|
mahāsnādividhinā śivaṃ parvasu pūjayet|| 7.11||
yāvatsu parvakāleṣu yāvadarcayate śivam|
% yāvacca sarvakāleṣu \T32
yāvat kālārcanātpuṇyaṃ tāvatparvārcanāllabhet|| 7.12||
% tāvat kālārcanātpuṇyaṃ yattatparvārcanaṃ labhet| \T32
tasmāt sarvaprayatnena yathāvibhavavistaraiḥ|
% tasmātparvasu yatnena \T32
pūjanīyaḥ śivo nityaṃ mahāpuṇyajīgīṣayāḥ|| 7.13||
% mahāpuṇyajighṛkṣayā| \T32
nairantaryeṇa ṣaṇmāsān vidhinā pūjayecchivam|
% nairataryeṇa \ ed
% nairantaryeṇa ṣaṇmāsaṃ vidhinā pūjya śaṅkaram| \T32
puṇyantadeva sakalaṃ labhate viṣuvārcane|| 7.14||
% viṣuvārcanāt| \T32
evameva vidhiryajñaṃ grahaṇe cottarāyaṇe|
% evameva phalaṃ jñeyaṃ grahaṇāyanayorapi| \T32
saṃkrāntidinachidreṣu ṣaḍaśītimukheṣu ca|| 7.15||
% saṃkrāntau ca dinacchidre ṣaḍaśītimukheṣu ca| \T32
māsaiścaturbhiryatpuṇyaṃ vidhinā pūjya śaṅkaram|
tat kārttikyāṃ labhetpuṇyaṃ paurṇamāsyāṃ śivārcane|| 7.16||
% śivārcanāt| \T32
puṇyameva ca phālguṇyām āṣāḍhyāñca viśeṣataḥ|
% puṇyaṃ tadeva phalgunyāṃ āṣāḍhyāṃ ca tathaiva ca| \T32
caturmāsyārcanaṃ hyetat mahāpuṇyaphalapradam|| 7.17||
% cāturmāsyārcanādetan \T32
māghe māse samudyuktastrisandhyaṃ yorcayecchivam|
ṣāṇmāsikaṃ kṛtaṃ puṇyaṃ māsenaiva na saṃśayaḥ|| 7.18||
% labhet ṣāṇmāsikaṃ puṇyaṃ \T32
yathā māghe tathāṣāḍhe māse caiva tu kārtike|
triṣu puṇyaṃ samaṃ jñeyaṃ māseṣveteṣu yatkṛtam|| 7.19||
% triṣu puṇyaṃ samujjñeyaṃ \T32
caturmāsārcanātpuṇyaṃ pauṣamāsārcanāllabhet|
% cāturmāsyakṛtaṃ puṇyaṃ \T32
caitraphālgunayoḥ puṇyaṃ dvimāsajanitaṃ labhet|| 7.20||
% bhavet| \T32
caturdaśyāmamāvāśyāṃ pauṇamāsyāñca pākṣikam|
puṇyamaṣṭaguṇaṃ jñeyam aṣṭamyāṃ yo.arcayecchivam|| 7.21||
pradadyādyogavāṃllakṣaṃ dogdhrīṇāṃ vedapārage|
% yaḥ pradadyādgavāṃ lakṣaṃ \T32
ekāhnamarcayelliṅgaṃ taysa puṇyaṃ tatodhikam|| 7.22||
% ekāhamarcayelliṃgaṃ \T32
māsī māsī tu yo.aśnīyādyāvajjivaṃ dvijottamaḥ|
% māse māse tu yo.aśnīyāt yāvajjīvaṃ sakṛnnaraḥ| \T32
yaścārcayetsakṛlliṅgaṃ samametanna saṃśayaḥ|| 7.23||
anena kramayogena puṇyavṛddhirdine dine|
% etena kramayogena phalavṛddhirdine dine| \T32
jñeyā saṃvatsarasyāpi yāvatkālaṃ tamarcayet|| 7.24||
% yāvadvā kālamarcayet| \T32
ya punaḥ saṅgamutsṛjya śivamabdaṃ prapūjayet|
anantarācchataguṇaṃ puṇyaṃ tasya pravartate|| 7.25||
% nairantaryācchataguṇaṃ tasya puṇyaṃ vivardhate| \T32
pañcāśadguṇitaṃ puṇyamabdhārdhaṃ yorcayecchivam|
ṛtāvṛtau tadardhasyānmāse cāpi tadardhakam|| 7.26||
% ṛtāvṛtau tadardhaṃ syāt māse māse tadardhakam| \T32
māsārdhamapi yo liṅgaṃ nairantaryeṇa pūjayet|
puruṣottamaḥ sa vijñeyā nairantaṅgarya hi duṣkaram|| 7.27||
% nairantaryaṃ hi duṣkaram| \T32
%% p.46
prātarutthāpyo liṅgaṃ bhaktyā pūjayate sadā|
% prātarutthāya \T32
kapilānāṃ śataṃ datvā yatpuṇyaṃ tadavāpnuyāt|| 7.28||
madhyaṃ dinakare prāpte yo liṅgaṃ samprapūjyate|
% madhyaṃ dinagate sūrye śivaṃ yaḥ pratipūjayet| \T32
sampūrṇā pṛthivīṃ datvā yatphalaṃ tadavāpnuyāt|| 7.29||
% sampūrṇāṃ \T32
vāruṇīmāśrite sūrye yaḥ śivaṃ samyagarcayeta|
% sampagarcayeta \ ed
% samyagarcayet| \T32
gavāṃ śatasahasrasya dantasya phalamāpnuyāt|| 7.30||
% dattasya \T32
yo liṅgamardharātre tu śucirbhūtvā prapūjayet|
samyagaṣṭaśatantena yjñānaṃ labhyate phalam|| 7.31||
% yajñānāṃ dharmato bhavet| \T32
evaṃ velāsu sarvāsu avelāsvapi śaṅkaram|
bhaktyā pūjayate nityaṃ sarvakāmamavāpnuyāt|| 7.32||
% sampūjayennaro bhaktyā \T32
śivaliṅgaṃ mahāpūṇyaṃ sarvadevanamaskṛtam|
ya spṛśedapi hastābhyāṃ na sa pāpaiḥ pralipyate|| 7.33||
na te bhūyaḥ prayāsyanti yonisaṃsārasaṅkaṭam|
% yonimārgaṃ susaṅkaṭam| \T32
kramātmakṣagamiṣyanti ye narā liṅgamāśritāḥ|| 7.34||
merumandaramātropi rāśīḥ pāpasya karmaṇaḥ|
iśvaravaidyamāsādya naśyate duṣṭarogavat|| 7.35||
% īśvaraṃ vaidyamāsādya \T32
% kāñcanaṃ merumātraṃ ca sarvāndatvā vasundharām| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
liṅgārcanarato nityaṃ mahāpātakasambhavaiḥ|
% śivārcanarato \T32
doṣai kṛtairna lipyeta padmapatramivāmbhasā|| 7.36||
chitvā bhitvā tu bhūtāni hatvā sarvamidaṃ jagat|
% chitvā hitvā ca \T32
yajedekaṃ virūpākṣaṃ na sa pāpena lipyate|| 7.37||
% liṣyate \ ed
% na sa pāpaiḥ pralipyate| \T32
apavitra pavitro vā sarvāvasthā gatopi vā|
% sarvāvasthāṃ gato vāpi yukto vā sarvapātakaiḥ| \T32
śivamiṣṭvā naraḥ sopi prayāti paramāṅgatim|| 7.38||
% śivamiṣṭvā naraḥ sopi prayāti paramaṃ padam| \T32
% saritsamudratīreṣu vaneṣū pavaneṣu ca| \T32
% giriśṛṅgeṣu tuṅgeṣu gahvaropavaneṣu ca| \T32
% puṣkariṇyāṃ taṭākeṣu tīrthāyatasaṃśraye| \T32
% yatra vā ramate buddhiḥ tatraiva śivamarcayet| \T32
% sarvayajñeṣu yatpuṇyaṃ tallabhennātra saṃśayaḥ| \T32
% yaḥ punaḥ sthānasaṃkalpyam utsṛjya śivamarcayet| \T32
% sośvamedhaphalaṃ sarvaṃ labhate nātra saṃśayaḥ| \T32
