% yastamarcayate bhaktyā tasya puṇyaṃ tatodhikam| \T32
%% Above 10 lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
ayaṃ vinaiva mantreṇa puṣparāśīḥ prakīrtitaḥ|
syādidaṃ mantrasaṃyukta puṇyaṃ śataguṇādhikam|| 7.39||
% syādayaṃ mantrasaṃyuktaṃ \T32
tasmātmantreṇa śarvāya snānaṃ gandhajalādhikam|
% tasmānmantreṇa śarvāya jñānagandhaphadādhikam| \T32
kṣitiṃ grāmañca ratnañca vastraṃ hemaṃ nivedayet|| 7.40||
% kṣitiṃ gāścaiva ratnāni homāḍhyaṃ ca nivedayet| \T32
jñeyo namaḥ śivāyeti mantraḥ sarvārthasādhakaḥ|
sarvamantrādhikaścāyamoṅkārādyaḥ ṣaḍākṣaraḥ|| 7.41||
% sarvamātrādhikaścāyaṃ \T32
śivenāntarbahiryasmāt sarvameva carācaram|
% śivenāntarbahirvyāptaṃ sarvametaccarācaram| \T32
jagadomaśca kurute tasmādomiti saṃsṛtaḥ|| 7.42||
% jagadomiti yadbrūte \T32
ayamardhacatasṛbhirmātrābhiḥ parigīyate|
% ayamardhena tisṛbhiḥ mātrābhiḥ parigīyate| \T32
rudro brahmā hariścaiva mātrāstisraḥ prakīrtitāḥ|| 7.43||
% rudro brahmā hariścaiva] \ed; brahmā hariśca rudraśca
% mātrāstisraḥ] \T32; mātrā tisra \ed
dakṣiṇāṅge bhavedbrahmā harirvāmāṅgasambhavaḥ|
% °samnavaḥ| \ed
% dakṣiṇāṅge bhavo brahmā \T32
hṛdayānnirgato rudro brahmaviṣṇuprabodhakaḥ|| 7.44||
% hṛdayānnīlarudraśca \T32
%% p.47
jagatsṛṣṭikaro brahmā viṣṇulokavimohakaḥ|
anugrahakaro nityaṃ līno rudraḥ śivātmakaḥ|| 7.45||
% anugrahaparo nityaṃ nīlarudraḥ śivātmakaḥ| \T32
tribhiretairjagadvyāptaṃ kāraṇairātmakarmabhiḥ|
% kāraṇairātmamūrtibhiḥ| \T32
