etā eva trayo lokāstrayo devāstrayognayaḥ|
% etā eva trayo vedāḥ trayo lokāstrayognayaḥ| \T32
trayo guṇāstrivargāśca yaccānyajjagati sthitam|| 7.47||
ardhamātrātparo rudraḥ śivaḥ paramakāraṇaḥ|
% śivaḥ paramakāraṇam| \T32
tasmādetatsamutpannaṃ jagataḥ kāraṇatrayam|| 7.48||
sarvajñānaparaḥ śuddho namaskāro maheśvaraḥ|
% sarvajñānātparaḥ śuddho namaskāro mahāmakhaḥ| \T32
namaskārātmayajñena tasmāt sampūjayecchivam|| 7.49||
ajñānamaśivatvaṃ syāt sarvaduḥkhālayaṃ mahat|
% sarvaduḥkhālayaṃ yataḥ| \T32
svabhāvāttadavāptaṃ hi tasmādrudroditaḥ śivaḥ|| 7.50||
% subhāvāttadavāptaṃ hi yasmādrudraḥ paraḥ śivaḥ| \T32
namaḥ śivāya śāntāya kāraṇatrayahetave|
nivedayāmi cātmānaṃ mantraivaṃ manasādhunā|| 7.51||
% nivedayenmamātmānam uktvaivaṃ parameśvare| \T32
kṛtvaunnamaḥ śivāyeti mucyate sarvapātakaiḥ|
% uktvoṃ namaḥ śivāyeti mucyate sarvabandhanāt| \T32
yasmāttasmāt sadā mantram oṅkārādyam anusmaret|| 7.52||
sarvadā sarvakāryeṣu śṛtaniṣṭhīvanādiṣu|
% kṣāntiṃ niṣṭhīvanādiṣu| \T32
janturnamaḥ śivāyeti sa gacchet paramaṃ padam|| 7.53||
% yāntyāṃ namaḥ śivāyeti giramuktvā śivaṃ padam| \T32
