% yaḥ svapan pratibuddhaśca prāṇānte tu samutsmaret| \T32
yadonnamaḥ śivāyeti sa gacchet paramaṃ padam|| 7.54||
% tadā namaḥ śivāyeti sa gacchet paramāṃ gatim| \T32
śāṭhyenāpi namaskāraḥ prayuktaḥ śūlapāṇaye|
saṃsārasṭhūlabandhanām ucchedanakaro bhavet|| 7.55||
% udveṣṭanakaro bhavet| \T32
apavitraḥ pavitro vā sarvāvasthāṃ gatopi vā|
yasmaret satataṃ rudraṃ na sa pāpena lipyate|| 7.56||
% yasmareddevamīśānaṃ sa bāhyābhyantaraḥ śuciḥ| \T32
smaraṇādeva rudrasya pāpasaṃghātapañjaram|
śatadhā bhedamāyāti girivajrāhato yathā|| 7.57||
% girirvajrahato yathā| \T32
sarveṣāṃ śivabhaktānāṃ aśeṣārthaprasiddhaye|
mantram āha śivaḥ sāram aśeṣārthaprabandhanam|| 7.58||
% mantramāha śivaḥ sākṣāt aśeṣārthanibandhanam| \T32
sabījaṃ sarvavidyānām ādyaṃ brahmaparātparam|
% savījaṃ \ed
% sadbījaṃ \T32
sarvārthasādhakaṃ mantraṃ śivasūtraṃ ṣaḍakṣaram|| 7.59||
bhāṣyam asyaiva sūtrasya sarvajñena svayambhuvā|
% bhāṣyam asyaiva rudrasya sarvajñānāni śambhunā| \T32
paścāt parāparāṇīha vyaktārthagaditāni tu|| 7.60||
% bhaktārthaṃ gaditāni tu| \T32
tasmādanena mantreṇa prakurvīta śivārcanam|
sandhyāyāñca japedenaṃ sarvapāpaviśuddhaye|| 7.61||
%% p.48
gṛhācchataguṇaṃ puṇyaṃ sandhyāyāñca jalāśraye|
śivadakṣiṇamūrtau ca tatpuṇyam ayutādhikam|| 7.62||
tasmācchivālaye sandhyāmācarecchāntamānasaḥ|
% tasmācchivālaye japyam ācarecchāntamānasaḥ| \T32
śivamantreṇa satataṃ sarvakāmaprasiddhaye|| 7.63||
jitendriyaḥ śāntamanāḥ śivamantreṇa yo.arcayet|
% śivamantreṇa pūjayet| \T32
na tasya śakyate vaktuṃ puṇyaṃ varṣaśatairapi|| 7.64||
etāvacchakyate vaktuṃ ysmin deśe vasedasau|
% yasmindeśe vasedayam| \T32
so.api deśe bhavet pūtaḥ kiṃ punastasya bāndhavāḥ|| 7.65||
yeṣāmannaṃ samasnāti ye cāsya paricārakāḥ|
% yasyāyamannamaśnāti etasya paricārakāḥ| \T32
te.api nihatapāpāḥ syus tairvinā na śivārcanam|| 7.66||
% te.apīha tatsamā jñeyāḥ \T32
na tatra deśe durbhikṣaṃ na ca mārī pravartate|
nākāle mriyate rājā pūjyate yatra śaṃkaraḥ|| 7.67||
