% sa yatphalamāpnoti tadekāgramanāḥ śṛṇu| \T32
% sarvavedeṣu yatproktaṃ sarvayajñeṣu yatphalam| \T32
% tatphalaṃ koṭiguṇitaṃ salabhennātra saṃśayaḥ| \T32
%% The above lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
yaḥ śivaṃ pūjayennityaṃ manujo.api jitendriyaḥ|
