% tasmādevaṃ śivaṃ bhaktyā pūjayecchāntamānasaḥ| \T32
% śivabhakto jitakrodhaḥ śivajñānaparāyaṇaḥ| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
maitrī kāruṇiko.ajasraṃ prāpnoti satataṃ śivam|| 7.72||
% maitrīkāruṇikopetaḥ \T32
kṣaṇārdhenāpi yatpuṇyaṃ kuryānmaitrīṃ subhāvitaḥ|
na tadvarṣaśatenāpi tapoyajñaśatairapi|| 7.73||
sarvaprāṇiṣu kāruṇyaṃ dīnānātheṣu sevanam|
% dīnānātheṣu bhāvayet| \T32
sukhaprāptiśca maitrī ca muditāṃ puṇyaśīlatām|| 7.74||
% maitrīśca \ed
% sukhaprāṇiṣu maitrī syānmuditāḥ puṇyaśīliṣu| \T32
ātmavacca tato prekṣa sarveṣāñca vadecchivam|
% apuṇyavatsu copekṣāṃ \T32
ityevaṃ pañcadhā cittaṃ bhāvayitvā yajecchivam|| 7.75||
% sampūjya paśubhaktāraṃ prahṛṣṭenāntarātmanā| \T32
% dhyānaṃ kuryādyathoddiṣṭaṃ sarvapāpanikṛntanam| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
