vaktrāya saṃkhyeya yuktāya nityaṃ rudrāya te namaḥ|| 7.111||
ekanetradvinetrāya bahunetrāya te namaḥ|
netrasaṃkhyeya yuktāya īśānāya namo namaḥ|| 7.112||
namostu te mahādeva namaste tu maheśvara|
namastestu mahāyogī namastestu mahojvalā|| 7.113||
namastestu mahādeva namastestu sadāśiva|
namaste bhagavan śānta namaste bhagavan dhruva|| 7.114||
namaste bhagavan dīpta namate bhagavan hara|
ajitāya namastubhyaṃ bhasmāṅgāya namo namaḥ|| 7.115||
sarvātmane namastubhyaṃ viśveśāya namostu te|
avyaktāya namstubhyaṃ śāśvatāya namo namaḥ|| 7.116||
sampūjyāya namastubhyaṃ varadāya namostu te|
anantāya namastubhyaṃ sarvāṃgāya namostu te|| 7.117||
śaṃkarāya namastu bhyaṃ umeśāya te namaḥ|
iti stavena divyena yastu stauti maheśvaram|| 7.118||
sa vidhūyāśupāpāni rudraloke mahīyate|
bhogārthī labhate bhogān rājyārthī rājyamāpnuyāt|| 7.119||
kanyārthī labhate kanyāṃ yogārthī yogamāpnuyāt|
mucyate vyādhito vyādhe duḥkhī duḥkhāt pramucyate|| 7.120||
baddho baddhāt pramucyate yaśarthī ca yaśo labhet|
% yaśorthī \ed
yāsu yāsu kāmayate kāmān tāsu tāsu prāpnoti mānavaḥ|| 7.121||
śivasya padamāpnoti nityaṃ pathati yo naraḥ|

\Colo
iti śrīśivadharmaśāstre śrīnandikeśvaraprokte pūjādharmo
nāma saptamodhyāyaḥ|

%% Here ends the portion of transcript T0772.

%% Chapter 8

%% p.85
pṛthivyāṃ yāni tīrthāni puṇyānyānyāyatanāni ca|
līyante tāni liṅge tu tasmālliṅgaṃ prapūjayet|| 8.1||
% līyante tāni liṅge tu tasmā . .. . . . . .| \T32
sa snātaḥ sarvatīrtheṣu sarvayajñeṣu dīkṣitaḥ|
%%  . . . . . . . . .  yajñaiśca dīkṣitaḥ| \T32
yaḥ pūjayenmahādevaṃ liṅgamūrtigataṃ śivam|| 8.2||
% yaḥ pūjayenmahāliṅgaṃ puṇyaṃ sarvārthasiddhidam| \T32
% śatena sthāpitaṃ liṅgaṃ sahasreṇa tu cālayet| \T32
% susthitaṃ duḥsthitaṃ vāpi śivaliṅgaṃ na cālayet| \T32
%% The above two verses are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
%% p.86
ghṛtābhiṣekaṃ yaḥ kuryād ahorātraṃ śivasya tu|
nityamacchinnadhārābhiḥ paurṇamāsyāṃ samudyataḥ|| 8.3||
% puṇyamāse samudyukto niyataṃ ślakṣṇadhārayā| \T32
gītanṛtyopahāreṇa śaṅkhavādyādiniśvanaiḥ|
kuryājjāgarantatra pradīpādyupaśobhitam|| 8.4||
% pradipādyupaśobhite| \T32
samastapāpanirmuktaḥ samastakulasaṃyutaḥ|
samastakāmasampūrṇaḥ samastavidhisaṃyutaḥ|| 8.5||
jvaladbhiḥ sa mahāyānairasaṃkhyeyairanopamaiḥ|
% asaṃkhyeyairanūpamaiḥ| \T32
yuktaḥ śivapure nityaṃ modate śivavat sukhī|| 8.6||
śatena sthāpayelliṅgaṃ sahasreṇa tu cālayet|
duḥsthitaṃ susthitaṃ vāpi śivaliṅganna cālayet|| 8.7||
%% Above verse is missing in T32.
grahaṇe viṣuve caiva puṇyeṣu divaseṣu ca|
ghṛtābhiṣekaṃ yaḥ kuryānmahāpuṇyamavāpnuyāt|| 8.8||
ghṛtābhiṣekaṃ yaḥ paśyadāsamāptimupoṣitaḥ|
vidhūya sarvapāpāni śivaloke mahīyate|| 8.9||
ekaḥ pūjayate bhaktyā cānyo bhaktyā prapaśyati|
%% p.87
tulyameva phalantābhyāṃ bhaktirevātra kāraṇam|| 8.10||
yaḥ kuryāt parvakāleṣu mahāpūjāpravardhanam|
% mahāpūjāpravartanam| \T32
śivasya rathayātrāṃ vā nagarantaḥ parikramāt|| 8.11||
% nāgarāntaḥ \T32
mahācitradhvajaiścatraiḥ kiṅkiṇīvarakānvitaiḥ|
% mahācitraiḥ dhvajaiścitraiḥ \T32
vitānadhvajamālābhirghaṇṭācāmaradarpaṇaiḥ|| 8.12||
śaṅkhabheryādinirghoṣairgītavādyādisaṃkulaiḥ|
% gītanāṭyādisaṃyutaiḥ| \T32
lepyadājumayairyantrairmātṛyakṣagaṇādibhiḥ|| 8.13||
% lekhyadārumayairyantraiḥ \T32
udakāgneyayantraiśca bahvāścarairanekaśaḥ|
% udakāntoyayantraiśca \T32
strīdolācakrayantraiśca rathamandiraśobhitam|| 8.14||
% strīḍolāścakrayantraiśca \T32
udyānakhānapānaiśca mahāyantraiḥ samāyutān|
% dadhyannapānakhānādyaiḥ mahāsatrasamāyutaiḥ| \T32
mahājanasamākīrṇān yathāvibhavakalpitān|| 8.15||
% yathāvibhavavistaram|  \T32
sa sarvadānapuṇyāni sarvayajñaphalāni ca|
% sarvadānāni puṇyāni sarvayajñaphalāni ca| \T32
atyugratapasāṃ puṇyaṃ sarvatīrthaphalāni ca|| 8.16||
labdhvā naravaraḥ śrīmān śivayātrāpravartanāt|
% labdhā \T32
śivaloke mahābhāgaiḥ śivavanmodate sadā|| 8.17||
tsyānte devarājasya suciraṃ kālamāpnuyāt|
% devarājatvaṃ \T32
jambūdvīpādhipaḥ śrīmāṃstasyānte ca bhavetpunaḥ|| 8.18||
%% p.88
āliṅgaṃ vediparyantaṃ yo dadyāt ghṛtakambalam|
% āliṅgaṃ vediparyantaṃ vāditrādghṛtakambalam| \T32
gṛtadhārāphalaṃ tasya māghapūrṇimaparvaṇi|| 8.19||
% māghe paurṇimaparvaṇi| \T32
jāgarād gītanṛtyādyaiḥ sakṛt kṛtvā tu parvaṇi|
% jāgaraṃ gītanṛttādyaiḥ \T32
manvantaraśataṃ sāgraṃ śivaloke mahīyate|| 8.20||
% chatrābhirāmanāṭyādyaṃ śivasyāyatanāgrataḥ| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
samyak samprekṣaṇaṃ kṛtvā rudralokamavāpnuyāt|
% samyak preṣaṇakaṃ datvā rudraloke mahīyate| \T32
surūpaḥ subhagaḥ śrīmān paribhraṣṭastu jāyate|| 8.21||
% parihṛṣṭo.atra jāyate| \T32
%% p.89
% saptadvīpasamudrāyāḥ kṣiteradhipatirbhavet| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
rūpaṃ piṣṭamayaṃ kṛtvā trinetraṃ ratnabhūṣitam|
śuklopavītasaṃyuktamekapādaṃ viśeṣataḥ|| 8.22||
danteṣu maiktikantasya pravālañca tathoṣṭhayoḥ|
dayād vajrañca netrābhyāṃ vaidūryañcāpi mastake|| 8.23||
% vaiḍūryaṃ vāpyasambhave| \T32
hemaraupyañca hastābhyāṃ tāmraṃ pādau ca kalpayet|
% hemarūpyañca hastābhyāṃ tāmraṃ pāde ca vinyaset| \T32
aṇḍajaiḥ pāṇḍajairvastraiḥ pariveṣṭyeta yo naraḥ|| 8.24||
% aṇḍajaiḥ pauṇḍrajairvastraiḥ vividhaiḥ pariveṣṭayet| \T32
sugandhairdivyagandhaiśca puṣpaiścāpi vibhūṣayet|
% subhagairdivyagandhaiśca \T32
vividhairbhakṣyabhojyādyairbalintatropakalpayet|| 8.25||
bhojayecchivabhaktāṃśca śaktyā viprāṃśca dakṣayet|
% viprāncchaktyā pratarpayet| \T32
prīyatāṃ me śivo nityam ityuktotthāpayed dvijān|| 8.26||
% uktvā cotthāpayedvijān| \T32
taireva tu dvijaiḥ sārdhantadrūpantu śivālaye|
% taireva sārdhaṃ viprendraiḥ tadrūpaṃ tu śivālaye| \T32
nītvā samarpayedviṣāṃ śivaliṅgasamīpagaḥ|| 8.27||
% (bha)nityā samarpayedvedyāṃ śivaliṅgasamīpataḥ| \T32
sarvayajñaphalaṃ prāpya sarvadānaphalāni ca|
surūpo rūpadānena śivaloke mahīyate|| 8.28||
% svarūpasvarūpadānena \T32
bhojanaṃ ghṛtasampūrṇaṃ madhunā pariśobhitam|
dadyāt kṛṣṇatilānāntu prasthamekantu māgadham|| 8.29||
% pṛthak prasthaṃ prakalpayet| \T32
dviguṇantaṇḍulānāñca pṛthak prasthaṃ prakalpayet|
%% p.90
aṇḍajaiḥ pāṇḍajairvastrairvicitraiḥ pariveṣṭitam|| 8.30||
% aṇḍajaiḥ pauṇḍrajairvastraiḥ \T32
liṅgaṃ saṃveṣṭya vastrābhyāṃ balimetannivedayet|
% evaṃ saṃveṣṭya \T32
arcayitvā vidhānena paurṇamāsyāṃ viśeṣataḥ|| 8.31||
samāḥ śatasahasrāṇi śivaloke mahīyate|
% yugakoṭisahasrāṇi \T32
puṇyakṣayādihāgatya samṛddhe jāyate kule|| 8.32||
medhāvī subhagaḥ śrīmān vedavedāṅgapāragaḥ|
tāmrapātraṃ payaḥ pūrṇāṃ kṛtvā tatsthañca kāñcanam|| 8.33||
pracchādyopari padmena gandhapuṣpārcitaṃ mahat|
śivabhaktaṃ dvijaṃ samyagbhojayitvā vidhānataḥ|| 8.34||
% śivabhaktadvijaṃ \T32
prācyāṃ samudgate some pratīcyāñca ravau gate|
paurṇamāsyāṃ savaiśākhyāṃ gṛhya pātraṃ śivāgrataḥ|| 8.35||
% paurṇamāsyāṃ tu vaiśākhyāṃ nītvā pātraṃ śivāgrataḥ| \T32
prīyatāṃ me mahādevaḥ somamūrtirjagatpatiḥ|
% somamūrtirjagatpattiḥ| \T32
tasmai viprāya tatpātram arpayed bhaktitaḥ śanaiḥ|| 8.36||
etat somavratannāma kṛtvā rudrāntikaṃ vrajet|
rudralokāt paribhraṣṭo bhavejjātismaro naraḥ|| 8.37||
pūrvābhyāsaina tenaiva punaḥ śivapuraṃ vrajet|
%% p.91
paurṇamāsyāṃ yathāṣāḍhyāṃ śivaṃ sampūjya yatnataḥ|| 8.38||
% paurṇamāsyāmathāṣāḍhyāṃ \T32
upavītaṃ śive dadyācchivabhaktāṃśca bhojayet|
punareva ca kārttikyāṃ pūjaya śambhuṃ kṣamāpayet|| 8.39||
% punarevṃ tu kārtikyāṃ sampūjyaivaṃ samāpayet| \T32
yatīnāṃ dakṣiṇāṃ dadyāt sūtravastrādipūrvikām|
yaḥ kuryātsakṛdapyevaṃ caturmāsapavitrakam|| 8.40||
% cāturmāsyapavitrakam| \T32
kalpakoṭiśataṃ divyaṃ rudraloke mahīyate|
puṇyakṣayāt paribhraṣṭaścaturvedaḥ prajāyate|| 8.41||
% caturvedī prajāyate| \T32
icchayā tu bhavedrājā guṇarūpasamanvitaḥ|| 8.41||
% icchāyā vā \T32
bhūmidānasya yat puṇyaṃ kanyādānasya yat phalam|
mukhavādyena tat puṇyamubhayaṃ labhate naraḥ|| 8.42||
tadeva puṇyaṃ gītasya nṛtyasya ca viśeṣataḥ|
tadeva jayaśabdasya tadeva tālakadhvaneḥ|| 8.43||
% hastatāladhvanau tathā| \T32
yo gāṃ payasvinīndadyāttaruṇīṃ vṛṣasaṃyutām|
śivāya tena dattaṃ syājjagadetaccarācaram|| 8.44||
%% p.92
vṛṣañca paripūrṇāṅgamudārañca śaśiprabham|
gopatiṃ dhūrvahañcāpi yatheṣṭañca nivedayet|| 8.45||
% gopatiṃ dhūrvahaṃ vāpi śivāya vinivedayet| \T32
yāvanti deharomāṇi tatprasūtikuleṣu ca|
% yāvanti tasya romāṇi \T32
tāvadyugasahasrāṇi rudraloke mahīyate|| 8.46||
śivāgnikāryamuddiśya surūpāṃ supayasvinīm|
kulīnāṃ kapilāṃ datvā dattaṃ bhavati cākṣayam|| 8.47||
% dattaṃ bhavati gośatam| \T32
bhayakāntāradurgeṣu kapilā māteva rakṣati|
% girikāntāradurgeṣu māteva parirakṣati| \T32
yatnena kapilāṃ tasmācchivāya vinivedayet|| 8.48||
śivasnānāgnikāryārtham utpannā kapilāgrataḥ|
% utpannāṃ kapilāṃ yataḥ| \T32
tasmāttatraiva sā yojyā kapilā śubhamicchatā|| 8.49||
kapilāṃ yaḥ pivecchūdraḥ śivasaṃskāravarjitaḥ|
% kāpilaṃ \T32
sa prayāti mahāghorannarakannātra saṃśayaḥ|| 8.50||
% sa yāti narakaṃ ghoraṃ yāvadābhūtasaṃplavam| \T32
hutaśeṣaṃ pivedvipraḥ svargī syādanyathā paśuḥ|
gāmālabhya namaskṛtya kuryādyaśca pradakṣiṇām|| 8.51||
% pradakṣiṇam| \T32
pradakṣiṇīkṛtā tena saptadvīpā vasundharā|
%% p.93
gavāṃ huṅkāraśabdena darśanāt sparśanena ca|| 8.52||
% darśanātsparśanādapi| \T32
pāpaṃ praṇaśyate yasmāt tasmātpaśyet spṛśeta vā|
% tasmātpaśyetspṛśedapi| \T32
kutasteṣāṃ hi pāpāni yeṣāṃ gṛhamalaṅkṛtam|| 8.53||
satataṃ bālavatsābhirgobhiḥ śrībhiriva svayam|
yāni tīrthāni medinyāmāsamudrasarāṃsi ca|| 8.54||
% yāni tīrthāni me dadyāt māsamātrātsarāṃsi ca| \T32
gavāṃ śṛṅgodakasnānāt kalānnārhanti ṣoḍaśīm|
na laṅghayed gavāmāsthi mṛtagandhanna varjayet|| 8.55||
% gavāmasthini laṅgheta mṛtagāvaṃ na varjayet| \T32
yāvat pibati tadgandhaṃ tāvat puṇyaiḥ prapūyate|
% yāvajjighrati tadgandhaṃ tāvatpuṇyaiḥ prapūryate| \T32
%% p.94
gavāṃ kaṇḍūyanaṃ dhūmaṃ gopradanasamaṃ bhavet|| 8.56||
% gavāṃ kaṇḍūyanāddhūpād \T32
tulyaṃ gośatadānena bhayarogādipālanam|
% gośatadānasya \T32
tṛṇodakadisaṃyuktaṃ yaḥ pradadyād gavāhnikam|| 8.57||
% tṛṇodakadisaṃyuktāṃ yaḥ pradadyādgavāṃ mahīm| \T32
sa gomedhasamaṃ puṇyaṃ labhate nātra saṃśayaḥ|
bahunātra kimuktena gāvaḥ pālyā prayatnataḥ|| 8.58||
%% p.95
% gāvo deyāḥ sadā rakṣyāḥ spṛśyā dṛśyāśca sarvadā| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
yastāḍayati gāṃ pāpaḥ sarvalokasya mātaram|
% ye tāḍayanti gāṃ \T32
% ākrośayanti ye mohāt ākruṣṭaṃ dāyikaṃ jagat| \T32
% tāḍanena gavāṃ mohāt yaścākrośennarādhamaḥ| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
narakāgnau sa pacyate gobhirniśvāsapīḍitaḥ|| 8.59||
% gavāṃ niśvāsapīḍitaḥ| \T32
sapalāśena daṇḍena tāḍyan vinivartayet|
% palāśenaiva daṇḍena mṛdunā gāṃ nivartayet| \T32
gaccha gaccheti tāṃ brūyān mā yāteti nivārayet|| 8.60||
% mā mātariti vārayet| \T32
halotsargantu yaḥ kuryāt pakṣayorubhayorapi|
% malotsargaṃ ca yaḥ kuryāt \T32
dvādaśyāṃ paurṇamāsyāñca caturdaśyaṣṭamīṣu ca|| 8.61||
tasya gāvo vṛṣā viṣṇuśivomāḥ sarvadevatāḥ|
% tasya gāvo vṛṣo viṣṇuḥ \T32
śāntiṃ juṣanti suprītāḥ svargamāyurbalaṃ śriyam|| 8.62||
% śāntiṃ kurvantu suprītā \T32
% dāsyanti ca sadā nityaṃ kalyāṇaṃ bhadrameva ca| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
evaṃ yo vartate goṣu tāḍanākośavarjitaḥ|
mahatīṃ śriyamāpnoti rudralokaṃ sa gacchati|| 8.63||
%% p.96
gobrāhmaṇārthamudyuktaḥ prāṇairyadi vimucyate|
prāpnoti paramaṃ sthānaṃ yatra devo maheśvaraḥ|| 8.64||
% rudralokaṃ sa gacchati| \T32
brāhmaṇāścaiva gāvaśca kulamekaṃ dvidhākṛtam|
ekatra mantrāstiṣṭhanti havirekatra tiṣṭhati|| 8.65||
% haviranyatra tiṣṭhati| \T32
% na camantrairvinā yajño haviṣā ca pravartate| \T32
% tasmādviprāśca gāvaśca puṇyātpuṇyatarā ubhau| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
goṣu yajñāḥ pravartante goṣu devāḥ pratiṣṭhitāḥ|
% gobhiryajñāḥ \T32
gobhirdevāḥ samudgīrṇāḥ saṣaḍaṅgapadakramāḥ|| 8.66||
śṛṅgamūle gavāṃ nityaṃ brahmā viṣṇuśca saṃsthitau|
% brahmā viṣṇuḥ svayaṃ sthitau| \T32
%% p.97
śṛṅgāgre sarvatīrthāni sthāvarāṇi carāṇi ca|| 8.67||
% carāṇi sthāvarāṇi ca| \T32
śiromadhye mahādevaḥ sarvadevapatiḥ sthitaḥ|
lalāṭāgre sthitā devī nāsāvaṃśeṣu ṣaṇmukhaḥ|| 8.68||
% lalāṭe pārvatīdevī nāsāgre caiva ṣaṇmukhaḥ| \T32
kambalāśvatarau nāgau nāsāpuṭasamāśritau|
% kamalāśvatarau nāgau  \T32
karṇayoraśvinau devau cakṣuṣo śaśibhāskarau|| 8.69||
% karṇayoraśvinīdevau netre ca \T32
danteṣu vasavaḥ sarve jihvāyāṃ varuṇāḥ sthitaḥ|
% danteṣu vāyavaḥ sarve jihvāyāṃ varuṇaḥ sthitaḥ| \T32
sarasvatī ca huṅkāre yamayakṣau ca gaṇḍayoḥ|| 8.70||
sandhyādvayaṃ tathaivoṣṭhe grīvāmidraḥ samāśritaḥ|
% sandhyādvayaṃ tathoṣṭau ca grīvāyāmidra āśritaḥ| \T32
ṛkṣāṇi kakudagre ca sandhyā corasi saṃsthitā|| 8.71||
% ṛkṣāṇi ca kakuddeśe \T32
catuṣpāt sakalo dharmaḥ svayaṃ jaṅghāsu saṃsthitaḥ|
khuramadhye tu gandharvāḥ khurāgreṣu ca pannagāḥ|| 8.72||
% ūrumadhyeṣu gandharvāḥ \T32
khurāṇāṃ paścimāgreṣu gaṇāścāpsarasaḥ sthitāḥ|
% khurāṇāṃ paścimāgre ca aparāśca samāśritāḥ| \T32
rudraikādaśikā pṛṣṭhe vāyuḥ sarveṣu sandhiṣu|| 8.73||
% rudraikādaśakaṃ pṛṣṭhe vasavaḥ sarvasiddhiṣu| \T32
śroṇīsaṃsthāśca pitaraḥ sthitā yonau tu mātaraḥ|
% śroṇītaṭasthāḥ pitaraḥ \T32
śrīrapāne gavānnityaṃ dharmo lāṅgūlamāśritaḥ|| 8.74||
% śrīrapāne gavāndanyan nāgā lāṅgūlasaṃśritāḥ| \T32
ādityaraśmayo bāle piṇḍībhūtā vyavasthitāḥ|
% vāle \T32
sākṣācca gaṅgā gomutre gomaye yamunā sthitā|| 8.75||
% sākṣādgaṃgā ca gomūtre \T32
aṣṭāviṃśaddevakoṭyo romakūpeṣu saṃsthitāḥ|
ṛṣayaśca sadā sarve romatve ca vyavasthitāḥ|| 8.76||
% ṛṣayaśca tathā sarve romarandhreṣu saṃsthitāḥ| \T32
udare pṛthivī sarvā saśailavanakānanā|
% udare pṛthivī devī \T32
catvāraḥ sāgarāḥ pūrṇā gavāṃ ye tu payodharāḥ|| 8.78||
% jaṭhare gārhyapatyāgni hṛdaye dakṣi.āgnikaḥ| \T32
% mukhe cāvahanīyo.agniḥ tahā cāṅge pativratāḥ| \T32
% asthiśukle sthitassarve hyaśvamedhādikaḥ kratuḥ| \T32
%% The above three lines are missing in the printed edtion, from Nepal.
etaddhi kathitaṃ sarvaṃ yathā goṣu pratiṣṭhitam|
% etacca kathitaṃ sarvaṃ goṣu yacca vyavasthitam| \T32
goṣu dattaṃ hutaṃ bhuktaṃ goṣu sarvaṃ carācaram|| 8.79||
tasmānna hiṃsyā gāvo vai pālayettaśca sarvadā|
% tasmādgāvo na hiṃsyāttu pālanīyāśca sarvadā| \T32
gāvaḥ stutyāśca nandyāśca gāvo māṃ pāntu nityaśaḥ|| 8.80||
% gāvaḥ stutyāśca vandyāśca \T32
%% p.98
%% This page records no verses; instead, it records only the commentary of the editor Naraharinath.
%% p.99
brahmaṇā brahma śabdena stūyate yaḥ sadā haraḥ|
% stūyate praṇavena yaḥ| \T32
sa śivaḥ śāśvato devo goṣu mārīṃ vyapohatu|| 8.81||
yo.arcyate satataṃ bhaktyā viṣṇunā prabhaviṣṇunā|
sa śivaḥ śāśvato devo goṣu mārīṃ vyapahatu|| 8.82||
%% Above verse 82 is missing in T32.
lambodareṇa devena gajavaktreṇa yaḥ stutaḥ|
% ihāmutrasthitāneka vighneśagaṇapūjitaḥ| \T32
sa śivaḥ śāśvato devo goṣu mārīṃ vyapohatu|| 8.83||
sarvarogahareṇāpi raviṇā yaḥ praṇamyate|
sa śivaḥ śāśvato devo goṣu mārīṃ vyapohatu|| 8.84||
%% In T32 the above verse 84 occurs between 82 & 83 of this edition.
śrīmatā rucirāṅgeṇa ghaṇṭākarṇagaṇena yaḥ|
% ghaṇṭākarṇaghanena yaḥ| \T32
nityaṃ praṇamyate bhaktyā hṛṣṭenātyantacetasā|| 8.85||
sa śivaḥ śāśvato devo goṣu mārīṃ vyapohatu|
nityaṃ rudrabalopeto rudraśaktisamanvitaḥ|| 8.86||
% nandinā daṇḍinā cāpi caṇḍinā bhārabhūtinā| \T32
% etairanyairgaṇairyakṣaiḥ sarvato.api viśeṣataḥ|| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
ghaṇṭākarṇagaṇo devo harājñānuvidhāyakaḥ|
% śivajñānuvidhāyakaḥ| \T32
śivatejo.anubhāvena goṣu mārīṃ vyapohatu|| 8.87||
% śivatojotibhāvena \T32
śivāya daivadevāya mahādevāya bhāvine|
% mahādevāya sambhave| \T32
rudrāya sthāṇave nityaṃ harāyograya te namaḥ|| 8.88||
parameśāya siddhāya mantrasiddhipradāyine|
% sarvasiddhipradāyine| \T32
tryambakāya maheśāya atiśāntāya te namaḥ|| 8.89||
% tryambakāya śāntāya śāntarūpāya te namaḥ| \T32
abhimantrya sadā toyam abhimantryairyathākramam|
% mantrairetairyathākramam| \T32
prokṣayīta gavāṃ dehaṃ tataḥ śāntirbhaviṣyati|| 8.90||
ya idaṃ paṭhate goṣu rogārtāsu viśeṣataḥ|
% ya imāṃ pathate goṣu \T32
gosāvitrīṃ sadā kālaṃ gavāṃ śāntirbhaviṣyati|| 8.91||
% go sāvitrīṃ mahāpuṇyāṃ \T32
prātarutthāya satataṃ gosāvitrīmimāṃ paṭhet|
gavāmutsavakāleṣu prasthāne vā samāgame|| 8.92||
% gavāṃ cotsargakāleṣu \T32
āyuṣmān balavān śrīmān gomānarthapatirbhavet|
dehānte ca paraṃ sthānaṃ sa gacchennātra saṃśayaḥ|| 8.93||
sarvapāpaviśuddhyarthaṃ gosāvitrīmimāṃ paṭhet|| 8.93A||
%% The above line is missing in T32.
prabhūtatoyeṣu bṛhattṛṇeṣu sapuṅgavānityamarogavatsāḥ|
carantu gāvaḥ sukhitā vaneṣu kṣīraṃ prayacchantu sukhaṃ sviyantu|| 8.94||
% kṣīraṃ prayacchantu sukhaṃ svapantu|| \T32
%% p.100 & 101
%% The above two pages reocrd no verses; instead, it records only the commentary of the editor Naraharinath.
%% p.102
yo.alaṅkṛtaṃ śivāyāśvamuttamaṃ vinivedayet|
so.aśvamedhasya yajñasya phalamaṣṭaguṇaṃ labhet|| 8.95||
suvinītāṃ striyaṃ dāsīṃ bhṛtyaṃ vāpi nivedayet|
% hṛdyāṃ vā vinivedayet| \T32
puruṣamedhayajñasya phalamaṣṭaguṇaṃ labhet|| 8.96||
% naramedhasya yajñasya \T32
nivedayati yo nāgān bhaktyā bhadramalaṅkṛtān|
% nāgaṃ \T32
śivāya parvadivase tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu|| 8.97||
%% p.103
sa mattairāvataprakhyairgajayuktaiḥ suśobhanaiḥ|
prakīḍati mahāyānaiḥ śatasaṃkhyairanekaśaḥ|| 8.98||
kalpakoṭisahasrāṇi kalpakoṭyayutāni ca|
% kalpakoṭiśatāni ca| \T32
rudraloke gataścānte bhavedindraḥ surādhipaḥ|| 8.99||
% rudraloke vasedante \T32
caturyugasahasrānte svargaṃ prāpya narādhipaḥ|
% sa gāṃ prāpya narādhipaḥ| \T32
bhavedindrasamaḥ śrīmān rūpavīryasamanvitaḥ|| 8.100||
% rūpavīryaśrutānvitaḥ| \T32
śivāya yaḥ phalopetāṃ sarvasasyaprarohaṇīm|
% yaḥ śivāya jalopetāṃ \T32
mahīṃ mahīpatirdadyāttasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu|| 8.101||
yāvaddaṇḍā bhaved bhūmirmīyamānā samantataḥ|
% samatataḥ \ed
tāvatsa kalpasaṃkhyānaṃ rudraloke mahīyate|| 8.102||
% tāvatkalpasahasrāṇi \T32
%% p.104
evaṃ sarvatra vijñeyaṃ phalaṃ daṇḍapramāṇataḥ|
grāmakṣetrapurakṣetraviṣayān vinivedayet|| 8.103||
% grāmakheṭapurakṣetraviṣayādinivedane| \T32
sarvasasyaphalopetān sarvabādhāvivarjitān|
% sarvasasyaphalopetaṃ sarvabādhāvivarjitam| \T32
grāmaṃ śivāya yo dadyāt tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu|| 8.104||
sarvatīrtheṣu yat puṇyaṃ sarvayajñeṣu yat phalam|
sarvadāneṣu yat puṇyaṃ grāmadānena tatphalam|| 8.105||
% grāmadānena tallabhet| \T32
sūryakoṭipratīkāśairdivyastrīkoṭisaṃyutaiḥ|
% divyastrībhiralaṃkṛtaiḥ| \T32
saṃyuktaḥ koṭiśo.anekaiḥ sarvakāmasamanvitaiḥ|| 8.106||
% saṃyuktaṃ koṭiśonekaiḥ sarvakāmasamanvitaiḥ| \T32
vimānairgrāmadānena trisaptakulasaṃyutaḥ|
yatheṣṭamaiśvare loke krīḍate kālamakṣayam|| 8.107||
puṇyaṃ nagaradānasya grāmadānācchatādhikam|
deśadānena cānantaṃ na śakyaṃ tatprakīrtitum|| 8.108||
% na śakyaṃ parikīrtitum| \T32
ratnānnapānagotrājārdya sarvabhūmeḥ prajāyate|
% ratnānnapānagotvādyaṃ \T32
tasmād bhūmipradānena naro bhavati sarvadaḥ|| 8.109||
yo.anyadattāṃ svadattāṃ vā hared bhūmiṃ narādhamaḥ|
% bhūmiṃ harati mānavaḥ| \T32
prapatyakṣayaṃ kālaṃ narakeṣu krameṇa saḥ|| 8.110||
% prapācyate.akṣayaṃ kālaṃ narakeṣu yathākramam| \T32
%% p.105
sarvaṃ vā bhūmiharaṇe hṛtameva na saṃśayaḥ|
% sarvaṃ vā bhūmiharaṇād \T32
bhūmihartā vasettasmān narake kālamakṣayam|| 8.111||
% bhūmihartā vasettasya \T32
devasvāni harantīha narāṃ narakanirbhayāḥ|
brahmasvāni ca ye mohāt pacyante narakeṣu ca|| 8.112||
% brahmasvāni ca yo mohāt \T32
% devabrahmasvapuṣṭāni vāhanāni mahīpateḥ| \T32
% yuddhakāle viśīryante saikatāḥ setavo yathā|| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
yatpradānātvaset svargaṃ yāvatkālasya saṃkhyatā|
tasmācchataguṇaṃ kālaṃ taddhṛtvā narake vaset|| 8.113||
% taddhartā narake vaset| \T32
viṃśatyaṣṭau ca yā koṭyo narakāṇāṃ sudāruṇāḥ|
krameṇa tāsu pacyante devabrahmasvahāriṇaḥ|| 8.114||
kalpānte ca samuttīrṇā vṛkṣaphīṭādiyiniṣu|
% vṛkṣakīṭādiyoniṣu| \T32
bhavanti suciraṃ kālaṃ kṣutpipāsādipīḍitāḥ|| 8.115||
evaṃ bhramantaḥ suciram īśvarājñāpracoditāḥ|
%% The above line is missing in T32.
kenacicchivabhaktena śivārcāyatanādiṣu|| 8.116||
tato nirdhūtapāpāste narāḥ syuḥ śivatejasā|
% tato nirdhūtapāpāste mānavāḥ śivatejasā| \T32
divaṃ prayānti santyajya śarīraṃ pātanātmakam|| 8.117||
% śarīraṃ yātanātmakam| \T32
sambhavanti śivakṣetre śivārcanaparā narāḥ|| 8.117A||
%% The above line is missing in T32.

\Colo
iti śivadharme śivadānaphalādhyāyo.aṣṭamaḥ|
% iti śivadharmaśāstre aṣṭamo.adhyāyaḥ | \T32

%% p.106

%% Chapter 9

atha paśupatimate śivadharme mahāśāstre śivaliṅgamahāvratannāma navamo.adhyāyaḥ||
oṃ namaḥ śivāya|
nandikeśvara uvāca|
% nandikeśvaraḥ \T32
ataḥ paramidaṃ puṇyaṃ vaks.yāmi munisattama|
puṇyātiśayasaṃyuktaṃ sarvadevanamaskṛtam|| 9.1||
% sarvadevairanuṣṭhitam| \T32
brahmaṇā viṣṇunā devyā skandenendreṇa yamena ca|
% skandendrābhyāṃ yamena ca| \T32
varuṇādityasomāgnimaruddhanadanāradaiḥ|| 9.2||
dharmaśrīśukranakṣatravilohitaśanaiścaraiḥ|
viśvāmitravasiṣṭhātribṛhaspatibudhādibhiḥ|| 9.3||
śvetāgasyadadhīcādyaiḥ sarvaiśca munisattamaiḥ|
bhṛṅgimātṛmahākālacaṇḍeśvaragaṇādhipaiḥ|| 9.4||
% bhṛṅgamātramahākālacaṇḍidaṇḍigaṇādhipaiḥ| \T32
vṛṣavāsukikarkoṭakulikānantatakṣakaiḥ|
śaṅkhapadmamahāpadmairanyaiścāpi mahoragaiḥ|| 9.5||
% mahāragaiḥ \ed
siddhayakṣaiḥ kimpuruṣairbahubhiśca mahātmabhiḥ|
% siddhayakṣaiḥśca gandharvaiḥ bhūtaiḥ kiṃpuruṣādibhiḥ| \T32
apasarodaityagandharvai rakṣokṣatagaṇairapi|| 9.6||
% vasubhiścopasaraiḥ sūryaiḥ rakṣobhūtagaṇiarapi| \T32
śivā gatiryathā prāptā sarvagatyatiśāyinī|
% śive gatiyathā \T32
mahādevaprasādena tathā vidhipraṃ śṛṇu|| 9.7||
% mayā ceśaprasādena \T32
%% p.107
sitacandanatoyena snāpya liṅgaṃ vilipya ca|
śvetairvikasitaiḥ padmaiḥ sampūjya praṇipatya ca|| 9.8||
paṅkaje vimale saumye niśchidre puṣpite ghane|
% tatra padmāsane saumye niśchidre puṣpite site| \T32
madhye keśarajālasya sthāpya liṅgaṃ kanīyasam|| 9.9||
aṅguṣṭhamātraṃ vidhivat sarvagandhamayaṃ śubham|
% aṅguṣṭhapratimaṃ liṅgaṃ sarvagandharvayaṃ śubham| \T32
sthāpya dakṣiṇāmūrtau tu bilvapatraistadarcayet|| 9.10||
aguruṃ dakṣiṇe pārśve paścime ca manaḥśilām|
uttare candanaṃ dadyāddharitālañca pūrvataḥ|| 9.11||
sugandhaiśca kusumairvicitraiścāpi pūjayet|
% sugandhaiḥ kusumairanyaiḥ \T32
dhūpaṃ kṛṣṇāgurundadyāghayataścāpi saguggulum|| 9.12||
% dhūpaṃ kṛṣṇāgaruṃ dadyāt saghṛtaṃ cāpi guggulum| \T32
vāsāṃsi cāpi sūkṣmāṇi vicitrāṇi nivedayet|
% vāsāṃsi ca susūkṣmāṇi vikeśāni nivedayet| \T32
pāyasaṃ ghṛtasaṃyuktaṃ ghṛtadīpāṃśca dīpayet|| 9.13||
% ghṛtadīpāṃśca dāpayet| \T32
sarvaṃ nivedya mantreṇa tato gacchet pradakṣiṇām|
% pradakṣiṇam| \T32
praṇamya bhaktyā deveśaṃ stutvā cānte kṣamāpayet|| 9.14||
sarvopahārasaṃyuktaṃ tacca liṅgaṃ nivedayet|
% tato liṅgaṃ nivedayet| \T32
śivāya śivamantreṇa dakṣiṇāṃ mūrtimāśritāḥ|| 9.15||
% śivāya śivamantraiśca dakṣiṇāmūtimāśritaḥ| \T32
anena vidhinā devāḥ sarve devatvamāgatāḥ|
devī devītvamāpannā guhaḥ skandatvamāgataḥ|| 9.16||
brahmā brahmatvamāpanno viṣṇurviṣṇutvamāgataḥ|
% harirviṣṇutvamāgataḥ| \T32
indraśca devarājatvaṃ gaṇāśca gaṇatāṃ gatāḥ|| 9.17||
munayo mokṣamāpanno mātaro mātṛtāṃ gatāḥ|
%% The above line 18ab is missing in T32.
evaṃ yo.arcayate liṅgaṃ padmagandhakṛtaṃ sakṛt|| 9.18||
% padmairgandhamayaṃ śubham| \T32
sarvapāpavinirmuktaḥ śivamevābhigacchati|
% śivalokamavāpnuyāt| \T32
etadvratottamaṃ guhyaṃ śivaliṅgamahāvratam|| 9.19||
%% p.108
bhaktasya te mayā khyātaṃ na deyaṃ yasya kasya cit|
% śivabhakte sadā deyaṃ śivena kathitaṃ purā| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
ciraparyuṣitaṃ mālyaṃ śivasyāpanayeta yaḥ|| 9.20||
% śivasyāpanayettu yaḥ| \T32
gosahasraphalantasya bhavatīha na saṃśayaḥ|| 9.20A||

\Colo
iti śivadharmaśāstre śivaliṅgamahāvratannāma navamo.adhyāyaḥ|

%% p.109

%% Chapter 10

atha paśupatimate śivadharme mahāśāstre upavāsagodānavidhirnāma daśamo.adhyāyaḥ|
oṃ namaḥ śivāya|
nandikeśvara uvāca
% nandikeśvara \T32
caturdaśyāmathāṣṭamyāṃ pakṣayorubhayorapi|
% pakṣayoḥ śuklakṛṣṇayoḥ| \T32
abdamekatra bhuñjīta śivārcanarataḥ śuciḥ|| 10.1||
% yobdamekaṃ na bhuṃjīta \T32
yatpuṇyamakṣayaṃ proktaṃ satataṃ satrayājinām|
satyavādiṣu yat puṇyaṃ yat puṇyaṃ tīrthagāminām|| 10.2||
agnihotṛṣu yat puṇyaṃ yat puṇyaṃ yajñayājinām|
% agnihotriṣu \T32
tat puṇyaṃ sakantasya śivalokaṃ sa gacchati|| 10.3||
% tat puṇyaṃ sakalaṃ prāpya \T32
yaḥ pṛthvīṃ bhojanaṃ kṛtvā bhukṅkte parvasu yatnataḥ|
% pṛthivīṃ bhājanaṃ kṛtvā bhuktaḥ parvasu yatnataḥ| \T32
ahorātreṇa caikena trirātraphalamaśnute|| 10.4||
dvayormāsasya pañcamyordvayoḥ pratipadornaraḥ|
sopavasaḥ sugandhāṅgaḥ śayīta priyayā saha|| 10.5||
śete niścalacittastu ratiprītivivarjitaḥ|
% śete niścalacitto yo ratikrīḍādivarjitaḥ| \T32
śivānusmṛtiśīlasya tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu|| 10.6||
% śivānusmṛtacittasya \T32
divyavarṣasahasrañca divyavarṣaśatantathā|
% divyavarṣasahasrāṇi \T32
tapastaptaṃ matattena bhavedatra na saṃśayaḥ|| 10.7||
% bhavedeva na saṃśayaḥ| \T32
bhavabhaktiḥ sa pūtātmā yadyapi syātpāpakṛt|
% bhavabhakti supūtātmā \T32
śivaloke vasennityaṃ śivavat saṃvṛto gaṇaiḥ|| 10.8||
%% p.110
kṛṣṇāṣṭamyāstu naktena yāvat kṛṣṇā caturdaśī|
% kṛṣṇāṣṭamyāṃ tu naktāśī \T32
iha bhogamavāpnoti paratra ca śivāṃ gatim|| 10.9||
yo.abdamekaṃ prakurvīta naktaṃ parvasu parvasu|
% yo.abdamekaṃ na bhuṃjīta \T32
brahmacārī jitakrodhaḥ śivasyārcanatatparaḥ|| 10.10||
% śivārcājapatatparaḥ| \T32
saṃvatsarānte viprendrān śivabhaktān samāhitān|
% śivabhaktān sadakṣiṇam| \T32
bhojayitvā tato brūyāt prīyatāṃ bhagavān śivaḥ|| 10.11||
% bhojayedyastu vidvāṃsaṃ kapālavratadhāriṇam| \T32
% bhojitāstena deveśā brahmaviṣṇumaheśvarāḥ|| \T32
% kapālapūrṇamaśanaṃ bhaikṣaṃ yo yasya gṛhṇāti| \T32
% kulaṃ tasyoddharatyeva daśa pūrvaṃ daśāparam|| \T32
% pādyādhyārcanamanīyāni gandhapuṣpaiḥ samantataḥ| \T32
% arcayedatinandaṣṭvā paścādbhaikṣyeṇa tarpayet|| \T32
% pūjitastaiḥ śivaḥ sākṣāt pūjito nātra saṃśayaḥ| \T32
% avamateravamataḥ syāt svayaṃ vai parameśvaraḥ|| \T32
% śraddhayā parayā yuktaḥ kapāle yaḥ prayacchati| \T32
% tattasya phalate dānaṃ vrajecchatasahasradhā|| \T32
%% The above lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
evaṃ vidhisamāyuktaḥ śivalokaṃ sa gacchati|
% śivaloke mahīyate| \T32
na ca mānuṣyakaṃ lokamadhruvaṃ prāpnuyānnaraḥ|| 10.12||
% na ca mānuṣyakaṃ dehaṃ punaḥ samprāpnuyānnaraḥ| \T32
%% p.111
upavāsatparaṃ bhaikṣaṃ bhaikṣātparamayācitam|
ayācitātparaṃ naktaṃ tasmānnaktena vartayet|| 10.13||
devaistu bhuktaṃ pūrvāhne madhyāhne ṛṣibhistathā|
% devairyuktaṃ tu pūrvāhne \T32
aparāhne ca pitṛbhiḥ sandhyāyāṃ guhyakādibhiḥ|| 10.14||
sarvavelāmatikramya naktamuttamabhojanam|
% sarvāṃ velāmatikramya \T32
vāmācāro mahādevo naktenoddharate narān|| 10.15||
% kāmācāro \T32
haviṣyabhojanaṃ snānaṃ satyamāhāralāghavam|
agnikāryamadhaḥ śayāṃ naktabhojī samācaret|| 10.16||
kṛṣṇāṣṭamyāṃ prayatnena naktaṃ kṛtvā vidhānataḥ|
% kṛtvā naktaṃ vidhānataḥ| \T32
mārgaśīrṣe śubhe māse śaṅkarandevamarcayet|| 10.17||
pītvā śaktyā tu gomūtram anāhāro niśi svapet|
atirātrasya yajñasya phalamaṣṭaguṇaṃ labhet|| 10.18||
evaṃ pauṣe.api sampūjya śambhunāmānamīśvarm|
% evaṃ puṣye.api \T32
kṛṣṇāṣṭamyāṃ ghṛtaṃ prāśya vājapeyāṣṭakaṃ labhet|| 10.19||
% vājapeyaphalaṃ labhet| \T32
māghe maheśvaraṃ nāma kṛṣṇāṣṭamyāṃ prapūjayet|
niśi pītvā ca gokṣīraṃ gomedhāṣṭakamāpnuyāt|| 10.20||
% gomedhasya phalaṃ labhet| \T32
phālgune ca mahādevaṃ sampūjya prāśayettilān|
% phālgunyāṃ ca \T32
varṣalakṣaṃ mahābhogaiḥ śivaloke mahīyate|| 10.21||
% rājasūsya yajñasya phalamaṣṭaguṇaṃ labhet| \T32
caitre ca sthāṇunāmānaṃ kṛṣṇāṣṭamyāṃ prapūjayet|
yavāṃśca bharjitān prāśya sāśvamedhaphalaṃ labhet|| 10.22||
% yān susaṃcitān prāśya so.aśvamedhaphalaṃ labhet| \T32
vaiśākhe śivamiṣṭvā ca pivedrātrau kuśodakam|
% vaiśākhe śivanāmānaṃ iṣṭvā rātrau kuśodakam| \T32
puruṣamedhayajñasya phalamaṣṭaguṇaṃ labhet|| 10.23||
% pītvā puruṣamedhasya \T32
jyeṣṭhe paśupatiṃ pūjya gavāṃ śṛṅgodakaṃ pibet|
gavāṃ koṭipradānasya yat puṇyaṃ tadavāpnuyāt|| 10.24||
āṣāḍhe cogranāmānamiṣṭvā prāśya ca gomayam|
sautrāmaṇestu yajñasya phalamaṣṭaguṇaṃ labhet|| 10.25||
śrāvaṇe śarvanāmānam iṣṭvā piṣyākabhakṣaṇāt|
% piṇyākaṃ niśi bhakṣayet| \T32
varṣakoṭiśataṃ sāgraṃ rudraloke mahīyat|| 10.26||
māse bhādrapade.aṣṭamyāṃ tryambakaṃ nāma pūjayet|
% tryambakaṃ devamarcayet| \T32
prāśanād bilvapatrāṇām anantaṃ phalamāpnuyāt|| 10.27||
% prāśanaṃ bilvapatrāṇām \T32
%% p.112
īśvaramāśvine pūjya pītvā vai taṇḍulodakam|
% māse cāśvayuje.aṣṭamyāṃ īśvaraṃ nāma pūjayet| \T32
pauṇḍarīkasya yajñasya phalamaṣṭaguṇaṃ labhet|| 10.28||
% taṇḍulodakamālihya pauṇḍarīkāṣṭakaṃ labhet| \T32
kārttike rudranāmānaṃ sampūjya prāśayeddadhi|
agniṣṭomasya yajñasya phalamaṣṭaguṇaṃ labhet|| 10.29||
varṣānte bhojayed viprān śivabhaktiparāyaṇān|
pāyasaṃ madhusaṃyuktaṃ ghṛtenoparisaṃplutam|| 10.30||
% madhunā ca pariplutam| \T32
śaktyā hiraṇyavāsāṃsi bhaktyā tebhyo nivedayet|
nivedayīta rudrāya gāñca kṛṣṇāṃ payasvinīm|| 10.31||
% varṣamekaṃ caredevaṃ nairantaryeṇa yo naraḥ| \T32
% kṛṣṇāṣṭamīvrataṃ bhaktyā tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu|| \T32
% sarvapāpavinirmuktaḥ sarvaiśvaryasamanvitaḥ| \T32
% vasecchivapure nityaṃ na bhūyo bhuvi jāyate|| \T32
%% The above lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
puṇyotsaveṣu sarveṣu viṣuvadgrahaṇādiṣu|
dānopavāsahomādyam akṣayaṃ jāyate kṛtam|| 10.32||
%% p.113
%% This page records no verses; instead, it records only the commentary of the editor Naraharinath.
%% p.114
pratimāsaṃ pravakṣyāmi śivavratamanuttamam|
% śivavratamihottamam| \T32
dharmakāmārthamokṣārthaṃ naranāryādidehinām|| 10.33||
pauṣamāse tu samprāpte yaḥ kuryānnaktabhojanam|
% puṣyamāse \T32
satyavādī jitakrodhaḥ śāligodhūmagorasaiḥ|| 10.34||
% jitendriyaḥ satyavādī \T32
pakṣayoraṣṭamīṃ yatnādupavāsena vartayet|
trisandhyamarcayedīśam agnikāryañca śaktitaḥ|| 10.35||
bhūmiśayāñca māsānte paurṇamāsyāṃ ghṛtādibhiḥ|
% bhūmiśāyī tu māsānte \T32
kṛtvā snānaṃ mahāpūjāṃ śive yatnāt prakalpayet|| 10.36||
naivedyaṃ yāvakaprasthaṃ kṣīrasiddhiṃ prakalpayet|
% nivedayet| \T32
bhojayīta dvijānaṣṭau śivabhaktān sadakṣiṇān|| 10.37||
% bhojayecca dvijānaṣṭau śivabhaktān sadakṣiṇam| \T32
śive gomithunañcaiva kapilaṃ vinivedayet|
% śivāyaivaṃ gomithunaṃ kāpilaṃ ca nivedayet| \T32
alaṅkṛtya surūpañca tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu|| 10.38||
sūryakoṭipratīkāśairvimānaiḥ sarvakāmikaiḥ|
rudrakanyāsamākīrṇairmahāvṛṣabhasaṃyutaiḥ|| 10.39||
saṅgītanṛtyavādyādyairapsarogaṇaśobhitaiḥ|
% apsarogaṇasevitaiḥ| \T32
cāmarairuddhūyamānaḥ stūyamānaḥ surāsuraiḥ|| 10.40||
% cāmarairdhūyamānaśca \T32
trinetraḥ śūlapāṇiśca sarvaiśvaryasamanvitaḥ|
% śivaiśvaryasamanvitaḥ| \T32
gacchecchivapuraṃ ramyaṃ yatrāste śaṅkaraḥ svayam|| 10.41||
yāvattadromasaṃkhyānaṃ tatprasūtikuleṣu ca|
tāvadyugasahasrāṇi sukhī śivapure vaset|| 10.42||
trisaptakulajaiḥ sārdhaṃ bhogān bhuktvā yathepsitān|
% bhogān bhuṅkte yathecchayā| \T32
jñānayogaṃ samāsādya sa tatraiva vimucyate|| 10.43||
yogādduḥkhāntamāpnoti jñānādyogaḥ pravartate|
śivadharmādbhavejjñānaṃ śivadharmaḥ śivārcanāt|| 10.44||
% śivadharmodbhavaṃ jñānaṃ \T32
ityeṣa vaḥ samākhyātaḥ saṃsārārṇavavartinām|
%% p.115
mokṣapāyaḥ śivadharmaḥ śivāñcamaniveśinām|| 10.45||
% śivamokṣakramopāyaḥ śivāśramaniṣevaṇam| \T32
%% p.116
māghamāse tu samprāpte yaḥ kuryānnaktabhojanam|
% māghamāse śubhe prāpte \T32
kṛsarāṃ ghṛtasaṃyuktāṃ bhuñjānaḥ saṃyatendriyaḥ|| 10.46||
sopavāsaścaturdaśyāṃ bhavedubhayapakṣayoḥ|
% upavāsaścaturdaśyāṃ \T32
śivāya paurṇamāsyāñca pradadyādghṛtakambalam|| 10.47||
% śivāya pauṇamāsyante \T32
kṛṣṇāṃ gomithunaścātra śivāya vinivedayet|
% kṛṣṇagomithunaṃ cātra surūpaṃ vinivedayet| \T32
śeṣaṃ kṛtvā yathoddiṣṭaṃ pūrvoktaṃ tu phalaṃ labhet|| 10.48||
% pūrvoktaṃ labhate phalam| \T32
indranīlapratīkāśairvimānaiḥ śikhisaṃyutaiḥ|
% vimānaiḥ sarvakāmikaiḥ| \T32
gatvā śivapure ramye bhuṅkte bhogān yathepsitān|| 10.49||
% gatvā śivapuraṃ ramyaṃ bhogān bhuṅkte yathepsitān| \T32
samprāpte phālgune māse yaḥ kuryānnaktabhojanam|
śyāmākakṣīranīvārairjitakrodho jitendriyaḥ|| 10.50||
caturdaśyāmathāṣṭamyām upavāsarato bhavet|
paurṇamāsyāṃ mahāsnānaṃ pañcagavyairghṛtādibhiḥ|| 10.51||
valmīkāgrādibhṛdbhiśca gomūtracchāgalādibhistathā|
% valmīkāgrādimṛdbhiśca gomūtrairgomayādibhiḥ| \T32
tvagbhiśca kṣīravṛkṣāṇāṃ dhātrīgandhādibhistathā|| 10.52||
% dhātragandhādibhiḥ saha| \T32
dadyāt gomithunaṃ bhaktyā tāmrābhaṃ parmeṣṭhine|
śeṣamanyadyathoddiṣṭaṃ kṛtvāpnoti mahat phalam|| 10.53||
padmarāgapratīkāśairvimānairgajasaṃyutaiḥ|
% vimānaiḥ sarvakāmikaiḥ| \T32
gatvā śivapuraṃ divyaṃ pūrvoktaṃ labhate phalam|| 10.54||
%% p.117
caitramāse tu samprāpte yaḥ kuryānnaktabhojanam|
% caitramāse śubhe prāpte \T32
piṣṭhakaṃ payasā yuktaṃ bhuñjānaḥ saṃyatendriyaḥ|| 10.55||
% bhuñjāno vijitendriyaḥ| \T32
dadyād gomithunaṃ cātra pāṭalaṃ samalaṅkṛtam|
śivāyātisurūpañca śeṣaṃ pūrvavadācaret|| 10.56||
puṣparāgaprabhiaryānair divyāśvarathasaṃjñayā|
% divyāśvagaṇasaṃyutaiḥ| \T32
gacchecchivapuraṃ ramyaṃ duṣprāpyam akṛtātmabhiḥ|| 10.57||
% yāyācchivapuraṃ divyaṃ duṣprāpam akṛtātmabhiḥ| \T32
vaiśākhe māsi samprāpte yaḥ kuryānnaktabhojanam|
śālyannaṃ payasā yuktaṃ bhuñjānaḥ saṃyatendriyaḥ|| 10.58||
% śālyannaṃ kṣīrasaṃyuktaṃ \T32
goṣṭhaśāyī śivādhyāyī niśāyām ekavastradhṛk|
% ekavastravṛt| \T32
niyamañca yathoddiṣṭaṃ sāmānyaṃ sarvadācaret|| 10.59||
% sarvaṃ samyak samācaret| \T32
vaiśākhe paurṇamāsyāṃ yaḥ kuryāt snānaṃ ghṛtādibhiḥ|
% vaiśākhapūṇamāsyāṃ tu kṛtvā snānaṃ vratādibhiḥ| \T32
śivāyālaṅkṛta śvetaṃ dadyāt gomithunaṃ śubham|| 10.60||
% śivāyālaṃkṛtaṃ śvetaṃ \T32
%% p.118
haṃsakundenduvarṇābhairmahāyānairalaṃkṛtam|
% himakundenduvarṇāḍhyaiḥ \T32
suśvetavṛṣasaṃyuktaiḥ sa yātīśvaramandiram|| 10.61||
sarvātiśayarūpābhiḥ strībhiḥ saṃparivāritaḥ|
% strībhiśca parivāritaḥ| \T32
nīlotpalasugandhābhiḥ  krīḍate kālamakṣayam|| 10.62||
jyeṣṭhamāse tu samprāpte yaḥ kuryānnaktabhojanam|
% jyeṣṭhamāse śubhe prāpte \T32
śālyannaṃ payasā dhautam ājyakṣīreṇa saṃyutam|| 10.63||
% śālyannamambhasā dhautam ājyakṣīravivarjitam| \T32
vīrāsanī niśārddhaṃ syād divā grāmannagacchati|
% virasāni tu rātrau syād divā gāmanugacchati| \T32
hitakārī gavāṃ nityamahaṅkāravivarjitaḥ|| 10.64||
paurṇamāsyāṃ ca pūrvoktaṃ kuryāt snānādikaṃ vidhim|
deyaṃ gomithunaṃ cātra dhūmavarṇamalaṅkṛtam|| 10.65||
% deyaṃ gomithunaṃ caiva  . . . . . . . . . .| \T32
nīlotpaladalaprakhyairmahāyānairanuttamaiḥ|
% . . . . . . prakhyaiḥ mahāyānairmanoramaiḥ| \T32
mahāsiṃhanibaddhaiśca krīḍate kālamakṣayam|| 10.66||
%% p.119
āṣāḍhamāse samprāpte yaḥ kuryānnaktabhojanam|
% āṣāḍhe suśubhe prāpte \T32
bhūrikhaṇḍājyasammiśrān śaktūn dadyāt sagorasān|| 10.67||
% phullakhaṇḍājyasammiśraṃ dadyādbhaktaṃ sagorasam| \T32
dadyād gomithunaṃ gauraṃ śivāyālaṅkṛtaṃ śubham|
% dadyād gomithunaṃ ghoraṃ \T32
sāmānyañca vidhiṃ kuryāt sarvaṃ vā prākpracoditam|| 10.68||
% sāmānyaṃ ca vidhiṃ sarvaṃ yaḥ kuryāt prākpracoditam| \T32
śuddhasphaṭikasaṃkāśairyānaiḥ sārasavāhanaiḥ|
aṇimādiguṇairyuktaḥ śivavad vicaret svayam|| 10.69||
% śivavadvicared ayam| \T32
samprāpte śrāvaṇe māse yaḥ kuryānnaktabhojanam|
kṣīraṣāṣṭikabhaktena sarvabhūtahite rataḥ|| 10.70||
śvetāgrapādapauṇḍrañca dadyād gomithunaṃ śive|
sāmānyamakhilaṃ kuryād vidhinā yatprakīrtitam|| 10.71||
% vidhānaṃ yatprakīrtitam| \T32
savicitrairmahāyānairvicitrāśvaniyojitaiḥ|
gatvā śivapurandivyaṃ pūrvoktaṃ labhate phalam|| 10.72||
%% p.120
prāpte bhādrapade māse yaḥ kuryānnaktabhojanam|
hutaśeṣantu bhuñjāno vṛkṣamūlāśrito divā|| 10.73||
% hutaśeṣa prabhuñjāno \T32
rātrau cāyatane vāsaḥ sarvabhūtānukampakaḥ|
% rātrau cāyatane vāsī \T32
nīlaskandhaṃ vṛṣaṅgāñca śivāya vinivedayet|| 10.74||
niśākarakaraprakhyairvajravaidūryaśobhitaiḥ|
cakravākasamāyuktairvimānaissārvakāmikaiḥ|| 10.75||
gatvā śivapuraṃ ramyamamarāsuravanditaḥ|
% gatvā śivapuraṃ divyaṃ \T32
krīḍate sa mahāyānairyāvadābhūtasamplavam|| 10.76||
% sa krīḍate \T32
śrīmadāśvinamāse ca yaḥ kuryānnaktabhojanam|
% prāpte cāśvayuje māse \T32
ghṛtāśanaṃ prabhuñjānaḥ prasannātmā jitendriyaḥ|| 10.77||
vṛṣabhannīlavarṇābhamurodeśe samunnatam|
% vṛṣabhaṃ nīlavarṇaṃ ca urodeśe samānatam| \T32
vimucya dadyādrudrāya gomekāṃ samalaṅkṛtām|| 10.78||
% gomekāmapyalaṃkṛtām| \T32
vidhiśeṣañca pūrvoktaṃ yaḥ kartā samupācaret|
% vidhiśeṣamaśeṣeṇa pūrvoktaṃ samupācaret| \T32
prāṇānte ca paraṃ sthānaṃ prayāti śivavadvaśī|| 10.79||
% prayāti śivavatsukhī| \T32
svacchamauktikasaṅkāśairindranīlopaśobhitaiḥ|
jīvañjīvakasaṃyuktairvimānaiḥ sarvakāmikaiḥ|| 10.80||
sukrīḍate mahābhogairyāvadābhūta samplavam|
% saṃkrīḍate \T32
%% p.121
suśubhe kārtike māse yaḥ kuryānnaktabhojanam|| 10.81||
% prāpte tu kārtike māse \T32
kṣīrodanaṃ prabhuñjīta satyavādī jitendriyaḥ|
% kṣīrodanaṃ prabhuṃjānaḥ \T32
dadyād gomithunaṃ cātra kapilāṃ jvalanaprabhām|| 10.82||
% kapilaṃ ca jvalatprabham| \T32
pūrvoktaṃ ca vidhiṃ kṛtvā śivatulyaguṇo bhavet|
% pūrvoktaṃ ca vidhiṃ kuryācchivatulyabalo bhavet| \T32
kalpānalaśikhāprakhyairmahāyānairanuttamaiḥ|| 10.83||
% kalpānalasamaprakhyaiḥ mahāyānairmahābalaiḥ| \T32
mahāsiṃhakṛtāyogaiḥ śivavanmodate vaśī|
% mahāsiṃhakṛtāṭopaiḥ śivavacceṣṭate sukhī| \T32
mārgaśīrṣe śubhe māse yaḥ kuryānnaktabhojanam|| 10.84||
yavānnaṃ payasā yuktaṃ bhuñjānaḥ saṃyatendriyaḥ|
dadyādgomithunaṃ divyaṃ pāṇḍuraṃ samalaṅkṛtam|| 10.85||
śeṣaṃ śivāya pūrvoktaṃ vidhinā samupakrame|
% śivāya śeṣaṃ pūrvoktavidhinā samupācaret| \T32
sitapadmanibhairyānaiḥ śvetāśvarathasaṃyutaiḥ|| 10.86||
% śvetāśvavarasaṃyutaiḥ| \T32
gatvā śivapuraṃ divyaṃ śivatulyabalo bhavet|
%% p.122
ahiṃsāsatyamasteyaṃ brahmacaryaṃ dayā kṣamā|| 10.87||
% brahmacaryaṃ damo dayā| \T32
triḥ snānañcāgnihavanaṃ bhūśayyā naktabhojanam|
% trisnānaṃ \T32
pakṣayorupavāsena caturdaśyaṣṭamīṃ vaset|| 10.88||
% caturdaśyaṣṭamīṣu ca| \T32
ityevamādiniyamairācaredyaḥ śivaṃ vratam|
% ityevamādikriyayā saṃcareta śivavratam| \T32
śivabhaktāṃ tu yā nārī dhruvaṃ sā puruṣo bhavet|| 10.89||
strītvamapyuttamaṃ sā cet kāṅkṣate śṛṇu tadvratam|
%% The above two lines are missing in T32. But they are there in T779 (see IFP T779, p.86, verse 77). 
umāmaheśvarannāma sadāprītivivardhanam|| 10.90||
aviyogakaraṃ śāntaṃ dharmakāmārthasādhanam|
paurṇamāsyāmamāvāsyācaturdaśyaṣṭamīṣu ca|| 10.91||
naktamabdaṃ prakurvīta haviṣo brahmacāriṇī|
% haviṣyaṃ brahmacāriṇī| \T32
umāmaheśapratimāṃ hemnā kṛtvā suśobhanām|| 10.92||
rājatīṃ vāpi varṣānte snāpayitvā ghṛtādibhiḥ|
gandhapuṣpairalaṃkṛtya vastraputaiśca śobhanaiḥ|| 10.93||
% gandhamālyairalaṃkṛtya vastrayugmaiśca śobhanaiḥ| \T32
bhakṣyabhojyairaśeṣaiśca vitānadhvajacāmaraiḥ|
% bhaktyā bhojyairaśeṣaiśca \T32
bhojayecchivabhaktāṃśca dīnānāthaṃśca tarpayet|| 10.94||
śaktyā ca dakṣiṇāndadyācchivamantraiḥ kṣamāpayet|
% śivamante kṣamāpayet| \T32
tāmrakāṃsyādipātraṃ vā sitabhasmāvaguṇṭhitam|| 10.95||
kṛtvā cāyatane madhye pratimāṃ samprakalpayet|
% madhyapratimāṃ \ed
% madhye pratimāmupakalpayet| \T32
śirasādāya tatpātraṃ vitānachatraśobhitam|| 10.96||
% dhṛtvā śirasi tatpātraṃ \T32
dhvajaśaṃkhādivibhavaiḥ śivasyāyatanaṃ nayet|
liṅgamūtermaheśasya brahmaratnā nivedayet|| 10.97||
% vratasyānte nivedayet| \T32
tadvedyāṃ sthāpayetpātramupaśobhāsamanvitam|
% vedyānte sthāpayetpātraṃ \T32
śivaṃ pradakṣiṇīkṛtya praṇipatya kṣamāpayet|| 10.98||
% paścātpradakṣiṇīkṛtya \T32
samāpya tadvrataṃ puṇyaṃ śṛṇuyācca phalaṃ labhet|
% śṛṇu sā yatphalaṃ labhet| \T32
dvādaśādityasaṅkāśairmahāyānairanopamaiḥ|| 10.99||
% sūryakoṭipratīkāśaiḥ vimānaiḥ sarvakāmikaiḥ| \T32
yatheṣṭamaiśvre loke rudraiḥ sārdhaṃ pramodate|
kalpakoṭisahasrāṇi kalpakoṭyayutāni ca|| 10.100||
% kalpakoṭiśatāni ca| \T32
tadante sā mahābhogairviṣṇuloke mahīyate|
tataḥ karmāvaśeṣeṇa sarvakāmasamanvitā|| 10.101||
% sarvakāmasamanvitam| \T32
brahmaloke samāsādya paramaṃ sukhamāpnuyāt|
% brahmalokaṃ samāsādya paraṃ sukhamavāpnuyāt| \T32
brahmalokāt paribhraṣṭā śrīvatsukhavatī bhavet|| 10.102||
% śrīmatī paripūjitā| \T32
prājāpatyaṃ samāsādya lokālokanamaskṛtam|
% lokapālanamaskṛtā| \T32
%% p.123
bhogāṃśca suciraṃ labdhvā somaloke vaset sukham|| 10.103||
% bhogāṃśca rucirān bhuṃktvā somaloke mahīyate| \T32
somādaindraṃ pare lokamāsādyaindraṃ patiṃ labhet|
% somalokādaindralokaṃ āsādyendrapadaṃ labhet| \T32
indralokācca gāndharvaṃ sā lokaṃ prāpya modate|| 10.104||
% lokaṃ prāpya pramodate| \T32
gandarvaṃ patimāpnoti bhogān bhuktvā yathepsitān|
% gandharvarājapatinā sārdhaṃ bhoge vasecciram| \T32
mahāratnaprabhādīptairupaśobhitamadbhutam|| 10.105||
yakṣalokaminaṃ prāptā yathā kāmaṃ pramodate|
% yakṣalomamanuprāpya \T32
yakṣalokāt paribhraṣṭā krīḍate merumūrdhanī|| 10.106||
sthānāni lokapālānāṃ kramādāgatya modate|
%% The above two lines are missing in T32.
sā lokālokaparyante sarvasmin kṣitimaṇḍale|| 10.107||
yatra kvacitsukhaṃ divyantadaśeṣamavāpnuyāt|
evaṃ sā sarvalokeṣu bhogān bhuktvā yathepsitān|| 10.108||
kramādāgatya lokesmin rājānaṃ patimāpnuyāt|
yuvānaṃ rūpasampannamaśeṣapṛthivīpatim|| 10.109||
dharmārthakāmamokṣajñam imamāsādya modate|
% śivabhaktaṃ dṛḍhavratam| \T32
tataḥ sā dharmaśeṣeṇa bhavatīśvarabhāvitā|| 10.110||
% tato.asau karmaśeṣeṇa \T32
svakarmabhāvanāyogāt punaḥ prārabhate śubham|
% svakarmavāsanāyogāt \T32
śubhācca punarapyevaṃ yoniṃ yāti sahasraśaḥ|| 10.111||
% lokānyāti sahasraśaḥ| \T32
yāvannāpnoti nirvāṇaṃ tāvad bhamati karmaṇā|
% yāvadāpnoti nirvedaṃ \T32
tannirvedācca vairāgyaṃ vairāgyājjñānasambhavaḥ|| 10.112||
% nirvedāccaiva vairāgyaṃ \T32
jñānāt pravartate yoge yogādduḥkhāntamāpnuyāt|
%% p. 124
%% This page records no verses; instead, it records only the commentary of the editor Naraharinath.
%% p. 125
aṣṭamyāñca caturdaśyānniyatā brahmacāriṇī|| 10.113||
varṣamekaṃ na bhuñjīta mahābhogajigīṣayā|
varṣānte pratimāṃ kṛtvā pūrvavad vidhimācaret|| 10.114||
snādyantadvrataṃ prāpya pūrvoktāṃśca guṇāṃllabhet|
jāmbūnadamayairyānaiścaturdārairalaṅkṛtaiḥ|| 10.115||
gatvā śivapuraṃ divyamaśeṣaṃ bhogamāpnuyāt|
%% The above lines 113cd - 116ab occur between 118ab & cd of this edition. 
umāmaheśvarannāma vratamīśvarabhaṇitam|| 10.116||
kāruṇyāt sarvanārīṇānnarāṇāñca viśeṣataḥ|
tasmāt sarvaprayatnena umāmaheśvaraṃ vratam|| 10.117||
kartavyaṃ naranārībhiḥ sukhasyontaramāpnuyāt|
% duḥkhasyāntamavāpnuyuḥ| \T32
umādevīpriyārthantu tuṣṭena paramārthataḥ|| 10.118||
% tuṣṭenaivāntarātmanā| \T32
nārī caivopavāsena abda kṛṣṇācaturdaśīm|
% yā nāryupavasedekaṃ \T32
varṣānte pratimāṃ kṛtvā śālipiṣṭamayīṃ śubhām|| 10.119||
pītānulepanairmālyaiḥ pītavastraiśca pūjayet|
pūrvoktamakhilaṃ kṛtvā śivāya vinivedayet|| 10.120||
saptabhaumairmahāyānaistaptacāmīkaraprabhaiḥ|
yugakoṭiśataṃ sāgraṃ rudraloke mahīyate|| 10.121||
śivādisarvalokeṣu bhogān bhuktvā yathepsitān|
kramādāgatya loke.asmin yatheṣṭaṃ patimāpnuyāt|| 10.122||
yāmāvāsyānnirāhārā bhavedevaṃ sayantritā|
% bhavedabdamatandritā| \T32
śūlapiṣṭamayaṃ kṛtvā varṣānte vinivedayet|| 10.123||
% varṣānte tu nivedayet| \T32
śivāya rājataṃ padmaṃ suvarṇakṛtakarṇikam|
% asvarṇakṛtakarṇakam| \T32
bhaktyā cavinyasenmūrdhni śeṣaṃ pūrvavadācaret|| 10.124||
% bhaktyā vinyasya tanmūrdhni \T32
kāmato.api kṛtaṃ pāpaṃ bhrūṇahatyādikaṃ ca yat|
% bhrūṇahatyādi yadbhavet| \T32
tatsarvaṃ śūlahānena hanyānnārī na saṃśayaḥ|| 10.125||
% tatsarvaṃ śūlamānena cchidyānnārī na saṃśayaḥ| \T32
mahāpadmavimānena naranārīsamanvitā|
yugakoṭiśataṃ sāgraṃ śivaloke mahīyate|| 10.126||
īśalokādilokeṣu bhuktvā bhogānanekadhā|
% śivādisarvalokeṣu bhuktvā bhogān yathepsitān| \T32
ihaloke kramāt prāpya yatheṣṭaṃ patimāpnuyāt|| 10.127||
% imaṃ lokaṃ kramātprāpya \T32
pauṇamāsyāmupavasedabdamekaṃ suyantritā|
% pauṇamāsyāmamāvāsyāṃ abdamekaṃ dṛdhavratā| \T32
%% p.126
%% This page records no verses; instead, it records only the commentary of the editor Naraharinath.
%% p.127
varṣānte sarvagandhāḍhyāṃ pratimāṃ vinivedayet|| 10.128||
suvicitrairmahāyānairdivyagandhavibhūṣitaiḥ|
% supavitrairmahāyānaiḥ divyagandhavahaiḥ śubhaiḥ| \T32
yugakoṭiśataṃ sāgraṃ śivaloke mahīyate|| 10.129||
% yugakoṭiśataṃ divyaṃ \T32
yatheṣṭamaiśvare loke bhuktvā bhogānaśeṣataḥ|
kramādāgatya loke.asmin rājānaṃ patimāpnuyāt|| 10.130||
%% p.128
yā kārttikaṃ śubhaṃ māsamekabhaktena yāpayet|
% samprāpte kārtike māse eka bhuktena vartayet| \T32
