% māsena vinivedayet| \T32
aṣṭamyāñca caturdaśyāmupavāsaratā bhavet|
%% p.129
indranīlapratīkāśairvimānaiḥ sārvakāmikaiḥ|| 10.132||
varṣāyuśataṃ sāgraṃ rudraloke mahīyate|
% śivaloke mahīyate| \T32
yathāvatsarvalokeṣu bhogamāsādya sarvataḥ|| 10.133||
% bhogamāsādya dharmataḥ| \T32
kramādāgatya loke.asmin yatheṣṭaṃ patimāpnuyāt|
ityevaṃ sarvamāseṣu vidhistulyaḥ prakīrtitaḥ|| 10.134||
ekabhaktopavāsasya phalañca sadṛśaṃ viduḥ|
% ekabhuktopavāsasya \T32
kṣamā satyaṃ dayā dānaṃ śaucamindriyanigrahaḥ|| 10.135||
śivapūjāgnihomaśca santoṣāsteyabhāvanā|
% santoṣo.asteyabhāvanā| \T32
sarvavrateṣvaya dharmaḥ sāmānyo daśadhā smṛtaḥ|| 10.136||
% sarvavratesvayaṃ \ed
% sarvavrateṣu yaddharmaḥ \T32
viśeṣamapi pravakṣyāmi pratimāsavrataṃ prati|
mārgaśīrṣe śubhe māse vṛṣaṃ piṣṭasunirmitam|| 10.137||
%% p.130
gandhamālyairalaṅkṛtya śivāya vinivedayet|
vṛṣayuktairmahāyānair apsarogaṇasaṃyutaiḥ|| 10.138||
% ārohaṇasuśobhitaiḥ| \T32
varṣāyutaśataṃ sāgraṃ śivaloke mahīyate|
sarvadevanikāyeṣu samprāpya sukhamuttamam|| 10.139||
kramādāgatya loke.asmin rājānaṃ patimāpnuyāt|
pauṣamāse śubhe caiva śūlaṃ kṛtvā pinākine|| 10.140||
gandhapuṣpairalaṅkṛtya śivāya vinivedayet|
tāmarakāṃsyādipātraṃ vā kṛtvā dadyāt pinākine|| 10.141||
%% The above line 141cd is missing in T32.
mahāpuṣpakayānena divyagandhaprabhāviṇā|
% divyagandhapravāhinā| \T32
