bhuktvā tu vipulān bhogānaśeṣapurasambhavān|
samprāpyaiva kramālloke yatheṣṭaṃ patimāpnuyāt|| 10.143||
%% p.131
rathañcāśvayutaṃ māghe dīpamālyopaśobhitam|
% dīpamālāpraśobhitam| \T32
