% śvetāśvavarasaṃyutaiḥ| \T32
varṣāyutaśataṃ sāgraṃ rudraloke mahīyate|| 10.145||
anubhūyātulān bhogān aśeṣapurasambhavān|
kramādāgatya loke.asmin rājānaṃ patimāpnuyāt|| 10.146||
phālgune pratimāṃ pauṣṭīṃ kṛtvā.agurusamanvitām|
% kṛtvā rūpasamanvitām| \T32
gandhamālyairalaṅkṛtya sthāpayedīśvarālaye|| 10.147||
yānairapratimairdivyairgeyavādyasamākulaiḥ|
% gītavāditrasaṃkulaiḥ| \T32
