sarvāmaranikāyeṣu prāpya bhogān sudurlabhān|
samprāpte.asmin kralālloke yatheṣṭaṃ patimāpnuyāt|| 10.149||
%% p.132
% samprāpyaivaṃ \T32
caitrebhayaṃ kumārañca kṛtvā paiṣṭamalaṅkṛtam|
% caitre bhavakumāraṃ ca \T32
