abhiṣṭaṃ patimāsādya labhedbhāgaṃ sudurlabham|| 10.152||
taṇḍulāḍhakapiṣṭena kṛtvā kailāsaparvatam|
īśvaromāsamāyuktaṃ sarvadhātuvibhūṣitam|| 10.153||
% (sthāpya pātre yathokte ca ānayecchivamandire|
% śaradindupratīkāśaiḥ vimānaiḥ sārvakāmikaiḥ||) \T32
%% Above verse is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
kandarairnicitaṃ citrairlavaṇaprasthasaṃyutam|
% kandarairdividhaiścitraiḥ lavaṇaprasthasaṃyutaiḥ| \T32
sarvaratnasamāyuktaṃ sthāpayedīśvarālaye|| 10.154||
kailāsavratamityevaṃ vaiśākhyaṃ yā samācaret|
śivādisarvalokeṣu bhuktvā bhogānaśeṣataḥ|| 10.155||
kramādāgatya śailendraiḥ kailāse modate ciram|
% kramādāgatya loke.asmin rājānaṃ patimāpnuyāt| \T32
%% p.133
liṅgaṃ piṣṭamayaṃ kṛtvā jyeṣṭhamāse prayojayet|| 10.156||
% jyeṣṭhe māse savedikam| \T32
bhaktyā sampūjya gandhādyairvastrayugmena veṣṭayet|
upaśobhāviśeṣaiśca tatra jāgaramācaret|| 10.157||
% upaśobhāviśeṣeṇa \T32
prabhāte dhvajasaṅkāśair vimānaiḥ sārvakāmikaiḥ|
% śivāya vinivedayet| \T32
śuddhasphaṭikasaṅkāśairvimānaiḥ sārvakāmikaiḥ|| 10.157||
varṣakoṭiśataṃ sāgraṃ śivaloke mahīyate|
bhuktvā bhogān yathākāmān aśeṣapurasambhavān|| 10.158||
% yathākāmaṃ \T32
krīḍāviraktabhāvaiśca modate śaṅkarājñayā|
% krīḍāviśeṣabhāvaiśca modate śaṅkarālaye| \T32
kramādāgatya loke.asmin rājānaṃ patimāpnuyāt|| 10.159||
%% 134
gṛhaṃ piṣṭamayaṃ kuryādāṣāḍhe pitribhūṣaṇam|
%% hyāṣāḍhe saptabhaumikam| \T32
