gṛhopakaraṇairyuktaṃ muśalolūkhalādibhiḥ|
% sarvadhānyasamāyuktaṃ sarvamaṇḍanabhūṣitam| \T32
% sarvadhātusamākīrṇaṃ sarvaratnopaśobhitam| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
sarvaratnādigośvādvairdāsīśayādyalaṅkṛtam|| 10.161||
etaiḥ piṣṭamayaiḥ sarvaiḥ pradīpādyupaśobhitam|
% sudīpādyupaśobhitam| \T32
sarvabhakṣyasamākīrṇaṃ gandhamālyairalaṅkṛtam|| 10.162||
śvetaraktaśitaiḥ padmairdhajairvastraiḥ suśobhitam|
% śvetaraktāsitaiḥ pītaiḥ dhvajavastropaśobhitam| \T32
