śatabhaumairmahāyānairvimānaiḥ sārvakāmikaiḥ|
% saptabhūmairmahāyānaiḥ sarvabhogasamanvitaiḥ| \T32
varṣakoṭiśataṃ sāgraṃ śivaloke mahīyate|| 10.165||
bhuktvā tu vipulān bhogān sarvalokeṣvanukramāt|
prāpya taṃ sarvabhogāḍhyaṃ saptabhaumagṛhaṃ labhet|| 10.166||
% prāpnoti sarvabhogāḍhyaṃ \T32
%% p.135
sarvadhātukṣamākīrṇaṃ vicitradhvajaśobhitam|
nivedayīta śarvāya śrāvaṇe tilaparvatam|| 10.167||
svacchendranīlasaṅkāśaiyānairapratimaiḥ śubhaiḥ|
varṣakoṭiśataṃ sāgraṃ rudraloke mahīyate|| 10.168||
% varṣakoṭiśataṃ divyaṃ śivaloke mahīyate| \T32
vividhān bhuvane bhogānavāpyavipulān divi|
% bhuktvā tu sakalān bhogān sarvalokeṣvanukramāt| \T32
kramāllokamimaṃ prāpya rājānaṃ patimāpnuyāt|| 10.169||
kṛtvā bhādrapade māse śobhitaṃ śāliparvatam|
% vipulaṃ dhānyaparvatam| \T32
vinatādhvajavastrādyairdhātubhiśca nivedayet|| 10.170||
divākarakaraprakhyairmahāyānaiḥ suśobhanaiḥ|
varṣakoṭisahasrāṇi rudraloke mahīyate|| 10.171||
samprāpya vipulān bhogānaśeṣapurasambhavān|
kramādāgatya loke.asmin rājānaṃ patimāpnuyāt|| 10.172||
%% p.136
kṛtvā cāśvayuje māse vipulaṃ dhānyaparvatam|
%% The above lines 170cd - 173ad are missing in T32.
suvarṇavastrasaṃyuktaṃ śivāya vinivedayet|| 10.173||
suvicitrairmahāyānairvarabhogasamanvitaiḥ|
varṣakoṭisahasrāṇi rudraloke mahīyate|| 10.174||
% varṣakoṭiśataṃ sāgraṃ śivaloke mahīyate| \T32
rudralokādilokeṣu bhuktvā bhogān yathepsitān|
samprāpte.asmin kramālloke rājānaṃ patimāpnuyāt|| 10.175||
sarvadhyānyasamāyuktaṃ sarvabījarasādibhiḥ|
% sarvabījasamanvitam| \T32
sarvadhātusamāyuktaṃ sarvaratnopaśobhitam|| 10.176||
śṛṅgaiścaturbhiḥ saṃyuktaṃ vitānacchatraśobhitam|
gandhairmālyaistathā dhūpaiḥ pradīpaiścāpi śobhitam|| 10.177||
% gandhamālyaiśca puṣpaiśca pradīpaiścopaśobhitam| \T32
vicitrairnṛtyagītaiśca śṅkhavīṇādibhistathā|
% vividhairgītanṛttaiśca \T32
brhmaghoṣaistathā puṇyair maṅgalaiśca viśeṣataḥ|| 10.178||
% maṅgalaiśca niṣevitam| \T32
mahādhvajāṣṭakayutaṃ vicitrakusumojjvalam|
% aṣṭabhiśca dhvajairyuktaṃ vitānacchatraśobhitam| \T32
nagendraṃ merunāmānaṃ trailokyādhāramuttamam|| 10.179||
tasya murdhni śivaṃ kuryāt sarvadevanamaskṛtam|
% tasya mūrdhni \T32
daityagandharvabhūtāṃśca siddhayakṣagaṇāstathā|| 10.180||
% daityagandharvasiddhādyān yakṣabhūtagaṇāṃstathā| \T32
vidyādharāpsaronāgān ṛṣīṃśca sarvadevatāḥ|
% ṛṣīṃścāpi viśeṣataḥ| \T32
śālipiṣṭamayān kṛtvā sarvarūpān vicakṣaṇaḥ|| 10.181||
% śālipiṣṭamayaṃ sarvaṃ rūpaṃ kṛtvā vicakṣaṇaḥ| \T32
devasya dakṣiṇo haste śūlaṃ tridaśapūjitam|
evaṃ sarveṣu deveṣu kuryādastraṃ yathākramam|| 10.182||
% kuryādastrāṇyanukramāt| \T32
%% p.137
śivasya mahiṣīpūjāṃ kṛtvā carusamanvitām|
% śivasya mahatīṃ pūjāṃ kṛtvā citrasamanvitām| \T32
pūjayet sarvadevāṃśca daśadikṣu baliṃ haret|| 10.183||
vratino bhojayetpañca śivabhaktān sadakṣiṇān|
% viprāṃśca bhojayetpaścāt \T32
dīkṣitān vartinaścaiva anugamya ca sāyugān| \T32
ācāryānugatān sarvān sārdhaṃ merumupasthitān| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
sarvārambhasamāyuktaṃ yathāvibhavakalpitam|| 10.184||
% sarvālaṃkārasaṃyuktaṃ yathā vibhavakalpitam| \T32
nivedayīta rudrāya kārttike nagamuttamam|
yā kuryāt sakṛdapyevaṃ tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu|| 10.185||
sarvāgameṣu yatpuṇyaṃ munibhiḥ kathitaṃ purā|
tatpuṇyaṃ koṭiguṇitaṃ prāpnuyānnātra saṃśayaḥ|| 10.186||
% tatsarvaṃ koṭiguṇitaṃ prāpnuyātsā na saṃśayaḥ| \T32
mahāratnaprabhairyānaiḥ sarvaratnasamanvitaiḥ|
gītanṛtyādivādyaiśca apsarobhiśca śobhitaiḥ|| 10.187||
% apsarogaṇaśobhitaiḥ| \T32
sūryakoṭisamaprakhyairvimānairmarusannibhaiḥ|
