% stūyamānanarādhipaiḥ| \T32
svacchandā sarvagā bhūtvā prayātīśvaramandiram|| 10.189||
kalpakoṭiśataṃ divyaṃ modate sā mahātapāḥ|
evaṃ sarveṣu lokeṣu bhuktvā bhogān yathepsitān|| 10.190||
puṇyakṣayādihāgatya rājānaṃ patimāpnuyāt|
% puṇyakṣayādihāgamya \T32
surūpā subhagā nityaṃ bhavatīśvarabhāvitā|| 10.191||
%% p.138
yaṃ yaṃ kāmaṃ samuddiśya naranārīnapuṃsakāḥ|
% yadyatkāmaṃ samuddiśya \T32
pūjayanti śivaṃ bhaktyā tattadeva (taṃ tameva)samāpnuyat(yaḥ)|| 192||
% tattadevāśu jāyate| \T32
mṛṇmayaṃ dārujaṃ śailamaiṣṭakaṃ vā sukalpitam|
kṛtvā maṭhaṃ gṛhaṃ vāpi yathāvibhavasambhavam|| 10.193||
% yathāvibhavavistaram| \T32
sarvopakaraṇopetaṃ sarvadhānyaprapūritam|
śivāya tadgṛhaṃ datvā sarvakāmamavāpnuyāt|| 10.194||
% sarvān kāmān avāpnuyāt| \T32
%% p.139
kṛtvaikabhaktaṃ hemante māghamāse suyantritaḥ|
% kṛtvaikaśuktiṃ hemante māsamekaṃ suyantritaḥ| \T32
māsānte ca rathaṃ kuryāccitravasropaśobhitam|| 10.195||
śvetaiścaturbhiḥ saṃyuktaṃ vṛṣabhaiḥ samalaṅkṛtam|
śobhitaṃ dhvajapūjādyaiścatracāmaradarpaṇaiḥ|| 10.196||
% śobhitaṃ dhvajadīpādyaiḥ chatracāmaradarpaṇaiḥ| \T32
taṇḍulāḍhakapiṣṭena liṅgaṃ kṛtvā savedakam|
% liṅgaṃ kṛtvā savedikam| \T32
vinyasya rathamadhye tu pūjayet kṛtalakṣaṇam|| 10.197||
tatrādau rājamārgeṇa śaṅkhabheryādiniḥsvanaiḥ|
bhrāmayitvā śanaiḥ paścācchivāyatanamānayet|| 10.198||
tatra jāgarapūjābhiḥ pradīpādyupaśobhitam|
prekṣaṇakapradānaiśca kṣapayīta śanairniśam|| 10.199||
% prekṣaṇīyapradānaiśca kṣapayitvā śanirniśām| \T32
prabhāte snāpanaṃ kṛtvā tadbhaktānāñca bhojanam|
dīnānāthakṛpaṇāṃśca yathāśaktisadakṣiṇān|| 10.200||
% yathāśaktyā ca dakṣiṇām| \T32
rathaṃ śobhāsamāyuktaṃ śivāya vinivedayet|
bhuktvā ca bāndhavaiḥ sārdhaṃ prāṇamyeśaṃ gṛhaṃ vrajet|| 10.201||
pravaraṃ sarvadānānāmasmin dharmaḥ samāpyate|
% sarvavratānāṃ pravaraṃ \T32
vrataṃ śivarathaṃ nāma sarvakāmārthasādhakam|| 10.202||
sarvavrateṣu yatpuṇyaṃ sarvayajñeṣu yat pahalam|
% sarvabhūteṣu yatpuṇyaṃ \T32
sarvaṃ śivarathenaiva tat puṇyaṃ sakalaṃ bhavet|| 10.203||
% tatsarvaṃ śivanāthenaiva tatpuṇyaphalabhāgbhavet| \T32
sūryāyutapratīkāśairvimānaiḥ sarvakāmikaiḥ|
trisaptakulajaiḥ sārdhaṃ śivaloke mahīyate|| 10.204||
% trisaptakulamuddhṛtya \T32
bhuktvā tu vipulān bhogān sarvaṃ deveṣvanukramāt|
kalpakoṭyayutaṃ sāgraṃ tasyānte sa mahīpatiḥ|| 10.205||
%% p.140
pañcaśūlīsamāyuktaṃ mṛdvīṃ khaṭvāmalaṅkṛtām|
% pañcatulīsamāyuktāṃ mṛdvīṃ khaṭvāṃ sukalpitām| \T32
sarvopakaraṇopetāṃ śivaśayyāṃ prakalpayet|| 10.206||
śivavedisamāyuktāṃ pauṣṭīṃ śayyānnivedayet|
% śivaṃ devīsamāyuktaṃ pauṣṭamasyāṃ nivedayet| \T32
śivajñānārthatattvajñe ācārye vinayānvite|| 10.207||
% śivajñānārthatattvajñaṃ ācāryaṃ vinayānvitam| \T32
sampūjya gandhapuṣpādyairvastrālaṅkāracāmaraiḥ|
bhakṣyabhojyairaśeṣaiśca tataḥ śayyānnivedayet|| 10.208||
%% p.141
tadūrṇātulavastrāṇāṃ parisaṃkhyā tu yāvatī|
% taṃtale vastratantūnāṃ \T32
tāvadvarṣasahasrāṇi rudraloke mahīyate|| 10.209||
śivādisarvalokeṣu bhuktvā bhogānaśeṣataḥ|
kramādāgatya loke.asmin siṃhāsanapatirbhavet|| 10.210||
daśa gāvaḥ savṛṣabhā vṛṣabhaikādaśī smṛtā|
% daśa gāvo vṛṣaścaiko \T32
śivāya vinivedyaiva viśuddhenānantarātmanā|| 10.211||
% śivāya vinivedyaivaṃ avadhāraya tatphalam| \T32
candraikādaśatulyātmā balabhogādibhirguṇaiḥ|
% rudraikādaśatulyāḍhyo \T32
śivādisarvalokeṣu yatheṣṭaṃ modate vaśī|| 10.212||
% yatheṣṭaṃ modate sukhī| \T32
kalpakoṭisahasrāṇi kalpakoṭyayutāni ca|
% kalpakoṭiśatāni ca| \T32
bhuktvā tu vipulān bhogān aśeṣakulajaiḥ saha|| 10.213||
tadante jñānamāsādya prasādātparameṣṭhinaḥ|
vimucya mohakalilaṃ svātmanyevāvatiṣṭhate|| 10.214||
%% p.142
savṛṣaṃ gośataṃ dadyācchivāyātīvaśobhanam|
triḥsaptakulajaiḥ sārdhaṃ śṛṇu yat phalamāpnuyāt|| 10.215||
sūryakoṭipratīkāśair vimānaiḥ sārvakāmikaiḥ|
% sarvakāmasamanvitaiḥ| \T32
anekākārasaṃkhyātair amarāsurapūjitaiḥ|| 10.216||
% mahāyānairasaṃkhyātaiḥ \T32
sa tu rudrabalopeto vīrabhadram ivāparaḥ|
% śatarudrabalopeto vīrabhadra ivāparaḥ| \T32
gatvā śivapuraṃ divyamaśeṣādhipatirbhavet|| 10.217||
bhuktvā tu vipulān bhogān pralaye sarvadehinām|
% pralaye samupasthite| \T32
mohakañcukamutsṛjya jñānakaivalyamāpnuyāt|| 10.218||
% sa kaibalyamavāpnuyāt| \T32
sarvajñaḥ paramaṃ śuddhaḥ svātmānyeva vyavasthitaḥ|
% sāmānyeva vyavasthitaḥ| \T32
sarvagaḥ paripūrṇāśca śivavatpariravyayaḥ|| 10.219||
dadyādubhayamukhīṃ gāṃ śivāyātīvaśobhanām|
% yodadyādubhayamukhīṃ śivāyātīvaśobhanām| \T32
saptadvīpāṃ kṣatindatvā yat phalaṃ tadavāpnuyāt|| 10.220||
% yatpuṇyaṃ tadavāpnuyāt| \T32
pādadvayaṃ śiro.ardhaśca yadā vatsasya nirgatam|
tadā gauḥ pṛthivī jñeyā yāvadgarbhannamuñcati|| 10.221||
% tadādau pṛthivī jñeyā taddātā syānmahīpradaḥ| \T32

\Colo
iti nandikeśvaraprokte śivadharme mahāśāstre
upavāsagopradānavidhirnāma daśamo.adhyāyaḥ||
% iti śivadharmaśāstre vratopavāsagopradānādhyāyo nāma daśamo.adhyāyaḥ| \T32

%% p.143

%% Chapter 11

sarveṣāmeva varṇānāṃ śivāśramaniṣeviṇām|
śivadharmaḥ śivenokto dharmakāmārthamuktaye|| 11.1||
% śivadharmāḥ \T32
brāhmaṇaḥ kṣatriyo vaiśyaḥ strīśūdro vā śivāśramī|
vānaprastho gṛhastho vā yaścānye vā gṛhāśramī|| 11.2||
% brahmacārī gṛhastho vā vānaprastho.atha bhikṣukaḥ| \T32
svāśramāduttare kuryāt puṣpārāmaṃ suśobhanam|
agnyagārasamāyuktam aiśānyāmīśvarālayam|| 11.3||
% āgneyāmagnyāgāraṃ ca \T32
pradeśāsambhave kuryād yatrāsya sambhavo bhavet|
% yatra syātsambhavo bhuvaḥ| \T32
śivāddakṣiṇataḥ kuryāt tadbhaktābhyāgatālayam|| 11.4||
% nairṛtyāṃ ca samiddeśaṃ vāruṇyāmudakāśrayam| \T32
% vāyavyāṃ dhānyadeśaṃ vai kauberyāṃ bhāṇḍagūḍhakam| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
trisandhyamarcayedīśam agnikāryañca śaktitaḥ|
trisandhyamekakālaṃ vā pūjayecchaktitaḥ śivam|| 11.5||
% ekakālaṃ trikālaṃ vā \T32
asampūjya śivaṃ mohānna bhuñjīta kadācana|
%% p.144
eṣa dharmaḥ paro jñeyaḥ śeṣo bhavati bhāvitaḥ|| 11.6||
% śeṣo bhavatu vā na vā| \T32
kāryātipātasaṃrodham ādyādinakakādiṣu|
% kāryātipātasaṃrodhād rāṣṭravibhramaṇādiṣu| \T32
manasā pūjayed bhaktyā dehānte cātyaye.api vā|| 11.7||
% vācikairvā japādibhiḥ| \T32
śivāśramāśritaiḥ pūjā kartavyā yatnataḥ sadā|
% kartavyā bhaktitaḥ sadā| \T32
manasā pūjayedyogī puṣpairvāraṇyasambhavaiḥ|| 11.8||
śivārthe puṣpahiṃsāyāṃ va bhavet sa tu hiṃsakaḥ|
yadyatpamapi cātmārthe hiṃsyāttu hiṃsakastadā|| 11.9||
% yadyalpamapi cātmārthaṃ hiṃsate hiṃsakastathā| \T32
śivārcāgnipato nityaṃ tadbhaktānāśca bhojanam|
% tadbhaktātithipūjakaḥ| \T32
parvamaithunavarjaḥ syācchīmān śivagṛhāśramī|| 11.10||
% parvamaithunavarjī syāddhīmāṃcchivagṛhāśramī| \T32
devāgnyatithibhaikṣyārthaṃ pacennaivātmakāraṇam|
ātmārthaṃ yaḥ pacenmohān narakāryaṃ sa jīvati|| 11.11||
% narakārthaṃ sa jīvati| \T32
devārthaṃ pacanaṃ yeṣāṃ santānārthantu maithunam|
% saṃtārārthaṃ ca maithunam| \T32
svargārthaṃ jīvitanteṣāṃ narakārthaviparyaye|| 11.12||
% narakārthaṃ viparyaye| \T32
vittatṛtīyabhāgena prakurvīta śivārcanam|
kurvīta vā tadardhena yato.anityaṃ hi jīvitam|| 11.13||
% tato.aniyaṃ hi jīvitam| \T32
nyāyenopārjayed vittam anyāyaṃ parivarjayet|
anyāyopārjitairvittarnarakārthaṃ sa jīvati|| 11.14||
% anyāyenārjitairdravayaiḥ \T32
%% p.145
yaḥ śivabrahmacārī syāt sa śivārcāgnitatparaḥ|
bhavejjitendriyaḥ śānto naiṣṭhiko bhūtiko.athavā|| 11.15||
sarvasaṅgavinirmuktaḥ kandamūlaphalāśanaḥ|
śivavaikhānaso jñeyaḥ śivārcāgniparo bhavet|| 11.16||
nivṛttaḥ sarvasaṅgebhyaḥ śivadhyānarataḥ sadā|
% nivṛttaḥ sarvarogebhyaḥ \T32
jñeyaḥ śivavratīndro.ayaṃ bhasmaniṣṭho jitendriyaḥ|| 11.17||
rudrākṣakaṅkaṇo haste jaṭiakā caiva mastake|
liṅgaṃ śivāśramasthānaṃ bhasmanā ca tripuṇḍrakam|| 11.18||
% śirasā dhārayetkoṭiṃ karṇayośca sahasrakam| \T32
% śatakoṭigalebaddhaṃ sahasraṃ bāhumadhyataḥ| \T32
% apramāṇaphalaṃ haste rudrākṣasya tu dhāraṇāt| \T32
% ucchiṣṭo vāpi kaṇṭhena yukto vā sarvapātakaiḥ| \T32
% haranti sarvapāpāśca rudrākṣasparśanena tu| \T32
% rudrākṣakaṇṭhamāśritya śvāno.api kriyate yadi| \T32
% so.api rudratvamāpnoti kiṃ punarmānavādayaḥ| \T32
%% Above verses are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
haste mūrdhnodvyupavīte vā rudrākṣandhārayedvratī|
agamyaḥ(myaṃ) sarvasattvānāṃ rudralokaṃ sa gacchati|| 11.19||
% āgamya sarvasatvānāṃ rudralokaṃ sa gacchati| \T32
rudrabhaktaiḥ śivasyaikā dhāryā rudrajaṭā sadā|
% rudrabhaktaiḥ sadā dhāryā rudrasaṃkhyā jaṭāḥ śubhāḥ| \T32
dhvaṃsanī sarvaduṣṭānāṃ rudratvaṃ samavāpnuyāt|| 11.20|\
% dhvaṃsanaṃ sarvaduḥkhānāṃ tābhi rudratvamāpnuyāt| \T32
sitena bhasmanā kuryāt trisandhyaṃ yastripuṇḍrakam|
%% p.146
rudrāgneryat paraṃ bījaṃ bhasmasma parikīrtitam|| 11.21||
% tadbhasma parikīrtitam| \T32
dhvasanaṃ sarvaduṣṭānāṃ sarvapāpaviśodhanam|
yogī sarvāṅgake snānam āpādatalamastakam|| 11.22||
% yogī sarvāṃgikasnānaṃ \T32
trisandhyam ācaren nityam āśu yogam avāpnuyāt|
yaḥ snānamācarennityam āgneyaṃ sa yatendriyaḥ|| 11.23||
% āgneyaṃ saṃyatendriyaḥ| \T32
kulaikaviṃśamuttārya sa gacchet paramaṃ padam|
% sa gacchet paramāṃ gatim| \T32
bhasmasnānaṃ jalasnānād asaṃkhyeyaguṇādhikam|| 11.24||
tasmād vāruṇamutsṛjya snānamāgneyam ācaret|
sarvatīrtheṣu yatpuṇyaṃ sarvatīrtheṣu yatphalam|| 11.25||
% sarvayajñeṣu yatphalam| \T32
tatphalaṃ labhate nityaṃ bhasmasnānānna saṃśayaḥ|
% tatphalaṃ labhate sarvaṃ \T32
mahāpātakasaṃyukto yukto vā sarvapātakaiḥ|| 11.26||
% mahāpātakasaṃyukto vā \T32
bhasmasnānaṃ niṣevīta mucyate sarvapātakaiḥ|
bhasmasnānāt paraṃ snānaṃ pavitraṃ naiva vidyate|| 11.27||
uktaṃ devamunirdevaiḥ snāto devaḥ svayaṃ śivaḥ|
% ityuktvā munidevebhyaḥ snāto.anena śivaḥ svayam| \T32
%% p.147
tataḥ prabhṛti brahmādyāmunayaśca śivārthinaḥ|| 11.28||
sarvaparvasu yatnena bhasmasnānaṃ pracakrire|
tasmādeva śivasnānamāgneyaṃ yassamācaret|| 11.29||
anenaiva śarīreṇa sa rudro nātra saṃśayaḥ|
duḥśīlaḥ śīlayukto vā yo vā sovāpyalakṣitaḥ|| 11.30||
% duḥśīlo yukto vā yo vā ko.avāpya lakṣaṇam| \T32
bhūtiśāsanasaṃyogāt sa pūjyo rājapātravat|
% bhūtiśāsanasaṃyuktaḥ sa pūjyo rājapūtravat| \T32
guṇavat pātrapūjāyāṃ tasya śāsanapūjanam|| 11.31||
śāsanaṃ pūjayet tasmād avicāraṃ śivājñayā|
rudrāgneryatparaṃ bījaṃ tadbhasma parikīrtitam|| 11.32||
dāhavatsarvaduḥkhānāṃ tasmād bhasmeti cocyate|
%% The above two lines 32cd & 33ab are missing in T32.
śivājñāpūjanāttasmācchivo bhavati pūjitaḥ|| 11.33||
vivaikalpamatistasmāt pūjayecchivaśāsanam|
% avikalpamatistasmāt \T32
chadmanāpi hi yo dhatte bhūtiśāsanamaiśvaram|| 11.34||
%% The above line 34cd is missing in T32.
so.api yāṃ gatimāpnoti na tāṃ yajñaśatairapi|
ācamedvidhivattoyaṃ nirlepaḥ śivabhasmanā|| 11.35||
% ācamettoyavidhinā \T32
gandhalepaviśuddhyarthaṃ nityamambha upaspṛśet|
% nityamadbhirupaspṛśet| \T32
gandhalepaviśuddho.api bhāvaduṣṭo na śuddhyati|| 11.36||
% gandhalepavihīno.api bhātuṣṭo viśuddhyati| \T32
bhāvaśuddhyā bhavecchuddhaḥ śuddhabhāvastato bhavet|
% bhāvaśudhyābhavecchuddhiḥ \T32
% bhasmasnānena yatpūrvaṃ pāpamāmaraṇāntikam| \T32
% janmāntarakṛtaṃ yattad dahatyagnirivendhanam| \T32
% snānaṃ vāruṇamāgneyaṃ divyaṃ vāyavyamānase| \T32
% paṃcasnānāni viprāṇāṃ vihitāni viśuddhaye| \T32
% vāruṇaṃ vāriṇā snānaṃ āgneyaṃ bhasmanā bhavet| \T32
% vṛṣṭyā sātapayā divyaṃ vāyavyaṃ rajasā gavām| \T32
% mānasaṃ dhyānamātreṇa vihitaṃ śivayoginām| \T32
%% The above lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
%% p.148
udakumbhasahasreṇa mṛdāḍhakaśatena yaḥ|| 11.37||
% mṛdhakaśatena vā| \T32
api varṣasahasreṇa bhāvaduṣṭo na śuddhyati|
bhāvaśuddhaścarecchaucaṃ vastrapūtaṃ jalaṃ pivet|| 11.38||
% bhāvapūtaṃ carecchaucaṃ \T32
dṣṭipūtaṃ nyasetpādaṃ satyapūtaṃ vaco vadet|
jaṭākalāpadhārī syāt pakṣārdhād vapanaṃ bhavet|| 11.39||
% pakṣe vā vapanaṃ bhavet| \T32
yadeva puṇyaṃ dīkṣāyāṃ tatpuṇyaṃ vapane punaḥ|
% yadeva puṇyaṃ yajñena tatpuṇyaṃ vapanādbhavet| \T32
jaṭī muṇdī śikhī vāpi bhikṣāśī vigataspṛhaḥ|| 11.40||
%% p.149
maunī bhūtānukampī ca yatiḥ śāntamatiścaret|
madhukarīñcared bhikṣām ekānnaṃ parivarjayet|| 11.41||
% madhukarīṃ caredvṛttiṃ \T32
upavāsātparaṃ bhaikṣam ekānnaṅgṛhiṇāmmalam|
% ekānnaṃ gṛhiṇā.a.ahṛtam| \T32
sarvasaṅgavinirmuktaḥ śuddhaḥ śivaparāyaṇaḥ|| 11.42||
% yaḥ sarvasaṃganirmuktaḥ śivaḥ śivaparāyaṇaḥ| \T32
yo.apīha vapanaṅkṛtvā yogīndrānucaro bhavet|
% sopīha vapanaṃ kṛtvā \T32
vasedāyatane nityaṃ sagaṇaḥ śivadhārmikaḥ|| 11.43||
% yogināmannadānena yogashtānamavāpnuyāt| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
puṣpārāmaikakarmātmā puṣpavāṭīkriyāparaḥ|
% puṣpārāmaikakartātmā \T32
trisnānapūjāsaṃyuktaḥ kaupīnācchāditaḥ sadā|| 11.44||
yogināṃ bhaktiyogena yogasthānamavāpnuyāt|
śivadhyānaparāḥ śāntāḥ śivadharmaparāyaṇāḥ|| 11.45||
% śivadhyānaparaḥ śāntaḥ \T32
sarva evāśramā jñeyāḥ śivabhaktāḥ śivāśramāḥ|
mahāvratāṣṭakaṃ dhāryam īśenoktaṃ śivārthibhiḥ|| 11.46||
% mahāvratāṣṭakaṃ kāryaṃ \T32
sarvavratānāṃ pravaram asmin dharmaḥ samāpyate|
śivabhaktiḥ sadā kṣāntirahiṃsā sarvadā śamaḥ|| 11.47||
% śive bhaktiḥ śive śāntiḥ  \T32
santoṣaḥ satyamasteyaṃ brahmacaryantathāṣṭamam|
yathāsambhavapūjābhiḥ karmaṇā manasā girā|| 11.48||
śive bhaktiḥ sadā kāryā tadvacca śivayogiṣu|
svadehānnirviśeṣeṇa śivabhaktāṃśca pālayet|| 11.49||
bhayadāridryarogebhyasteṣāṃ kuryāt priyāṇi ca|
śivasya paripūrṇasya kinnāma kiyate naraiḥ|| 11.50||
yat kṛtaṃ śivabhaktānāṃ tatkṛtaṃ hi śive bhavet|
% tat kṛtaṃ ca śive bhavet| \T32
sudūramapi gantavyaṃ yatra māheśvaro janaḥ|| 11.51||
prayatnenāpi draṣṭavyaṃstatra sannihito naraḥ(haraḥ)|
% tatra sannihito haraḥ| \T32
māheśvarasya bhaktasya śivārcanaratasya ca|| 11.52||
ājñāṃ kṛtvā yathānyāyamaśvamedhaphalaṃ labhet|
% pūjāṃ kṛtvā yathānyāyam aśvamehdapalaṃ bhavet| \T32
%% p.150
%% This page records no verses; instead, it records only the commentary of the editor Naraharinath.
%% p.151
nityaṃ śivakathāsakto nityaṃ śivaparāyaṇaḥ|| 11.53||
arcayitvā yathānyāyaṃ gāṇapatyaṃ labhennaraḥ|
% gāṇapatyamavāpnuyāt| \T32
śivāśramaṃ gataṃ bhaktyā śivabhaktaṃ prapūjayet|| 11.54||
% śivāśramagatān bhaktyā śivabhaktān prapūjayet| \T32
svāgatāsanapādārghamadhuparkādibhojanaiḥ|
% svāgatāsanapādyārghya \T32
svāgatasya namaskāraṃ kuryādapyabhivādanam|| 11.55||
% pūjayitvā yathānyāyaṃ yaḥ \T32
daśavarṣasahasrāṇi so.agniloke mahīyate|
% rudraloke mahīyate| \T32
prāptāya śivabhaktāya yo dadyāt svayamāsanam|| 11.56||
% prāptāya śivabhaktāya yo dadyācchubhamasanam| \T32
viṃśadvarṣasahasrāṇi purandarapure vaset|
% triṃśadvarṣasahasrāṇi \T32
śivabhaktaṃ gṛhe dṛṣṭvā tuṣṭiṃ vrajati yo naraḥ|| 11.57||
% prāptāya śivabhaktāya \T32
varṣakoṭisahasrāṇi purandarapure vaset|
% vasedvaiśravaṇālaye| \T32
śivabhaktāya viprāya pādau prakṣālya yatnataḥ|| 11.58||
% śivabhaktasya viprasya pādau prakṣyālya bhaktitaḥ| \T32
gṛtenābhyajya codvartya viṣṇuloke mahīyate|
śivabhaktaṃ dvijaṃ prāptaṃ madhuparkādyanukramāt|| 11.59||
% śivabhaktāndvijānprāptān \T32
bhojayitvā yathānyāyaṃ śivaloke mahīyate|
śrāntasaṃvāhanaṃ kṛtvā somalokamavāpnuyāt|| 11.60||
% somaloke mahīyate| \T32
pratiśrayapradānena haimaṃ svarge gṛhaṃ labhet|| 11.61||
janantu śītalaṃ datvā sarvakāmamavāpnuyāt|
% . . . suśītalaṃ datvā sarvān kāmān avāpnuyāt| \T32
labheddipapradānena jñānacakṣuratīndriyam|| 11.62||
mṛduśayyāpradānena siṃhāsanapatirbhavet|
%% In T32 the above line occurs after the line 60cd of this edition.
datvāmbhasā tathā snānaṃ saubhāgyaṃ buddhivardhanam|| 11.63||
snānaṃ vividha śaucārthaṃ vāruṇaṃ lokamāpnuyāt|
% datvāmbhaḥ snānaśaucārthaṃ vāruṇaṃ lokamāpnuyāt| \T32
svedabinduparītāṅgam adhvaśramasukarṣitam|| 11.64||
% adhvanaḥ śramakarśitam| \T32
saṃvījya tālavṛntena vāyuloke mahīyate|
kṣutpipāsāturaṃ śrāntaṃ ārtaṃ malinarogiṇam|| 11.65||
% ārtaṃ rogiṇameva vā| \T32
pālayitvā yathāśakti sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate|
%% p. 152
rogārtasya śivaṅkṛtvā bhaiṣajyādyaiḥ prayatnataḥ|| 11.66||
yugakoṭiśataṃ sāgraṃ śivaloke mahīyate|
kālātpunarihāyataḥ samastajñānapāragaḥ|| 11.67||
sarūpaḥ subhagaḥ śrīmān nīrujaḥ suprajaḥ sukhī|
% nirmalo nirupadravaḥ| \T32
śaraṇāgatamudvignam āghrātaṃ riputaskaraiḥ|| 11.68||
mā bhairiti samāśvāsya śivaloke mahīyate|
% mā bhaiṣīriti cāśvāsya \T32
%% p.153
dāridryārṇavanirmagnaṃ hāhābhūtamacetanam|| 11.69||
samuddhṛtya yathāśakti sarvakāmamavāpnuyāt|
% samuddhṛtya yathā śaktyā \T32
patite śastrasaṅkīrṇe svacaṇḍālādipakṣiṇām|| 11.70||
% patitāḥ śastrasaṃkīrṇāḥ śvacaṇḍālādipakṣiṇām| \T32
kāruṇyāt sarvabhūtebhyo deyamannaṃ svaśaktitaḥ|
atyalpamapi kāruṇyāddattaṃ bhavati cākṣayam|| 11.71||
tasmādvai sarvabhūteṣu kāruṇyāddattamakṣayam|
% kāruṇyāddanamuttamam| \T32
abhāve tṛṇabhūmyambhaḥ patramūlaphalāni ca|| 11.72||
datvā gatāyānārye.api svargaṃ yānti priyeṇa vā|
% datvā gatāya nāryo.api \T32
nedṛśaṃ svargasopānaṃ yathāloke priyaṃ vacaḥ|| 11.73||
% mahībhṛt svargasopānaṃ yathā loke\T32
ihāyuṣyaṃ sukhanteṣāṃ vāgyeṣāṃ mudhurasvarā|
% ihāmutra sukhaṃ teṣāṃ \T32
amṛtasyandinīṃ vācañcandanasparśaśītalām|| 11.74||
dharmāvirodhinīmuktvā sukhamakṣayamāpnuyāt|
alaṃ dānena viprendra yājanādyāpanena vā|| 11.75||
% yajanādhyayanena vā| \T32
idaṃ vaḥ svargasopānam alaṃ yat priyaṃ vacaḥ|
% idaṃ tatsvargasopānaṃ \T32
pratyutthānābhigamanamantavrajyāpiryaṃ vacaḥ|| 11.76||
% pratyuthāyābhigamanaṃ varjyaṃ caivāpriyaṃ vacaḥ| \T32
pūrvābhibhāṣaṇā dṛṣṭiḥ pratyekaṃ svargahetavaḥ|
% pūrvābhibhāṣaṇaṃ tuṣṭaḥ \T32
smpṛcchedāgataṃ bhaktyā cāyāte svāgataṃ vdet|| 11.77||
gamane.apyeva vaktavyaṃ panthānaḥ santu te śivāḥ|
%% p.154
śivaṃ bhavatu vo nityam aśeṣārthaprasādhakam|| 11.78||
% śivaṃ bhavatu me nityaṃ \T32
āśīrvādamidaṃ vākyaṃ sarvakāryeṣu sarvadā|
namaskārābhivādeṣu svastimaṅgalavācakaiḥ|| 11.79||
% svastimaṃgalavācane| \T32
śivaṃ bhavatu sarvatra prabrūyāt sarvakarmasu|
% śivaṃ bhavatu vo brūyāt sarvakāryeṣu sarvadā| \T32
evamādiśivācāram anuṣṭhāya śivāśramī|| 11.80||
aśeṣapāpanirmuktaḥ śivaloke mahīyate|
śivabhakteṣu yā bhaktistadbhaktaḥ kriyate naraiḥ|| 11.81||
% tadbhaktai . . tejalaiḥ| \T32
śive bhavati sā nityaṃ bhaktirbhaktairanuṣṭhitā|
ākruṣṭastāḍito vāpi yo nākrośennatāḍayet|| 11.82||
% ākṛṣṭastāḍito vāpi yo \T32
vācā yo.avikṛtaḥ svasthaḥ kṣānitirekhā sunirmalā|
% vāgādyavikṛtā svasthā kṣānitireṣā sunirmalā| \T32
sarveṣāmeva tīrthānāṃ tīrthaṃ jñānasya pāragaḥ|| 11.83||
jñānatīrthāt paraṃ tīrthaṃ ye snātāḥ kṣāntivāriṇā|
% yat pūrṇaṃ kṣāntivāriṇā| \T32
jñānayogatapojapyayajñadānādisatkriyāḥ|| 11.84||
krodhanasya vṛthā yasmāttasmāt krodhaṃ vivarjayet|
% krodhinastu \T32
%% p.155
marmāsthiprāṇahṛdayaṃ nirdayedapriyaṃ vacaḥ|| 11.85||
na vācyamapriyaṃ tasmācchivabhaktairviśeṣataḥ|
kṣamā dānaṃ tapaḥ satyaṃ kṣamā.ahiṃsā kṣamā śrutam|| 11.86||
kṣamā svargasya mokṣasya kṣamayaiva jagaddhṛtam|
%% p.156
sa śūraḥ sāttviko vidvān sa tapasvī jitendriyaḥ|| 11.87||
yenāśu kṣāntiśastreṇa krodhaśatrurvivarjitaḥ|
nirmalaiḥ kṣāntisalilaiḥ samāpyāyanaśītalaiḥ|| 11.88||
% nirmalaiḥ kṣāntisalilaiḥ lokāhlādya śītalaiḥ| \T32
iha saukhyamavāpnoti paratra ca śivāṅgatim|
ātmavat sarvabhūtānāṃ yo hitāya śivāya ca|| 11.89||
% ātmavatsarvabhūteṣu \T32
sarvathā vartate niyam ahiṃseyamudāhṛtā|
% sa yathā vartate nityam \T32
sarvaśāstrāṇi vedāśca yajñāścaiṣāntu yatphalām|| 11.90||
% sarvaśāstreṣu vedeṣu sarvayajñeṣu yatphalam| \T32
ye na hiṃsanti bhūtāni teṣāṃ puṇyantato.adhikam|
% yo na hiṃsanti bhūtāni tasyapuṇyaṃ tato.adhikam| \T32
trailokyamapi yo dadyādakhilaṃ ratnapūritam|| 11.91||
carettapāṃsi sarvāṇi na tattulyam ahiṃsayā|
ahiṃseyaṃ paro dharmaḥ śaktānāṃ parikīrtitam|| 11.92||
% ahiṃsā paramo dharmaḥ \T32
aśaktānāmayandharmo dānayajñādipūrvakaḥ|
nātaḥ paraṃ prapaśyāmaḥ kvacidapyāgame vayam|| 11.93||
puṃsāmabhayadānantu dānamadbhutamuttamam|
% puṃsāmabhayadānāttu \T32
sarvabhūtābhayandatvā yaścarecchāntamānasaḥ|| 11.94||
ihaiva sarvabhūtebhyo na bhayantasya vidyate|
ye na hiṃsanti bhūtāni sthāvarāṇi carāṇi ca|| 11.95||
te bhuñjate duḥkhahīnāḥ parāṃ śāntimanuttamām|
% sarvaduḥkhavinirmuktaḥ parāṃ śāntimavāpnuyāt| \T32
pāpā ramanti pāpeṣu atikrūrā narādhamāḥ|| 11.96||
% pāpe ramante pāpiṣṭhā \T32
āhū(bhū)tasamplavaṃ yāvat pacyante narakeṣu te|
% pacyante narakāgniṣu| \T32
svadeśe yo nṛpaḥ kuryāt prāṇidhātanivāraṇam|| 11.97||
% prāṇighātanivāraṇam| \T32
sa nṛpaḥ saha deśena nandate vibhavaiściram|
dehānte sa mahābhogaiḥ samastakulasaṃyutaḥ|| 11.98||
kalpakoṭisahasrāṇi śivaloke mahīyate|
% kalpakoṭiśataṃ sāgraṃ \T32
yastu svārthaṃ parārthaṃ vā samastendriyasaṃyamaḥ|| 11.99||
% yaḥ svārthaṃ vā parārthaṃ vā \T32
nākārye sampravarteta tamāhuḥ śāntalakṣaṇam|
% akārye na pravarteta \T32
yaḥ praśāntendriyagrāmaḥ sadācandrāṃśunirmalaḥ|| 11.100||
sa prāpnoti paraṃ sthānaṃ śāntaḥ śāntena cetasā|
%% p.157
%% This page records no verses; instead, it records only the commentary of the editor Naraharinath.
%% p.158
yathālabdhopapannena prītyā caiva matena ca|| 11.101||
% yathākālopapannena vṛttinyāyāgatena ca| \T32
utpannārthena yastoṣaḥ santoṣaḥ sa prakīrtitaḥ|
% utpannārtheṣu yastoṣaḥ sa toṣaḥ parikīrtitaḥ| \T32
atītānāgatārtheṣu vartamāne nu(na) jīvati|| 11.102||
% vartamāneṣu sarvadā| \T32
nānusmaratyatītārthaṃ santoṣo.ayamudāhṛtaḥ|
tena sarvamakhairiṣṭaṃ tenāptaṃ caiva satpadam|| 11.103||
% tenacāptaṃ ca tatphalam| \T32
yena tṛṣṇāpadantyaktvā santoṣaḥ samyagāśritaḥ|
% yena tṛṣṇāgrahaṃ tyaktaṃ santoṣaṃ samyagāśritaḥ| \T32
santoṣaiśvaryayuktānāṃ yatsukhaṃ śāntacetasām|| 11.104||
devāsuramanuṣyāṇāṃ kṛtaḥ svapne.api tatsukham|
svānubhūtaṃ svadṛṣṭañca yo dṛṣṭārthanna gūhati|| 11.105||
% yaḥ puṣṭārthaṃ na gṛhyate| \T32
yathābhūtārthakathanam ityetat satyalakṣaṇam|
satyaṃ satyaṃ punaḥ satyam etāvatsatyalakṣanam|| 11.106||
parapīḍāvinirmuktaṃ yāvat syadvacanaṃ śivam|
% yathāvadvacanaṃ śubham| \T32
aśvamedhācca tatsatyam adhikaṃ tulitaṃ purā|| 11.107||
% aśvamedhāyutaṃ puṇyaṃ satyaṃ ca tulayā dhṛtam| \T32
aśvamedhāyutātsatyamadhikaṃ bahubhirguṇaiḥ|
% aśvamedhāyutātsatyaṃ ayutaṃ daśabhirguṇaiḥ| \T32
satye pratiṣṭhitaṃ jñānaṃ dharmaḥ sate pratiṣṭhitaḥ|| 11.108||
satye pratiṣṭhitaṃ śaucaṃ sarvaṃ satye pratiṣṭhitam|
% mokṣaḥ satye pratiṣṭhitaḥ| \T32
svāminā lakṣyamāṇānāmutsṛṣṭānāñca sambhavo|| 11.109||
% svāminā rakṣyamāṇānāṃ utsṛṣṭānāṃ ca saṃbhramāt| \T32
parasvānāmanādānam etadsteyalakṣaṇam|
% idamasteyalakṣaṇam| \T32
na lobhena parasveṣu yo manāgapi vartate|| 11.110||
% alobhena prarasveṣu \T32
karmaṇā manasā vācā s tṛptaḥ śivatāṃ vrajet|
maitunasyāsamācārastadacittamajalpanam|| 11.111||
%% p.159
lakṣaṇaṃ brahmacaryasya samastendriyasaṃyamaḥ|
% samastendriyasaṃyamam| \T32
brahmacarye sthitaṃ śaucaṃ brahmacarye sthitantapaḥ|| 11.112||
brahmacarye sthitaṃ jñānaṃ brahmacarye sthitā kṣamā|
ye sthitā brahmacaryeṇa te te nityaṃ saṃsthitāḥ śive|| 11.113||
ekarātroṣitasyāpi yā gatirbrahmacāriṇaḥ|
% ekarātroṣitā yāpi sā gati brahmacāriṇaḥ| \T32
gṛhibhiḥ sā na samprāptuṃ śakyā yajñaśatairapi|| 11.114||
% sā gṛhasthairna saṃprāptā kṛtayajñaśatairapi| \T32
ya sambhavaṃ samutsṛjya cetasāste nirākulam|
% yaḥ sambhave samutsṛjya cetasā.a.aste nirākulam| \T32
aho yativaraḥ śrīmān sva sva sevā striyāmṛtau|| 11.115||
% nopayāti striyaṃ ratau| \T32
parvavarjyaṃ vrajetso.api paradārādivarjakaḥ|
% parvavarjaṃ brajannopi paradāravivarjitāḥ| \T32
brahmacārisamaḥ so.api jñeyaḥ śivagṛhāśramī|| 11.116||
% brahmacāriṇa ete.api vijñeyā hi śivāśrame| \T32
%% p.160
śivāgnyatithigurvarthaṃ kurvan karmāṇi sarvataḥ|
% kuryāt karmāṇi sarvadā| \T32
ahiṃsakaḥ savijñeyo rudraśca kramate kṣitau|| 11.117||
% ahiṃsākalpavijñeyo na sa tasyāśramatraye| \T32
śivāgnigurukāryeṣu ya udyuktaḥ sadā naraḥ|
% samudyuktaḥ sadā naraḥ| \T32
tasya siddhyanti karmāṇi manasā cintitāni tu|| 11.118||
% manasā cintitānyapi| \T32
eṣa darmadrumaḥ śrīmān aṣṭaśākhaḥ śivodbhavaḥ|
% eṣa dharmavrataḥ śrīmān \T32
na śakto vistarān vaktum upaśākhāprabhedataḥ|| 11.119||
% yaḥ paṭheta śive bhaktyā ācārādhyāyamuttamam| \T32
% trisaptakulajaiḥ sārdhaṃ śivaloke mahīyate|| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.

\Colo
iti śivadharmaśāstre nandikeśvaraprokte śivāśramo nāmaikādaśo.adhyāyaḥ||
% iti śivadharmaśāstre śivāśramācāro nāma ekādaśo.adhyāyaḥ| \T32

%% p.161

%% Chapter 12

atha paśupatimate śivadharme mahāśāstre nandikeśvaraprokte
śivabhaktyādya śākhopaśākhā dvādaśo.adhyāyaḥ||
oṃ namaḥ śivāya
nandikeśvara uvāca
% śrīnandikeśvaraḥ \T32
atha saṃkṣepato vakṣye śivabhaktānukampayā|
ādyaśākhopaśākhārthaṃ śivabhaktisamudbhavam|| 12.1||
% ādyaśākhopaśākharthaśivabhaktisamudbhavam| \T32
kvacidgacchedyadā paśyecchivaliṅgamapūjitam|
% kvacidgacchanyadā paśyet śivaliṃgaṃ prapūjitam| \T32
tadā tat pūjya yo gacchet sa rudro nātr saṃśayaḥ|| 12.2||
% sadā sampūjya yo gacchet \T32
snānaivedyavastrādyan nādadīta priyāṇyapi|
% svānanaivedyavastrāṇi \T32
tyaktanacchivamuddiśya taddānenaiva tatphalam|| 12.3||
% dattaṃ yacchivamuddiśya tasmāddānena yatphalam| \T32
% dṛṣṭvā yatanamāsādya namaskṛtvā śivaṃ vrajet| \T32
%% aiśa Skt (ktvā for lyap)
%% above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
catuṣpathaṃ nadīṃ śailaṃ śivayoginameva ca|
avatīrya namaskuryād dṛṣṭvā liṅgaṃ dṛdhavrataḥ|| 12.4||
% avatīrya namaskṛtvā \T32
%% aiśa Skt (ktvā for lyap)
hastiyānāśvayānebhyaḥ śivayogitapasvinam|
% hastiyānāsanatvebhyaḥ \T32
tatrastho.pi namaskṛtya śivaloke mahīyate|| 12.5||
% tatrastho .api namaskṛtvā \T32
%% aiśa Skt (ktvā for lyap)
mṛgāśvoṣṭrapayo matsyamāṃsalaśunagṛñjanam|
% yūkāśvoṣṭravayomatsyamāṃsaṃ laśunakṛṃjanam| \T32
kavakādyāni vīryañca kutsitañca vivarjayet|| 12.6||
% kabakadvaryaca sauvīraṃ kutsitāni vivarjayet| \T32
% niryāsamapyapakvānnaṃ nityameva vivarjayet| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
sarvadā nogratapasāṃ aśvamedhāyutasya ca|
phalaṃ prāpnotyayatnena matsyamāṃsavivarjanāt|| 12.7||
% phalaṃ prāpnoti yatnena matsyamāṃsasya varjanāt| \T32
sarvadoṣāśrayaṃ madyamatidūrād vivarjayet|
% iti purādvivarjayet| \T32
%% p.162
kva madyaṃ kva śive bhaktiḥ kva śaucaṃ kva śivārcanam|| 12.8||
% kva madyaṃ kva śive bhaktiḥ kva māṃsaṃ kva śivārcanam| \T32
% madyamāṃsaprasaktānāṃ dūre tiṣṭhati śaṅkaraḥ| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
sarvatīrtheṣu yatpuṇyaṃ sarvayajñeṣu yatphalam|
tatphalaṃ labhate sarvaṃ yo madyaṃ parivarjayet|| 12.9||
%% p.163
garbhādijanmasaṃskāraśmaśānāntādibhojanam|
% garbhādisarvasaṃskāre śmaśānānte ca bhojanam| \T32
rajasvalābhisaṃspṛṣṭaṃ śivabhakto vivarjayet|| 12.10||
% rajasvalādisaṃspṛṣṭiṃ śivabhakto vivarjayet| \T32
na gobrāhmaṇabhasmāgniliṅgacchāyāṃ padaiḥ spṛśet|
% na gobrāhmaṇabhasmāni liṃgacchāyāṃ padā spṛśet| \T32
na laṅghayeta nirmālyaṃ nāpsu tiṣṭeta nagnakaḥ|| 12.11||
% na laṃghayīta nirmālyaṃ apsu tiṣṭhenna nagnataḥ| \T32
dhārayecchivanirmālyaṃ bhaktyā lobhānna bhakṣayet|
% bhaktyā lehyaṃ ca bhakṣayet| \T32
bhakṣaṇānnarakaṃ gacchet tadvilaṅghya tvadhagatim|| 12.12||
% tadvilaṃghya ca mūḍhadhīḥ| \T32
na tatra snānapūjādyaṃ pratigṛhṇāni śaṅkaraḥ|
% na tadyaḥ snānapūjādyaṃ pratigṛhṇāti śaṅkaraḥ| \T32
yatra naivedyanirmālyam alaṅghya pūjayecchivam|| 12.13||
% akhalat pūjayecchivam| \T32
bhūpradeśaṃ yathā kaścit svadehamaladūṣitam|
% bhūpradeśe yathā kaścit \T32
nāśrayeta tathā rudro na taṃ nirmālyadūṣitam|| 12.14||
% naraṃ nirmālyadūṣitam| \T32
asaṃspṛśyo bhavet so.api yathā svāṅgamalaspṛśī|
% asaṃspṛśyo bhavetso .ayaṃ yo yasyāṃgamalaṃ spṛśet| \T32
tasmācca na spṛśelliṅgaṃ na te nirmālyadūṣitaḥ|| 12.15||
% tasyāṃ na saṃspṛśelliṃgaṃ nase nirmālyadūṣitaḥ| \T32
yatra naivedyanirmālyaṃ saṅkīrṇaṃ kalaśādibhiḥ|
snānantu kriyate bhaktyā na taṃ gṛhṇāti śaṅkaraḥ|| 12.16||
% snānaṃ vai kriyate bhaktyā na tadgṛhṇāti śaṅkaraḥ| \T32
mūrtayo yāḥ śivasyāṣṭau tāsu nindāṃ vivarjayet|
gurośca śivabhaktānāṃ nṛpasādhutapasvinām|| 12.17||
% gurau ca śivabhakteṣu nṛpasādhutapasviṣu| \T32
aṣṭamyādis.u sarveṣu pakṣayorubhayorapi|
śmaśrukarmākṣunābhyaṅgaprasthānāni vivarjayet|| 12.18||
% śmaśrukamaṃjinābhyaṃgaṃ prasthānaṃ ca vivarjayet| \T32
kuryād viśeṣataḥ pūjāṃ naktaṃ cātra samācaret|
% parameśvarapūjāṃ ca kuryānmaṃntrī samāhitaḥ| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
strīdyūtamadyamāṃsādi yatnāt parvasu varjayet|| 12.19||
trikālamekakālaṃ vā nityaṃ snānaṃ samācaret|
%% The above line 20ab is missing in T32.
śaucañca mṛjjalaiḥ kuryād gandhalepāpanuttaye|| 12.20||
yo.aśnīyādannamasnātaḥ pāpamadyāt sa kevalam|
tasmāt snātvā prabhuñjīta bhasmanā salilena vā|| 12.21||
prātaḥ snātvāmbhasā gacched bhasmanā vā śivaṃ padam|
% bhasmanā ca śivaṃ padam| \T32
% trisaṃdyamācaredyastu śivārcāmagnipūjanam| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
pāpakañcukamutsṛjya kulasaptakamuddharet|| 12.22||
% pāpakaṃcukamutsṛjya śivaloke mahīyate| \T32
kuryāt praticaturmāsaṃ mahāpūjāpravarddhanam|
% mahāpūjāpravartanam| \T32
bhojanaṃ ca pradātavyaṃ śaktyā dānaśca kalpayet|| 12.23||
% bhojanaṃ śivabhaktānāṃ śaktyā dānaṃ prakalpayet| \T32
trisaptakulasaṃyuktaḥ samastaiśvaryasaṃyutaḥ|
gacchecchivapuraṃ ramyaṃ cāturmāsapravartanāt|| 12.24||
% vasecchivapure nityaṃ cāturmāsyapravartanāt| \T32
%% p.164
%% This page records no verses; instead, it records only the commentary of the editor Naraharinath.
%% p.165
daive parvotsave śrāddhe puṇyeṣu divaseṣu ca|
% evaṃ parvotsave śrāddhe \T32
śivaṃ sampūjya naivedyair bhojayecchivayoginaḥ|| 12.25||
% pūjayecchivayoginam| \T32
pitaraḥ sarvadevāśca śivamāśritya saṃsthitāḥ|
prīte śive tu te sarve suprītāḥ syurna saṃśayaḥ|| 12.26||
jñānavairāgyasampannaṃ bhasmaniṣṭhaṃ jitendriyam|
% bhasmaniṣṭhajitendriyam|| 28||
bhojayecchāntamanasaṃ śrāddheṣu śivayoginam|| 12.27||
yadā svarāditattvānāṃ parijñānaṃ vivekataḥ|
% yadīśvarāditattvānāṃ parijñānaṃ vivekatā| \T32
bhavet sādharmyavaidharmyāt tat syājjñānasya lakṣaṇam|| 12.28||
% etajjñānasya lakṣaṇam| \T32
nāniṣṭaṃ dveṣṭi samprāptanna ceṣṭam abhinandati|
praītitāpaviṣādānāṃ vairāgyamativartanam|| 12.29||
% rāgadveṣavihīno yaḥ sa vairāgyeṣu vartate| \T32
bhasmaniṣṭhasya divase darśanenāpi yatphalam|
% bhasmaniṣṭhāpratiṣṭhasya divasenāpi yatphalam| \T32
na tacchakyaṃ gṛhasthena prāptuṃ kratuśatairapi|| 12.30||
vaśyendriyaḥ prasannātmā na ca dviṣṭi na kāṅkṣati|
% yo na dveṣṭi na kāṃkṣati| \T32
śabdādiviṣayān bhogān sa vijñeyo jitendriyaḥ|| 12.31||
jñānavairāgyasampannaḥ śivaśāntena cetasā|
% śivaḥ śāntena cetasā| \T32
yuktaḥ ṣaḍaṅgayogena śivayogī prakīrtitaḥ|| 12.32||
śivadharmodbhavaṃ jñānaṃ jñānādvairāgyasambhavaḥ|
jñānavairāgyayuktasya śivayogaḥ pravartate|| 12.33||
śivayogāśca sarvajñaḥ paripūrṇāstu nityaśaḥ|
% śivayogācca sarvajñaḥ paripūrṇaḥ sunirvṛtaḥ| \T32
svātmanyavasthitaḥ śuddhaḥ śivavat sa śivo bhavet|| 12.34||
% śivavatsarvago bhavet| \T32
sarveṣāmeva bhūtānām uttamaḥ puruṣaḥ smṛtaḥ|
% uttamaṃ mānuṣaṃ smṛtam| \T32
% sarveṣāmeva varṇānāṃ traivarṇyāḥ puruṣāḥ varāḥ| \T32
%% The above line is missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
puruṣebhyo dvijaḥ śreṣṭho dvijebhyo granthapāragaḥ|| 12.35||
% dvijebhyaḥ vedapāragaḥ| \T32
granthajñādvedaviduṣastebhyastattvārthacintakaḥ|
% vedavidbhyastu vidvāṃsaḥ tebhyastattvārthacintakaḥ| \T32
nānātattvavidarthajñāt pratibuddho viśiṣyate|| 12.36||
% tattvavidbhyaśca nānātvaṃ pratibuddho viśiṣyate| \T32
%% p.166
nānātattvajñakoṭibhyo viśiṣṭāḥ śivayoginaḥ|
% nānārthatatvakoṭibhyo viśiṣṭo yogamāśritaḥ| \T32
yogināṃ śatakoṭibhyaḥ paramaḥ śivayogirāṭ|| 12.37||
% yogināṃ yogikoṭibhyaḥ śivayogī viśiṣyate| \T32
% tattvārthavedikoṭibhyaḥ śivayogī viśiṣyate| \T32
yogajñā yoganiṣṭhāśca pitaro yogasambhavāḥ|
bhukte priyanti te sarve viśeṣācchivayogibhiḥ|| 12.38||
% bhuṃkte prīṇanti te tasmāt dviśeṣo .atīva yoginaḥ| \T32
sarvayajñatapodānaiḥ kṛtairdattaiśca yatphalam|
tatphalaṃ labhate sarvaṃ sambhojya śivayoginam|| 12.39||
yaścāgnirudrakālātmā dakṣiṇāhavanistathā|
% yaścāgnikālarudrātyā dakṣiṇābhava ṛtvijaḥ| \T32
ṛgyajuḥ sāmasaṃyogairvedayajña prakīrtitaḥ|| 12.40||
% ṛgyajussāmasaṃyoga evaṃ yajñaḥ prakīrtitaḥ| \T32
%% p.167
brahmacaryaṃ tapo maunaṃ kṣāntirāhāralāghavam|
% brahmacaryaṃ japo maunaṃ \T32
ityetattapasāṃ rūpaṃ sughoraṃ pañcalakṣaṇam|| 12.41||
% ityetattapaso rūpam aghoraṃ pañcalakṣaṇam| \T32
yadiṣṭañca viśiṣṭaśca nyāyapātrañca yadbhavet|
% nyāyaprāptaṃ ca yadbhavet| \T32
tattadguṇavate deyam ityetaddānalakṣaṇam|| 12.42||
% etaddānasya lakṣaṇam| \T32
nivartanasahasrāḍhyāṃ sarvasasyaprarohiṇīm|
% sarvadoṣairvirahitāṃ \T32
dadyādbhūmiṃ jalopetāṃ bhūmidānaṃ taducyate|| 12.43||
ekacchatrāṃ mahīṃ kṛtvā dvijebhyo pratipādayet|
sampūrṇāṃ yo nṛpaḥ kaścid bhūmidānaṃ taducyate|| 12.44||
% mahīdānaṃ taducyate| \T32
% kanyāmalaṃkṛtāṃ dadyādalaṃ jīvanasaṃyutām| \T32
% dvijāya vedaviduṣe kanyādānaṃ taducyate| \T32
% śivabhaktāya viprāya dattvā kanyāṃ svalaṃkṛtām| \T32
% kulatrayaṃ samuddhṛtya svargaṃ prāpnoti niścalam| \T32
%% The above lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
sarvadoṣavinirmuktāṃ taruṇīṃ supayasvinīm| % sarvadoṣavinirmuktaṃ taruṇīṃ yaḥ payasvinīm| \T32
yo gāmalaṅkṛtāndadyād godānaṃ tadudāhṛtam|| 12.45|| % yo gāmalaṃkṛtāṃ dadyād godānamiti kīrtitam| \T32
madhyamottamavastrāṇi yo dadyāttuttamāni ca| % yo dadyāttu navāni ca| \T32
etatsamānato jñeyaṃ vastradānasya lakṣaṇam|| 12.46|| % etatsamāsato jñeyaṃ \T32
brahmacaryasamādhibhyaḥ kṣāntiśīlaparāyaṇaḥ| % brahmacārī samādhisthaḥ śāntaḥ śivaparāyaṇaḥ| \T32
%% p.168
ahorātraṃ na bhuñjīta copavāsasya lakṣaṇam|| 12.47||
catvāriṃśasamāyuktaṃ piṇḍānāṃ hi śatadvayam|
% catvāriṃśatsamāyuktaṃ \T32
niyamādyadyathākāmamiti cāndrāyaṇaṃ smṛtam|| 12.48||
% māsenādyādyathākālam iti cāndrāyaṇaṃ smṛtam| \T32
ṛṣibhiḥ sarvaśāstrajñais taponiṣṭhair jitendriyaiḥ|
devaiś ca sevitaṃ tīrthaṃ kṣitau tīrthan tad ucyate|| 12.49||
% devaiśca sevitaṃ toyaṃ \T32
% evamādyāni dānāni tapāṃsi niyamāni ca| \T32
% samastāni mamāśakyaṃ \gap\ vaktumeva ca| \T32
% sūkṣmāṇi sādhakānyadya mune vakṣyāmi tāni te| \T32
%% The above lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
rudrāvatārasthānāni puṇyakṣetrāṇi nirdiśet|
mṛtānān teṣu rudratvaṃ śivakṣetreṣu dehinām|| 12.50||
%% In T32 here occurs the section of pañcāṣṭaka.
ārāmāvasathaṃ kūpam udyānaṃ devatāgṛham| % dānādyāvasathaṃ kūpaṃ udyānaṃ devatālayam| \T32
tīrtheṣv etāni yaḥ kuryāt so.akṣayaṃ labhate phalam|| 12.51|| % sthāneṣveteṣu yaḥ kuryāt so.akṣayaṃ phalamāpnuyāt| \T32
kṣamā.aspṛhā dayā satyaṃ dānaṃ śīlantapaḥ śrutam|
etad antāṅgam uddiṣṭaṃ paraṃ pātrasya lakṣaṇam|| 12.52||
% etadaṣṭāṃgamuddiṣṭaṃ \T32
yajñopavāsadānāni tapastīrthaphalāni ca|
sampūjya vibhavair bhaktyā labhate śivayoginam|| 12.53||
%% In T32 the above verse 53 occurs in between 55cd and 56ab of this edition. 
śive bhaktiḥ kṣamā satyam aśeṣendriyasaṃyamaḥ|
śivabhakteṣu maitrī ca śivadharmasya lakṣaṇam|| 12.54||
% sarvabhūteṣu maitrī ca  \T32
śivayogī śivajñānī śivadharmarataśca yaḥ|
ity etat trividhaṃ jñeyaṃ śivapātrasya laks.aṇam|| 12.55||
śivam uddiśya dātavyam anapekṣya gṛṇāśrayam(gṛhāśrayam)|
% anapekṣya guṇāśrayam| \T32
vittamīśvarabhaktena śivadānasya lakṣaṇam|| 12.56||
% vittamīśvarabhaktebhyaḥ \T32
%% p.169
śivabhaktaṃ dvijaśreṣṭhaṃ yaḥ śrāddhādiṣu bhojayet|
% śivabhaktadvijaṃ bhaktyā \T32
kulasaptakam uddhṛtya śivaloke mahīyate|| 12.57||
% kulatrayaṃ samuddhṛtya \T32
bahunātra kim uktena śivabhaktan tu bhojayet|
% śivabhaktaṃ prapūjayet| \T32
%% p.170
śivabhkto yadā bhuṅkte sākṣād bhuṅkte tadā śivaḥ|| 12.58|| % śivabhaktaḥ sthito bhuṃkte sākṣādbhuṅkte sadāśivaḥ| \T32
dvijānāṃ vedaviduṣāṃ koṭī sambhojya yatphalam| % koṭiṃ sambhojya yatphalam| \T32
% tatphalaṃ kiṭiguṇitaṃ sambhojya śivayoginam| \T32
% . . . vītarāgāya bhikṣādānena tadbhavet| \T32
%% The above two lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
tasmācchrāddhe viśeṣeṇa puṇyeṣu divaseṣu ca|| 12.59||
śivamuddhiśya viprendraṃ śivabhaktantu bhojayet|
% śivamuddiśya viprendrān śivabhaktāṃśca bhojayet| \T32
% mṛdbhasmādhārapātrāṇi vaṃśālābukṛtāni ca| \T32
% so .api yāṃ gatimāpnoti so .api yajñaśatairapi| \T32
% tasmānmānyaśca pūjyaśca rakṣaṇīyaśca sarvadā| \T32
% nāmamātraprasanno .api kṣaṇārthamapi yaḥ śive| \T32
% sa muniḥ sa mahāsādhuḥ sa yogī sa śivaṃ vrajet| \T32
%% Above five lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
asaṃyataḥ saṃyato vā sarvāvasthāṅgato.api vā|| 12.60||
yo vā so vā (sa vā) śive bhakta śivavatpātramuttamam|
samparkādarthalābhādvā pāpī rudraṃ prapūjayet|| 12.61||
%% The above three lines are missing in T32.
gṛheśrāddhasya yatpuṇyam araṇye tacchavādhikam|
% tacchatādhikam| \T32
śivāśrameṣu vijñeyaṃ tatpuṇyamayutādhikam|| 12.62||
% tannadīṣvayutaṃ puṇyam anantaṃ syācchivālaye| \T32
nivedayīta yaḥ saumyamāsanaṃ dṛdu vetrajam|
% nivedayīta yaḥ samyag āsanaṃ rudravetrajam| \T32
nāgadantamayaṃ vāpi siṃhāsanapatirbhavet|| 12.63||
kaupīnacchādanaṃ vāso nivedya śivayogine|
% kaupīnādīni kārpāsaṃ \T32
yugakoṭisahasrāṇi rudraloke mahīyate|| 12.64||
% śivaloke mahīyate| \T32
aurṇaṃ prāvaraṇaṃ datvā vikīrṇaṃ śivayogine|
% vistīrṇaṃ śivayogine| \T32
lomni lomni suvarṇasya dattasya phalamāpnuyāt|| 12.65||
% romṇi romṇi \T32
mṛgadvīpyādikaṃ dharma tilapiṣṭavimarditam|
% vyāghraṃ mṛgacarmādi \T32
mṛduraktakaṣāyeṇa nivedya śivayogine|| 12.66||
% mṛduraktaṃ kaṣāyeṇa \T32
yāvattadromasaṃkhyānaṃ mṛgadvīpyādicarmaṇi|
% yāvattdromasaṃkhyātaṃ mṛgavyāghrādicarmaṇi| \T32
tāvadvarṣasahasrāṇi rudraloke mahīyate|| 12.67||
% tāvadyugasahasrāṇi \T32
jalasthalasthapatrāṇi yo dadyācchivayogine|
% jalasthalapavitrāṇi nivedya śivayogine| \T32
trāṇārthaṃ sarvajantūnāṃ so.abdalakṣaṃ vaseddivi|| 12.68||
% trāṇārthaṃ sūkṣmatantūnāṃ abdalakṣaṃ vaseddivi| \T32
triveṣṭāmbhaḥ samāyuktaḥ yaḥ pradadyātkamaṇḍalum|
% triviṣkambhasamāyuktaṃ \T32
mahāsarāṃsi yatkṛtvā puṇyaṃ tatsakalaṃ labhet|| 12.69||
% mahāsarāṃsi yaddatvā tatpuṇyaṃ sakalaṃ labhet| \T32
mṛdamānīya saślakṣṇaṃ prāṇidoṣavivarjitām|
% mṛduvāsaśca suślikṣṇaṃ vraṇadoṣavivarjitam| \T32
nivedya śivayogibhyaḥ kṣitidānaphalaṃ labhet|| 12.70||
% sarvayajñaphalaṃ labhet| \T32
bhṛdbhasmādhārapātrāṇi vaṃśālābukṛtāni ca|
% dvyaṃśadāru garvādyaṃ sukṛtaṃ bhaikṣabhājanam| \T32
nivedya śivayogibhyaḥ sarvatīrthaphalaṃ labhet|| 12.71||
% nivedya śivayogibhyaḥ sadā satraphalaṃ labhet| \T32
%% p.171
%% This page records no verses; instead, it records only the commentary of the editor Naraharinath.
%% p.172
dantadhāvanamuddiṣṭaṃ nivedya śivayogine|
divyastrībhogasaṃyuktaṃ divi ramyaṃ puraṃ labhet|| 12.72||
% haimaṃ svarge puraṃ labhet| \T32
yogapaṭṭopavītāni nivedya śivayogine|
vastrayugmasahasrasya dattasya phalamāpnuyāt|| 12.73||
mṛṇmayālābukādyādyaṃ dambhṛtaṃ bhaikṣabhājanam|
nivedya śivayogibhyaḥ sadāsatraphalaṃ labhet|| 12.74||
%% Above verse 74 is missing in T32.
śivabhaktāya yo dadyādupānatkāṣṭhapāduke|
sa medhyāśvasahasrasya dattasya phalamāpnuyāt|| 12.75||
% sa varāśvasahasrasya \T32
kālmāṣadaṇḍaṃ yo dadyādannaṃ vā śivayogine|
% kalmāṣadaṇḍaṃ yo dadyād anyaṃ vā śivayogine| \T32
balāvaṣṭambhayuktābhyāṃ sa syāddaṇḍapraṇāyakaḥ|| 12.76||
% balāvaṣṭambhayuktātmā bhavedaṇḍādhināyakaḥ| \T32
tālavaṃśātapatraṃ vā yo dadyācchivayogine|
% tāmraṃ vaṃśātapatraṃ vā nivedya śivayogine| \T32
ekacchatrāṃ sa bhuñjīta pṛthivīñca narādhipaḥ|| 12.77||
% maṇḍalaṃ śatayojanam| \T32
pātrāntaraviśeṣāṇi viśeṣācchivayogine|
% pātrāntaraviśeṣeṣu datteṣu śivayogine| \T32
bhavet kṣitipatiḥ śrīmān kulādhāro guṇānvitaḥ|| 12.78||
śivajñānābhiyuktāya yo dadyāt pustakaṃ mahat|
yugakoṭiśataṃ divyaṃ rudraloke mahīyate|| 12.79||
% śivaloke mahīyate| \T32
bhavedihāgataḥ śrīmān sadyo vedasya pāragaḥ|
% sukhāḍhyo vedapāragaḥ| \T32
sarvajñānārthavaktā ca bṛhaspatisamo dhiyā|| 12.80||
% samyagjñānārthavaktā ca bṛhaspatisamo bhavet| \T32
śivayogī śivajñānī śivadharmarataśca yaḥ|
śivasamprāptitulyatvāt sarvatulyaguṇaḥ smṛtāḥ|| 12.81||
%% In T32 the above verse 81 occurs after the missing verse mentioned bellow.
yaḥ kuryāt kārayedvāpi vapanaṃ śivayoginām|
varṣalakṣaṃ mahābhogaiḥ śivaloke mahīyate|| 12.82||
% yaḥ kārayecca bhaktānāṃ vapanaṃ śivayoginām| \T32
% ihaloke sukhaṃ prāpya so.ante muktimavāpnuyāt| \T32
% evaṃ vastuviśeṣeṣu datteṣu śivayogine| \T32
%% The above three lines are missing in the printed edition, from Nepal.
rudro rudrākṣadānena bhavatīti kimadbhutam|
tanmālāṃ yaḥ sadā haste rudraśca kramate kṣitau|| 12.83||
% tanmālayā sadāhlaste \T32
rudrākṣāṇi sadā rudro ye ca rudrākṣadhārakāḥ|
% rudrākṣāṇi svayaṃ rudro \T32
rudrākṣadhāraṇāttasmādiha rudraḥ paratra ca|| 12.84||
%% p.173
dhatte rudrākṣamālāṃ yaḥ śobhāyuktāṃ sadā kare|
% rudrākṣamālāṃ yo dhatte bhaktyā kṇṭhe kare.api vā| \T32
śatārdhārdhapramāṇena sa rudro nātra saṃśayaḥ|| 12.85||
paśavo.api hi rudrākṣaiḥ saṃyuktā yānti rudratām|
kiṃ punaścālayanti sma naro rudrākṣamālikām|| 12.86||
ya evaṃ cālayenmālāṃ tajjapyāñca na saṃśayaḥ|
%% The above three lines 86ab - 87ab are missing in T32.
%% p.174
japaśca rudramantrāṇāṃ koṭikoṭiguṇottaram|| 12.87||
% japācca rudramantrāṇāṃ  \T32
